oirs</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">A Night of Meetings×6</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">A Morning of Surprise×6</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">An Afternoon of Ambition×6</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">A King and His People×3</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Soldiers and Weapons×3</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Heart to Heart×3</td>\n<tr><td rowSpan="70" style="text-align:center">Materials</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">XL Character Enhancement×60,000</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">XL Weapon Enhancement×60,000</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Tanzanite×1,650</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Light of Memory×2,000</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Small Wish Fragment×40</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Medium Wish Fragment×40</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Large Wish Fragment×40</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Firm Will×30</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Robust Will×30</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Hidden Ambition×30</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Burning Ambition×30</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Nepheline×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Zeolite×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Rattlestone×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Quartz Sand×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Yellow Sand×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">White Sand×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Red Earth×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">White Earth×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Black Earth×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Rhyolite×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Granite×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Amphibolite×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Tuff×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Basalt×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Diorite×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Gneiss×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Angrite×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Moldavite×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Aubrite×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Chondrite×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Eucrite×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Merlinite×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Growth Agent×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Secret Growth Agent×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Curing Agent×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Potent Curing Agent×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Elongator×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">High-quality Elongator×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Active Agent×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Superior Active Agent×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Refining Agent×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Valuable Refining Agent×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Enhancement Agent×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Rare Enhancement Agent×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Normal Nail×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Sturdy Nail×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Small Nut×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Large Nut×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Generic Bolt×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Stainless Steel Bolt×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Common Wax×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Fine Wax×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Standard Gear×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Intricate Gear×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Rusty Coil×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Pristine Coil×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Standard Machine Oil×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Pure Machine Oil×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Basic Wire×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Stainless Steel Wire×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Young Timber×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Flawless Timber×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Used Charcoal×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Prized Charcoal×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Broken Glass×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Reinforced Glass×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">White Cloth×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Natural Cloth×300</td>\n<tr><td rowSpan="25" style="text-align:center">Companion Materials</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Low-quality Ink×850</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Medium-quality Ink×850</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">High-quality Ink×850</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Superb-quality Ink×850</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Small Meat Hunk×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Medium Meat Hunk×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Large Meat Hunk×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Massive Meat Hunk×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Small Feather Duster×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Medium Feather Duster×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Large Feather Duster×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">XL Feather Duster×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Small Fish×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Medium Fish×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Large Fish×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Massive Fish×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Small Battery×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Medium Battery×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Large Battery×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">XL Battery×300</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Small Circuit×550</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Medium Circuit×550</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Large Circuit×550</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">XL Circuit×550</td>\n<tr><td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center">Gold</td>\n</tr><td style="text-align:left">Gold×20,000,000</td>\n\n\n</tbody>\n\n\n</table>\n\n\n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Notes\n  </h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n    <ul>\n      <li>\n        Duration and content are subject to change without notice.\n      </li>\n      <li>\nIf you already have a companion, you will receive Skip Ticket x50 instead.<br>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n<br />\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/0bfeaf6dcb9ebe0400ad66bad046ef8a8903c05e9441a5bd2ef4d9a19ab9bd38','/images/en/operations/banner/8ce5aca4610d1a3ff03fa4d3c74e7dfb3cec4fe7c5b5979b960dd40926173fec');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1081,0,1,'Ver2.19.20 Update',1680847200000,replace('<section> \n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/2dbfc2692574355ac476fa119e6784df2eade9b1f9f18c130a3c9df53c165feb">\n</div>\n<p>Hello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n<br />\nThe latest version of the app, <span class="text-red">ver. 2.19.20</span> will be released on Apr. 9 PST.\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>Update Details</h3>\n\n<h4>App system has been updated</h4>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n  <h3>Notes</h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n    <ul>\n <li>It may take some time for the new version of the app to show up in the store.</li>\n <li>This version update requires a large amount of data. We recommend using Wi-Fi while updating.</li>\n <li>The mandatory update to the new version is scheduled for <span class="text-red">Apr. 10, around 17:30 PST</span>.<br>\n* The mandatory update date/time is subject to change without notice. Thank you for your understanding.<br>\n* Until the update becomes mandatory, you can use the application even if you have not updated it yet.\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<p>Thank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/2dbfc2692574355ac476fa119e6784df2eade9b1f9f18c130a3c9df53c165feb','/images/en/operations/banner/03875df530f8b9b6bfe18b040bba799796a7aab9a4e5024670e373c6e877a0e0');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1098,0,1,'Batch Weapon Loadout',1682402400000,replace('<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/17f34311c712b0cb7d071dfce551eaaeb5e7a4d2771cf12f2ceffc1a62a4b2bd">\n</div>\n\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n<br />\nThe new Batch Weapon Loadout feature will be added with the Ver 2.20.0 update.<br />\n</p>\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>About Batch Weapon Loadout</h3>\n<h4>Batch Weapon Loadout</h4>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/0b35a9902025981b58c509982620c4c4021235ce3b9b946ecdfea69e95e65637">\n</div>\n<p><span class="text-red">Primary and Secondary weapons can be equipped at once</span> using the Batch Weapon Loadout button on the Loadout screen.</p>\n\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>Notes</h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n    <ul>\n\n      <li>\n        This content is subject to change without notice.\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n</section>\n<br />\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>','\n',char(10)),NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/17f34311c712b0cb7d071dfce551eaaeb5e7a4d2771cf12f2ceffc1a62a4b2bd','/images/en/operations/banner/78be899666f23fcbfaf6636803cd3fe007b967d9f2bf492d1b554ef84644329c');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1099,0,1,'Ver2.20.0 Update',1682402400000,replace('<section> \n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/2dbfc2692574355ac476fa119e6784df2eade9b1f9f18c130a3c9df53c165feb">\n</div>\n<p>Hello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n<br />\nThe latest version of the app, <span class="text-red">ver. 2.20.0</span> will be released on Apr. 26 PST.\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>Update Details</h3>\n\n<h4>"Batch Weapon Loadout" Addition</h4>\n<p>Improvements will be made to the Loadout screen so that <span class="text-red">Primary and Secondary weapons can be equipped at once</span>.</p>\n\n<br>\n\n<h4>Monthly Pass Release Prep</h4>\n<p>\n<span class="text-red">This feature will let you take on special missions</span> that are updated every month.<br />\nThere will be two types: the Standard Monthly Pass and the Premium Monthly Pass.<br />\n* This content will be made available on May 1 PST.\n</p>\n\n\n<section>\n  <h3>Notes</h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n    <ul>\n <li>It may take some time for the new version of the app to show up in the store.</li>\n <li>This version update requires a large amount of data. We recommend using Wi-Fi while updating.</li>\n <li>The mandatory update to the new version is scheduled for <span class="text-red">Apr. 27, around 17:30 PST</span>.<br>\n* The mandatory update date/time is subject to change without notice. Thank you for your understanding.<br>\n* Until the update becomes mandatory, you can use the application even if you have not updated it yet.\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<p>Thank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/2dbfc2692574355ac476fa119e6784df2eade9b1f9f18c130a3c9df53c165feb','/images/en/operations/banner/03875df530f8b9b6bfe18b040bba799796a7aab9a4e5024670e373c6e877a0e0');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1109,0,2,'Event Quest "Fate Board: Shadow" On Now',1682647200000,replace('<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/900362239868895a50c610d64422e3a6a670bde08fa75a8cd8bdb3dac46b49e4">\n</div>\n\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n<br />\nThe Event Quest <span class="text-red">Fate Board: Shadow</span> open on Apr. 27 18:00 PST.  <br>\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>Duration</h3>\n<p>\n<div class="holding-period">Apr. 27 18:00 - May 18 17:59 PST</div>\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>How to Play Event Quests</h3>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/8b06e7521b786aa1dc476b0a7fe0d53a94643fc5c543e354738329d13a0d379b">\n</div>\n\n<p>\nFate Board: Shadow is a <span class="text-red">high-difficulty event quest centered around creating affinity-based loadouts</span>.<br />\nThe five quests, organized as a single stage, feature <span class="text-red">light</span> or <span class="text-red">dark</span> enemies.<br />\nIn each quest, there are <span class="text-red">Loadout Bonus</span> that further enhance stats when equipping weapons of certain affinities in your loadout. Make use of the effects to gain the upper hand.<br />\nSince the enemies have high HP and use powerful attacks, use your allies'' <span class="text-red">recovery skills</span> to your advantage in battle.<br />\nRewards include items needed to <span class="text-red">Exalt</span> your characters or <span class="text-red">Refine</span> your weapons.<br />\n<br />\n\n* This event quest will be unlocked upon completing Main Quest Ch. 2.<br />\n* This event is scheduled to reappear in the future, at which time the clear status will be carried over.<br />\n<br />\n</p>\n\n\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/051934b7eec5dfb3a45a7605326d535cb5d43837819aadac91a615328b8c31ac">\n</div>\n\n<p>\nPutting weapons of a specific affinity for each quest as the primary or secondary weapons in your loadout will create a <span class="text-red">Loadout Bonus</span> which enhances the target weapons'' stats during the quest.<br />\n<br />\n* The Loadout Bonus will only apply during quests. The parameters displayed in the loadout screen are the values before the Loadout Bonus is applied.<br />\n<br />\n\n<br />\n</p>\n\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/497dbc29949534c1da19c811685f9d9822daaebb88b8ace695cb059d8b562fb8">\n</div>\n\n<p>\nIn addition to the quest clear rewards, there are also <span class="text-red">period achievement rewards</span>, <span class="text-red">quest mission rewards</span>, and <span class="text-red">stage clear rewards</span>.<br />\n<br />\nPeriod achievement rewards are rewards for quests completed up to a point that can be obtained by logging in after the availability period, either in The Cage or on the main screen of the event.<br />\nRewards can be claimed during the event of the same name.<br />\n* Rewards will vary depending on the quest reached at the end of each event.<br />\n<br />\nYou can only get the quest mission rewards once. They are earned based on <span class="text-red">the total number of quest missions completed for each stage</span>.<br />\n<br />\nYou can only claim stage clear rewards once, from <span class="text-red">a treasure chest that appears upon clearing each stage</span>.<br />\n* Rewards from a treasure chest are not sent to your gift box and are added directly to your inventory.<br />\n\n<br />\n* You may not be able to claim period achievement rewards if you have not opened the event''s main screen even once during the event period.\n<br />\n</p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>\nNotes\n</h3>\n<div class="attention_content">\n<ul>\n<li>\nDuration and content are subject to change without notice.\n</li>\n<li>\nIllustrations shown in notices, etc. may differ from those in-game.\n</li>\n<li>\nYou cannot have more than one character with the same name in the same deck.\n</li>\n<li>\n <span class="text-red">Note: Force Bonus is not available for Fate Boards quests.</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</section>\n<br />\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/900362239868895a50c610d64422e3a6a670bde08fa75a8cd8bdb3dac46b49e4','/images/en/operations/banner/d41152e0481ab4e5926efcce7be70a8bc9ace564d91bac6778d0d5d207d6216f');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1110,0,7,'Monthly Pass Now Available',1682928000000,replace('<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/d174152e4232ee88f6c576d462a7180ece3f1dcf7748b3158d8a4ccd38eeb99a">\n</div>\n<p>\n Hello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br /> \n This is a message from the management team.<br />\n <br />\nThe <span class="text-red">Monthly Pass</span> is available as of May 1 0:00 PST.<br />\n\nThe Monthly Pass lets you take on special monthly missions that give Mission Points when you complete them. Your Monthly Pass level will increase as you earn more points from missions, and you''ll obtain rewards based on your level.<br />\n<br />\n\n\nThere are two types of Monthly Pass: the Standard Monthly Pass and the <span class="text-red">Premium Monthly Pass</span>. You can purchase the Premium Monthly Pass from the Premium Shop, and it will give you access to rewards like <span class="text-red">Awakening Stone Exchange Medals</span> and <span class="text-red">★★★★ Premium Summon Tickets</span>.<br /><br />\n* Each Monthly Pass offers different rewards.<br />\n* The Standard Monthly Pass is free to all users who want to take on the missions.<br />\n* To view details on the Monthly Pass, tap "Pass" at the top of the screen.\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>Sale Duration</h3>\n<div class="holding-period">\nMay 1 0:00 - May 31 <span class="text-red">21:59</span> PST\n</div>\n</section>\n\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Awakening Stone Exchange Medals</h3>\n<p><span class="text-red">Special medals that can be exchanged for Awakening Stones for costumes of your choice</span> at the Awakening Stone Medal Exchange.<br />\n* You can only exchange Awakening Stones for each costume once.<br />\n* Some costumes available in events and campaigns are not applicable.<br />\n* Costumes will be added regularly to the Exchange.\n</p>\n\n</section>\n\n* The Premium Monthly Pass gives you access to Standard Monthly Pass rewards as well.\n</p>\n\n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Notes\n  </h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n    <ul>\n      <li>\n        Availability and content are subject to change without notice.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Level-based rewards will not be sent to your gift box, but will be added directly to your inventory.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Mission Points are not carried over to the next month.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        You will earn rewards for the Monthly Pass levels you reached prior to purchasing your Premium Monthly Pass.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        The Premium Monthly Pass can only be applied to the Monthly Pass for the month in which it was purchased.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        The mission period ends on <span class="text-red">May 31 23:59 PST</span>.\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n<br />\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/d174152e4232ee88f6c576d462a7180ece3f1dcf7748b3158d8a4ccd38eeb99a','/images/en/operations/banner/ddb5b114afc031bfead1cb9e8ca966e7cf9150ced6b70b25797c44a64809a0aa');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1119,0,4,'Support Campaigns in May',1682928000000,replace('<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/04e2679a33dd5eb53c46e2f4f14408a9efe5c48ab32ccfc0f37d1fcda3b7ec89">\n</div>\n<p>\n Hello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br /> \n This is a message from the management team.<br />\n <br />\n The <span class="text-red">Support Campaigns</span> for May has begun as of May 1 0:00 PST.<br />\n Details of each campaign are as follows.\n </p>\n\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>Support Campaign List for May</h3>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/7a875158bfa3313992a649a83d7bf0b5919df4edd9eeab6f1441af04d4f5237d">\n</div>\n\n<section>\n<h4>Main & Guerrilla Quest Support Campaign</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nMay 1 0:00 - May 10 23:59 PST\n</div>\n\n<p>\n-The drop rate of all items in the main quest and guerrilla quest will increase by <span class="text-red">x2.5.</span><br>\n-The stamina cost for main quest and guerrilla quest will be <span class="text-red">halved</span>.<br>\n-At least one <span class="text-red">Small Slab Fragment and Medium Slab Fragment</span> will drop from story quests.<br>\n</p>\n\n</section>\n\n<br>\n\n<section>\n<h4>Memoir Collection and Enhancement Support Campaign</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nMay 11 0:00 - May 20 23:59 PST\n</div>\n<p>\n-The drop rate of all items in dungeons will increase by <span class="text-red">x2.5.</span><br>\n-The stamina cost for dungeons will be <span class="text-red">halved</span>.<br>\n-<span class="text-red">"Success" will be guaranteed</span> when enhancing memoirs.<br>\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<br>\n\n\n<section>\n<h4>Dark Memories & Daily Quest Support Campaign</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nMay 21 0:00 - May 31 23:59 PST\n</div>\n\n<p>\n-The drop rate of all items in the daily quests will increase by <span class="text-red">x2.5</span>.<br>\n-The drop rate of all items in the Dark Coin Quest and EX Ticket Quest will increase by <span class="text-red">x2</span>.<br>\n-The stamina cost for dark memories quests and daily quests will be <span class="text-red">halved</span>.<br>\n-Completing specific quests in any of the Dark Memory quests, at least one <span class="text-red">Recalling Light</span> will be a guaranteed drop.<br>\n</p>\n\n</section>\n\n<br>\n\n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Notes\n  </h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n    <ul>\n      <li>\n        When the stamina cost is halved from an odd number, the decimal number will be rounded down to the lower value. \n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Event duration and content are subject to change without notice.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        The campaigns may reappear in the future.\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n<br />\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/04e2679a33dd5eb53c46e2f4f14408a9efe5c48ab32ccfc0f37d1fcda3b7ec89','/images/en/operations/banner/addfbd1a2ddb833f8ec8279da2a35c746a665087a4e59ccbe346e7ba0333dd0c');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1136,0,5,'Regarding the Issue in ''The People and the World'' New Chapter',1684375200000,replace('<section>\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br>\n<br>\nAs of May 17 18:00 PST, we have confirmed the following issues with the new chapter addition of The People and the World.\n</p>\n<h3>Currently Known Issues</h3>\n<p>\nThe storyline of some Dark Memories quests may be stuck replaying, making it impossible to progress.\n\n</p>\n\n<h3>Known Causes</h3>\n<p>This issue may affect players that have cleared Very Hard Quest 9 and Quest 10 of The Moon VI: Daybreak or The Sun VI: Twilight by Mar. 22 18:00 PST 2023, and have since not opened the app until May 17 2023 18:00 PST.\n\n</p>\n\n<h3>Known Fixes</h3>\n<p>\nThis issue can be resolved by restarting the app.<br>\n</p>\n<br>\n<p>\nWe thank you for your patience and apologize for the inconvenience.<br>\n</p>\n\n<section>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1250,0,5,'Regarding the Issue in ''The People and the World'' New Chapter',1689819900000,replace('<section>\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br>\n<br>\nAs of Jul. 19 18:00 PST, we have confirmed the following issues with the new chapter addition of The People and the World.\n</p>\n<h3>Known Issues</h3>\n<p>\n<h4>Background music may not play when starting The People and the World Overture II: Scarlet.</h4>\n\n<p>\nThis issue may be resolved using the following methods.<br> \n   1.The issue may be resolved by restarting the application.<br>\n   2. The issue may be resolved by starting Overture II: Scarlet from the map.<br>\n   3. The issue may be resolved by clearing Quest 1 of Overture II: Scarlet.<br><br>\n\n\n</p>\n\n<h4>Unintended effects may be displayed regarding the hologram of Mama during some scenarios in the Opening and Overture II: Scarlet chapters of The People and the World.</h4>\n<p><span class="text-red">This issue was fixed on Jul. 19 20:25 PST. </span><br>\n</p>\n<br>\n<p>\nWe are currently working on finding out the cause of the issues that have not been fixed yet, and appreciate your patience and understanding.<br />\n</p>\n\n<section>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),1689832800000,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1267,0,3,'Festive Girl Summons On Now',1691114400000,replace('<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/e30967cda39f508c156ca9e5ac7133153c972b653d30d3be5d4018eeeb3f4d04">\n</div>\n\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n<br />\n\nThe <span class="text-red">Festive Girl Summons</span> is available as of Aug. 3 18:00 PST.<br />\nThe new featured character <span class="text-red">Fio (Festive Girl)</span> <span class="text-red">will have the Karma feature</span> after the Aug. 17 PST update.\n</p>\n\n<section>\n<h3>New Costume Series: Festive Summons</h3>\n<p>\nThe summons are scheduled as follows. Paid Only summons will be available at the same time.\n</p>\n<br />\n\n\n<h4><span class="text-red">Festive Girl Summons</span></h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\n<span class="text-red">Aug. 3 18:00 - Aug. 10 17:59 PST</span>\n</div>\n\n\n<h4>Festive Hunter Summons</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nAug. 10 18:00 - Aug. 17 14:59 PST\n</div>\n\n\n<h4>Festive Weapon Summons</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nAug. 17 18:00 - Aug. 24 17:59 PST\n</div>\n\n\n<h4>Festive Monster Summons</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nAug. 24 18:00 - Aug. 31 17:59 PST\n</div>\n\n\n<h4>Reverie''s Garb Summons (all 4 new costumes listed above will appear)</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nAug. 31 18:00 - Sep. 10 17:59 PST\n</div>\n<br /><br />\n\n\n\n<p>\nSummon shard summons and exchange periods are as follows.\n</p>\n<br />\n\n\n<h4>Summon Shards (Festive) Exchange</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nAug. 3 18:00 - Sep. 2 17:59 PST\n</div>\n<p>\n・ Shards (Festive) can be obtained from the <span class="text-red">Festive Girl Summons</span>, <span class="text-red">Festive Hunter Summons</span>, <span class="text-red">Festive Weapon Summons</span>, and <span class="text-red">Festive Monster Summons</span>.<br />・ Exchangeable weapons will be added <span class="text-red">as each summons period begins</span>.\n\n\n\n<br /><br />\n\n<h4>Summon Shards (Reverie''s Garb) Exchange</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nAug. 31 18:00 - Sep. 12 17:59 PST\n</div>\n<p>\n・ Shards (Reverie''s Garb) can be obtained from the <span class="text-red">Reverie''s Garb Summons</span>.\n</p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n<section>\n\n<h3>Limited-time Characters &amp; Weapons</h3>\n<p>In this summons, the <span class="text-red">following limited-time characters have featured rates</span>.<br />\n\n\n\nInformation on stats, skills, and abilities can be found on the summons screen.</p>\n\n<h4>Limited-Time Characters</h4>\n<p>\n<img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/></p>\n\n<p><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/4cc0cf287f70cdf1938c5469c868f7a30a6dcb1a54ae9d78e7629cbd450a84fe" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Fio (Festive Girl)<br />\n* You can get this character by acquiring the <span class="text-red">Jester''s Grin</span> weapon.</p>\n<br />\n\n\n<h4>Limited-Time Weapons</h4>\n<p><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/></p>\n\n<p><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/848ae4b130de4fb052bf9123a775b2ded35ea163a39d95df984d62840b994508" class="weapon_icon" width="6%">Jester''s Grin<br /></p>\n\n<br />\n<p>\nIn addition, weapons that come with the previously appearing Celebratory costume series characters will reappear in this summons. For more information, please check Rates on the summons page.<br /><br />\n<span class="text-red">* Celebratory character weapons will not have featured rates.</span>\n</p>\n\n\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Summons Details\n  </h3>\n    <div class="information_table">\n    <table style="width:58%">\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th style="width:6%">\n            Type\n          </th>\n          <th style="width:12%">\n            Required Gems\n          </th>\n          <th style="width:40%">\n            Obtainable Shards (Festive)\n          </th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            1x summons\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/gem_icon.png" width="20%"> 300\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/consumable118192_icon.png" width="6%"> 1\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            10x summons\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/gem_icon.png" width="20%"> 3,000\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/consumable118192_icon.png" width="6%"> 10\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n\n<p>\n<span class="text-red">At least one ★★★ or higher weapon is guaranteed</span> in each <span class="text-red">10x summon</span>.<br />\n* You will also earn the appropriate number of shards (Festive) for summons performed using premium summon tickets (including 10x summon tickets).\n</p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Summon Shards (Festive)</h3>\n<p>\nYou will earn <span class="text-red">Shards (Festive)</span> every time you use the Festive Girl Summons.<br />\nTrade <span class="text-red">150 Shards (Festive)</span> at the Shard (Festive) Exchange to acquire limited-time characters. New items will be added for exchange <span class="text-red">as each Festive summons period begins</span>.<br />\n<br />\n* The Exchange <span class="text-red">is only available for a limited time.</span> Once the exchange period ends, you will be unable to exchange shards.<br />\n* Once the exchange period ends, each remaining shard <span class="text-red">will be converted into a bookmark</span> upon entering the summons screen.<br />\n* If you exchange for a character weapon you already own, you will earn <span class="text-red">10 ascension materials and 1 Awakening Stone for the character in addition to the weapon</span>.<br />\n* Shards can only be used at the exchange of the same name.<br />\n* Shards earned from both free and paid versions of the <span class="text-red">Festive Girl Summons</span>, <span class="text-red">Festive Hunter Summons</span>, <span class="text-red">Festive Weapon Summons</span>, and <span class="text-red">Festive Monster Summons</span> are the same item.<br />\n\n* Shards earned from both free and paid versions of the <span class="text-red">Reverie''s Garb Summons</span> are <span class="text-red">different items</span>.<br />\n\n* You will also earn shards for summons performed using premium summon tickets (including 10x summon tickets).<br />\n\n<section>\n<h3>Resonant Costume Bonuses in Subjugation Battles</h3>\n<p>\n\nSeason 006 of Subjugation Battles will have a resonant costume quest bonus. The bonus effect of the resonant costumes <span class="text-red">reduces cooldown time for weapon skills in certain Subjugation Battle quests</span> and <span class="text-red">activates an attack increase based on the ascension count</span>.<br />\n</p>\n\n</section>\n<section>\n\n   <div class="information_table weapon_table">\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n\n\n          <th colSpan="5" class="al-center">Ascension Count and Effects</th>\n　　　　　　　　　\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n\n          <th style="width:10%">None</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">1</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">2</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">3</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">4</th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n   　　　　　<tr>\n\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+25%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n+10%<br /></td>\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+30%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n+10%<br /></td>\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+35%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n+10%<br /></td>\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+40%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n+10%<br /></td>\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+50%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n+10%<br /></td>\n\n        </tr>\n         \n\n        <tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n</section>\n<br />\n\n<section>\n<h4>Quest Bonus: Resonant Costume Effect</h4>\n  <div class="information_table powerup_rate_table">\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th>\n            Resonant Costume\n          </th>\n          <th>\n            Quests\n          </th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <th>\n            <img class="chara_image" src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/4cc0cf287f70cdf1938c5469c868f7a30a6dcb1a54ae9d78e7629cbd450a84fe" alt=""> Fio (Festive Girl)\n          </th>\n\n          <td>\n           <span class="text-red">Manifestation: Windy Cursed God</span>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n \n\n    \n\n    </table>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>Event Quest Bonuses</h3>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/5bb839e87224494376cc56fb5bc4e22bb74b1d395565aad0ed2e832a634af83d">\n</div>\n<p>\nThe characters and weapons featured in this summons grant <span class="text-red">quest bonuses</span> in the event quest "Record: Happy Home". Playing the quest with these costumes will activate <span class="text-red">various effects</span>, and some effects will <span class="text-red">increase depending on the ascension count</span>.</span><br />\n<p/>\n<section>\n\n   <div class="information_table weapon_table">\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n\n         \n          <th colSpan="5" class="al-center">Resonant Costume "Festive Girl" Ascension Count Effect</th>\n　　　　　　　　　\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n\n          <th style="width:10%">None</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">1</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">2</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">3</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">4</th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n   　　　　　<tr>\n          \n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+100%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+125%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+150%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+175%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+200%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>\n\n        </tr>\n         \n        <tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n\n<p>\n<br />\n\nIn addition, resonant weapons will have an effect that <span class="text-red">increases the amount of Happy Home Medals dropped</span>.</span><br />\n\n\n<h4> Quest Bonus: Resonance Weapon Effect</h4>\n<div class="information_table weapon_table">\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th rowSpan="2" style="width:28%">Weapon</th>\n<th rowSpan="2" style="width:14%; text-align:center;">Event Tickets</th>\n<th colspan="5" style="text-align:center">Ascension Count</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th style="text-align:center">None</th>\n<th style="text-align:center">1</th>\n<th style="text-align:center">2</th>\n<th style="text-align:center">3</th>\n<th style="text-align:center">4</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n    <tbody>\n      \n\n      <tr>\n        <th><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/848ae4b130de4fb052bf9123a775b2ded35ea163a39d95df984d62840b994508" class="weapon_icon">Jester''s Grin</th>\n        <td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center"><img class="coin_icon" src="/images/en/operations/coin/7a59d1c16765c471ea700f22a996e89c8ad48d8d3f0e96f0bf2601fcd7972a41"><br />\n\n          <img class="coin_icon" src="/images/en/operations/coin/e33c1c76b54eac5cc42a8a835a14638bb94c797e42b3d91532630c6b80353ca6">\n          <img class="coin_icon" src="/images/en/operations/coin/e285379997f716f2520112601d9e40aa1d98356951af0fab1f4bb498e38e5fb4">\n        </td>\n        <td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center">+5</td>\n        <td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center">+11</td>\n        <td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center">+17</td>\n        <td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center">+23</td>\n        <td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center">+30</td>\n      </tr>\n\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div>\n\n<p>\nFor more information on the event quest, check the "Resurrected Event Quest "Record: Happy Home" On Now" notice.\n<p/>\n<div data-category="information" data-informationId="1269" class="other-link-btn common_btn common_button-typeA">Resurrected Event Quest "Record: Happy Home" On Now</div>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Notes\n  </h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n    <ul>\n      <li>\n        Event duration and content are subject to change without notice.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Illustrations shown in notices, etc. may differ from those in-game.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        The rarity, stats, skills, and abilities of characters and weapons displayed on the summons screen and on the official Twitter account are shown at maximum levels.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        "Increased rates" means that the character''s appearance rate is higher than that of other characters of the same rarity.\n      </li>\n<li>\n<span class="text-red">Fio (Festive Girl) &amp; Jester''s Grin will appear in future summons.</span><br />\n</li>\n<li>\n        <span class="text-red">Fio (Festive Girl) &amp; Jester''s Grin will not appear when using ★★★+ Premium Summon Tickets or ★★★★ Premium Summon Tickets.</span>\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        You cannot have more than one character with the same name in the same deck.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        For more information about rates, please check the Rates button on the summons page.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        If you perform a summons using the 10x summon button, a ★★★ or higher weapon will always appear on the 10th summon, regardless of the results of the first 9 summons.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        The video clip that plays when pressing the Skill button was recorded in a development environment.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        The skill introduction video shows the character at level 20 equipped with only a primary weapon at level 1 and all skill levels at level 1.\n      </li>\n            <li>\n        Shards (Festive) can only be used during the exchange period and cannot be carried over to the next event.\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n<br />\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n  </section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/37959ca22d53eaa9c442895fbd73f75cc018d3cf44bb8ed92dda9aaa6e969036');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1268,0,3,'Paid Only: Festive Girl Multi-Step Summons On Now',1691114400000,replace('<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/995f4c1a1d3f0c1b81dd582b6cf03a56f8f04545febc711772476d706040111b">\n</div>\n\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n<br />\nThe <span class="text-red">Paid Only: Festive Girl Multi-Step Summons</span> is available as of Aug. 3 18:00 PST.<br />\nIn Step 2, <span class="text-red">Fio (Festive Girl) or past Celebratory character</span> will be guaranteed in the 10th slot.<br>\nIn Step 3, <span class="text-red">Fio (Festive Girl)</span> will be guaranteed in the 10th slot. <br />\n\nThe new featured character <span class="text-red">Fio (Festive Girl)</span> <span class="text-red">will have the Karma feature</span> after the Aug. 18 PST update.\n</p>\n\n<section>\n<h3>New Costume Series: Festive Summons</h3>\n<p>\nThe summons are scheduled as follows. Paid Only summons will be available at the same time.\n</p>\n<br />\n\n\n<h4><span class="text-red">Festive Girl Summons</span></h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\n<span class="text-red">Aug. 3 18:00 - Aug. 10 17:59 PST</span>\n</div>\n\n\n<h4>Festive Hunter Summons</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nAug. 10 18:00 - Aug. 17 14:59 PST\n</div>\n\n\n<h4>Festive Weapon Summons</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nAug. 17 18:00 - Aug. 24 17:59 PST\n</div>\n\n\n<h4>Festive Monster Summons</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nAug. 24 18:00 - Aug. 31 17:59 PST\n</div>\n\n\n<h4>Reverie''s Garb Summons (all 4 new costumes listed above will appear)</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nAug. 31 18:00 - Sep. 10 17:59 PST\n</div>\n<br /><br />\n\n\n\n<p>\nSummon shard summons and exchange periods are as follows.\n</p>\n<br />\n\n\n<h4>Summon Shards (Festive) Exchange</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nAug. 3 18:00 - Sep. 2 17:59 PST\n</div>\n<p>\n・ Shards (Festive) can be obtained from the <span class="text-red">Festive Girl Summons</span>, <span class="text-red">Festive Hunter Summons</span>, <span class="text-red">Festive Weapon Summons</span>, and <span class="text-red">Festive Monster Summons</span>.<br />・ Exchangeable weapons will be added <span class="text-red">as each summons period begins</span>.\n\n\n\n<br /><br />\n\n<h4>Summon Shards (Reverie''s Garb) Exchange</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nAug. 31 18:00 - Sep. 12 17:59 PST\n</div>\n<p>\n・ Shards (Reverie''s Garb) can be obtained from the <span class="text-red">Reverie''s Garb Summons</span>.\n</p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n<section>\n\n<h3>Limited-time Characters &amp; Weapons</h3>\n<p>In this summons, the <span class="text-red">following limited-time characters have featured rates</span>.<br />\n\n\n\nInformation on stats, skills, and abilities can be found on the summons screen.</p>\n\n<h4>Limited-Time Characters</h4>\n<p>\n<img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/></p>\n\n<p><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/4cc0cf287f70cdf1938c5469c868f7a30a6dcb1a54ae9d78e7629cbd450a84fe" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Fio (Festive Girl)<br />\n* You can get this character by acquiring the <span class="text-red">Jester''s Grin</span> weapon.</p>\n<br />\n\n\n<h4>Limited-Time Weapons</h4>\n<p><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/></p>\n\n<p><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/848ae4b130de4fb052bf9123a775b2ded35ea163a39d95df984d62840b994508" class="weapon_icon" width="6%">Jester''s Grin<br /></p>\n\n<br />\n<p>\nIn addition, weapons that come with the previously appearing Celebratory costume series characters will reappear in this summons. For more information, please check Rates on the summons page.<br /><br />\n<span class="text-red">* Celebratory character weapons will not have featured rates.</span>\n</p>\n\n\n</section>\n\n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Summons Details\n  </h3>\n    <div class="information_table">\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th style="width:10%">\n            Step\n          </th>\n          <th style="width:10%">\n            Type\n          </th>\n          <th style="width:13%">\n            Required Gems\n          </th>\n          <th style="width:67%">\n            Obtainable Shards, Bonuses, and Other\n          </th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            Step 1\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            x10 summons\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/gem_icon.png" width="20%"> 3,000\n          </td>\n          <td>\n<img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/consumable118192_icon.png" width="6%"> Shard (Festive) x10<br> <span class="text-red">Insignia of Skill x2, Advanced Handbook x40</span>\n\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            Step 2\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            x10 summons\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/gem_icon.png" width="20%"> 3,000\n          </td>\n          <td>\n<img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/consumable118192_icon.png" width="6%"> Shards (Festive) x10<br> <span class="text-red">Festive Girl or past Celebratory character</span> is guaranteed in the 10th slot\n\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            Step 3\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            x10 summons\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/gem_icon.png" width="20%"> 3,000\n          </td>\n          </td>\n          <td>\n<img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/consumable118192_icon.png" width="6%"> Shards (Festive) x10 <br><span class="text-red">Festive Girl</span>  guaranteed in the 10th slot<br>\n\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n\n<p>\n</span>\n\n<p>\n* A <span class="text-red">★★★ or above weapon</span> is guaranteed on the 10th summon on Step 1, and a <span class="text-red">Festive Girl or past Celebratory character</span> is guaranteed on the 10th summon on Step 2, a <span class="text-red">Festive Girl</span> is guaranteed on the 10th summon on Step 3. <br />\n* You will proceed through Steps 1-3 in order, and then return to Step 1 after finishing Step 3.<br />\n* The Paid Only: Festive Girl Multi-Step Summons does not have a limit to how many times you can loop back to Step 1.<br />\n* Any bonus you earn will be sent to your gift box.\n</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Summon Shards (Festive)</h3>\n<p>\nYou will earn <span class="text-red">Shards (Festive)</span> every time you use the Paid Only: Festive Girl Multi-Step Summons.<br />\nTrade <span class="text-red">150 Shards (Festive)</span> at the Shard (Festive) Exchange to acquire limited-time characters. New items will be added for exchange <span class="text-red">as each Festive summons period begins</span>.<br />\n<br />\n* The Exchange <span class="text-red">is only available for a limited time.</span> Once the exchange period ends, you will be unable to exchange shards.<br />\n* Once the exchange period ends, each remaining shard <span class="text-red">will be converted into a bookmark</span> upon entering the summons screen.<br />\n* If you exchange for a character weapon you already own, you will earn <span class="text-red">10 ascension materials and 1 Awakening Stone for the character in addition to the weapon</span>.<br />\n* Shards can only be used at the exchange of the same name.<br />\n* Shards earned from both free and paid versions of the <span class="text-red">Festive Girl Summons</span>, <span class="text-red">Festive Hunter Summons</span>, <span class="text-red">Festive Weapon Summons</span>, and <span class="text-red">Festive Monster Summons</span> are the same item.<br />\n\n* Shards earned from both free and paid versions of the <span class="text-red">Reverie''s Garb Summons</span> are <span class="text-red">different items</span>.<br />\n\n* You will also earn shards for summons performed using premium summon tickets (including 10x summon tickets).<br />\n\n<section>\n<h3>Resonant Costume Bonuses in Subjugation Battles</h3>\n<p>\n\nSeason 006 of Subjugation Battles will have a resonant costume quest bonus. The bonus effect of the resonant costumes <span class="text-red">reduces cooldown time for weapon skills in certain Subjugation Battle quests</span> and <span class="text-red">activates an attack increase based on the ascension count</span>.<br />\n</p>\n\n</section>\n<section>\n\n   <div class="information_table weapon_table">\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n\n\n          <th colSpan="5" class="al-center">Ascension Count and Effects</th>\n　　　　　　　　　\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n\n          <th style="width:10%">None</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">1</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">2</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">3</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">4</th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n   　　　　　<tr>\n\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+25%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n+10%<br /></td>\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+30%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n+10%<br /></td>\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+35%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n+10%<br /></td>\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+40%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n+10%<br /></td>\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+50%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n+10%<br /></td>\n\n        </tr>\n         \n\n        <tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n</section>\n<br />\n\n<section>\n<h4>Quest Bonus: Resonant Costume Effect</h4>\n  <div class="information_table powerup_rate_table">\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th>\n            Resonant Costume\n          </th>\n          <th>\n            Quests\n          </th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <th>\n            <img class="chara_image" src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/4cc0cf287f70cdf1938c5469c868f7a30a6dcb1a54ae9d78e7629cbd450a84fe" alt=""> Fio (Festive Girl)\n          </th>\n\n          <td>\n           <span class="text-red">Manifestation: Windy Cursed God</span>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n \n\n    \n\n    </table>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>Event Quest Bonuses</h3>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/5bb839e87224494376cc56fb5bc4e22bb74b1d395565aad0ed2e832a634af83d">\n</div>\n<p>\nThe characters and weapons featured in this summons grant <span class="text-red">quest bonuses</span> in the event quest "Record: Happy Home". Playing the quest with these costumes will activate <span class="text-red">various effects</span>, and some effects will <span class="text-red">increase depending on the ascension count</span>.</span><br />\n<p/>\n<section>\n\n   <div class="information_table weapon_table">\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n\n         \n          <th colSpan="5" class="al-center">Resonant Costume "Festive Girl" Ascension Count Effect</th>\n　　　　　　　　　\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n\n          <th style="width:10%">None</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">1</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">2</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">3</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">4</th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n   　　　　　<tr>\n          \n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+100%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+125%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+150%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+175%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+200%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>\n\n        </tr>\n         \n        <tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n\n<p>\n<br />\n\nIn addition, resonant weapons will have an effect that <span class="text-red">increases the amount of Happy Home Medals dropped</span>.</span><br />\n\n\n<h4> Quest Bonus: Resonance Weapon Effect</h4>\n<div class="information_table weapon_table">\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th rowSpan="2" style="width:28%">Weapon</th>\n<th rowSpan="2" style="width:14%; text-align:center;">Event Tickets</th>\n<th colspan="5" style="text-align:center">Ascension Count</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th style="text-align:center">None</th>\n<th style="text-align:center">1</th>\n<th style="text-align:center">2</th>\n<th style="text-align:center">3</th>\n<th style="text-align:center">4</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n    <tbody>\n      \n\n      <tr>\n        <th><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/848ae4b130de4fb052bf9123a775b2ded35ea163a39d95df984d62840b994508" class="weapon_icon">Jester''s Grin</th>\n        <td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center"><img class="coin_icon" src="/images/en/operations/coin/7a59d1c16765c471ea700f22a996e89c8ad48d8d3f0e96f0bf2601fcd7972a41"><br />\n\n          <img class="coin_icon" src="/images/en/operations/coin/e33c1c76b54eac5cc42a8a835a14638bb94c797e42b3d91532630c6b80353ca6">\n          <img class="coin_icon" src="/images/en/operations/coin/e285379997f716f2520112601d9e40aa1d98356951af0fab1f4bb498e38e5fb4">\n        </td>\n        <td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center">+5</td>\n        <td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center">+11</td>\n        <td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center">+17</td>\n        <td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center">+23</td>\n        <td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center">+30</td>\n      </tr>\n\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div>\n\n<p>\nFor more information on the event quest, check the "Resurrected Event Quest "Record: Happy Home" On Now" notice.\n<p/>\n<div data-category="information" data-informationId="1269" class="other-link-btn common_btn common_button-typeA">Resurrected Event Quest "Record: Happy Home" On Now</div>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Notes\n  </h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n    <ul>\n      <li>\n        Event duration and content are subject to change without notice.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Illustrations shown in notices, etc. may differ from those in-game.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        The rarity, stats, skills, and abilities of characters and weapons displayed on the summons screen and on the official Twitter account are shown at maximum levels.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        "Increased rates" means that the character''s appearance rate is higher than that of other characters of the same rarity.\n      </li>\n<li>\n<span class="text-red">Fio (Festive Girl) &amp; Jester''s Grin will appear in future summons.</span><br />\n</li>\n<li>\n        <span class="text-red">Fio (Festive Girl) &amp; Jester''s Grin will not appear when using ★★★+ Premium Summon Tickets or ★★★★ Premium Summon Tickets.</span>\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        You cannot have more than one character with the same name in the same deck.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        For more information about rates, please check the Rates button on the summons page.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        If you perform a summons using the 10x summon button, a ★★★ or higher weapon will always appear on the 10th summon, regardless of the results of the first 9 summons.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        The video clip that plays when pressing the Skill button was recorded in a development environment.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        The skill introduction video shows the character at level 20 equipped with only a primary weapon at level 1 and all skill levels at level 1.\n      </li>\n            <li>\n        Shards (Festive) can only be used during the exchange period and cannot be carried over to the next event.\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n<br />\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n  </section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/0243e3092802e7d075bc350780ed46948216ca7634290db670f7e005c50f22e3');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1269,0,2,'Resurrected Event Quest "Record: Happy Home" On Now',1691114400000,replace('<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/5bb839e87224494376cc56fb5bc4e22bb74b1d395565aad0ed2e832a634af83d">\n</div>\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n<br />\nThe Resurrected Event Quest <span class="text-red">"Record: Happy Home"</span> has begun as of Aug. 3 18:00 PST.<br />\n<span class="text-red">Event Small Stamina Boost x300</span> have also been gifted to all players.<br />\n\n* Once the event quest ends, you will be unable to claim or use Event Small Stamina Boosts.\n\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>Duration</h3>\n<div class="holding-period">Aug. 3 18:00 - Aug. 17 <span class="text-red">14:59</span> PST</div>\n<p>\n* The Exchange can be used until two days after the event duration ends. Please see the Exchange in game for details.\n</p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>How to Play Event Quests</h3>\n\n<p>\n Save up the <span class="text-red">Happy Home Medal</span> you receive for completing quests to trade in at the <span class="text-red">Happy Home Medal Exchange</span> for the event-exclusive companions as well as enhancements and other items.<br />\n <br>\n The more difficult the quest, the more reward you will earn.<br />\n Additionally, using certain characters, costumes, or weapons while playing this event quest will grant you a <span class="text-red">quest bonus</span> that will allow you to play this event more efficiently.<br>\n <br />\n Note: This event quest will be unlocked upon completing Main Quest Ch. 2.<br>\n</p>\n</section>\n\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Quest Bonus: Resonant Weapon</h3>\n<p>\nEquipping certain weapons while playing the event quests will grant the <span class="text-red">quest bonus for resonant weapons.</span><br>\nThis bonus <span class="text-red">increases the amount of different kinds of Happy Home Medals dropped</span>, depending on the weapon.<br>\nAscending these weapons <span class="text-red">further increases the bonus effect.</span><br>\n<br>\n</p>\n\n\n\n  </div>\n<h4>\n    Quest Bonus: Resonant Weapons Effect List\n  </h4>\n<div class="information_table weapon_table">\n  <table>\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th rowSpan="2" style="width:24%">Weapon</th>\n        <th rowSpan="2" style="width:13%; text-align:center;">Medals</th>\n        <th colSpan="5" style="text-align:center">Ascension Count</th>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <th style="text-align:center">None</th>\n        <th style="text-align:center">1</th>\n        <th style="text-align:center">2</th>\n        <th style="text-align:center">3</th>\n        <th style="text-align:center">4</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n     <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <th><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/1848e70031fa51dd79087b7efb69ba5012eb83a4ec97b8d151b8d23ad9e9cb8f" class="weapon_icon">Blackened Will</th>\n        <td style="text-align:center">\n          <img class="coin_icon" src="/images/en/operations/coin/7a59d1c16765c471ea700f22a996e89c8ad48d8d3f0e96f0bf2601fcd7972a41">\n        </td>\n        <td style="text-align:center">+1</td>\n        <td style="text-align:center">+3</td>\n        <td style="text-align:center">+5</td>\n        <td style="text-align:center">+7</td>\n        <td style="text-align:center">+10</td>\n      </tr>\n     <tr>\n        <th><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/848ae4b130de4fb052bf9123a775b2ded35ea163a39d95df984d62840b994508" class="weapon_icon">Jester''s Grin</th>\n        <td rowSpan="10" style="text-align:center"><img class="coin_icon" src="/images/en/operations/coin/7a59d1c16765c471ea700f22a996e89c8ad48d8d3f0e96f0bf2601fcd7972a41"><br />\n\n          <img class="coin_icon" src="/images/en/operations/coin/e33c1c76b54eac5cc42a8a835a14638bb94c797e42b3d91532630c6b80353ca6">\n          <img class="coin_icon" src="/images/en/operations/coin/e285379997f716f2520112601d9e40aa1d98356951af0fab1f4bb498e38e5fb4">\n        </td>\n        <td rowSpan="1" style="text-align:center">+5</td>\n        <td rowSpan="1" style="text-align:center">+11</td>\n        <td rowSpan="1" style="text-align:center">+17</td>\n        <td rowSpan="1" style="text-align:center">+23</td>\n        <td rowSpan="1" style="text-align:center">+30</td>\n      </tr>\n\n\n     <tr>\n        <th><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/9605c0bd9fa851e991cf47eada202b0b083d05c5b3e369f872055961d3d1831f" class="weapon_icon">Visitor''s Harpoon</th>\n\n        <td rowSpan="6" style="text-align:center">+1</td>\n        <td rowSpan="6" style="text-align:center">+3</td>\n        <td rowSpan="6" style="text-align:center">+5</td>\n        <td rowSpan="6" style="text-align:center">+7</td>\n        <td rowSpan="6" style="text-align:center">+10</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <th><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/5515779a5464a92774436141689022f9a46b3820cb945f604dd162df35a60e26" class="weapon_icon">Mechanical Blade</th>\n      </tr>\n\n      <tr>\n        <th><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/687e3d3100d40e7d76ad1588000820c611648d0fcabf20d7a5a36bcdd349008d" class="weapon_icon">Demon''s Duality</th>\n  </tr>\n\n\n\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div>\n\n<p>\n* Equipping resonant weapons will grant you this bonus regardless of whether they are equipped as primary or secondary weapons.<br>\n* Resonant weapon drop increases will stack if multiple resonant weapons are equipped.\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>Quest Bonus: Resonant Costume</h3>\n\n<p>\n\nUsing certain costumes will grant the <span class="text-red">quest bonus for resonant costumes</span>.<br />\nThese bonuses activate <span class="text-red">various effects</span> for associated costumes when playing the event quests. Plus, some bonuses will have <span class="text-red">increased effects depending on the ascension count</span> of a costume.<br /><br />\n</p>\n\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h4>Quest Bonus: Resonant Costumes Effect List</h4>\n  <div class="information_table powerup_rate_table">\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n<tr>\n <th>Resonant Costume Characters</th><th>Effect</th>\n</tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <th>\nPriyet<br />  \n</th><td rowSpan="1" style="text-align:center">Attack＋50%</td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n  <div class="information_table weapon_table">\n  <table>\n   <thead>\n    <tr>\n\n     \n     <th colSpan="5" class="al-center">Resonant Costume "Festive Girl" Ascension Count Effect</th>\n　　　　　　　　　\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n\n     <th style="width:10%">None</th>\n     <th style="width:10%">1</th>\n     <th style="width:10%">2</th>\n     <th style="width:10%">3</th>\n     <th style="width:10%">4</th>\n    </tr>\n   </thead>\n   <tbody>\n  　　　　　<tr>\n     \n     <td>Attack<span class="text-red">＋100%</span><br />HP＋50%<br /></td>\n     <td>Attack<span class="text-red">＋125%</span><br />HP＋50%<br /></td>\n     <td>Attack<span class="text-red">＋150%</span><br />HP＋50%<br /></td>\n     <td>Attack<span class="text-red">＋175%</span><br />HP＋50%<br /></td>\n     <td>Attack<span class="text-red">＋200%</span><br />HP＋50%<br /></td>\n\n    </tr>\n     \n    <tr>\n   </tbody>\n  </table>\n </div>\n </section>\n\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Selected Costumes and Resonant Weapons Enhancement Glorious Success Rate Tripled</h3>\n\n\n<p>\n<span class="text-red">The chance of getting a "Glorious Success" result will be tripled</span> when upgrading resonant weapons and <span class="text-red">Priyet</span> and <span class="text-red">Fio</span>''s costumes.<br>\n<br>\n* Excess materials and weapons used in enhancement will be returned if the maximum level is exceeded.<br />\n* This campaign''s effects do not stack with other "Glorious Success" rate up campaigns.<br />\n</p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Mama Point Missions</h3>\n<p>\nCompleting missions will earn you <span class="text-red">Mama Points</span>.<br />\nCheck the Special tab on the Missions page for details.<br />\n</p>\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>        \nFestive Girl Summons</h3>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/e30967cda39f508c156ca9e5ac7133153c972b653d30d3be5d4018eeeb3f4d04">\n</div>\n<br />\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/995f4c1a1d3f0c1b81dd582b6cf03a56f8f04545febc711772476d706040111b">\n</div>\n<br />\n\n<p>\nAug. 3 18:00 - Aug. 10 17:59 PST, the Festive Girl Summons, Paid Only: Festive Girl Multi-Step Summons will be available with <span class="text-red">increased appearance rates for costumes and weapons that grant quest bonuses in "Record: Happy Home"</span>.<br />\nPlease check the corresponding notices for more details on these summons.<br>\n</p>\n<div data-category="information" data-informationId="1267" class="other-link-btn common_btn common_button-typeA">"Festive Girl Summons" On Now</div>\n<div data-category="information" data-informationId="1268" class="other-link-btn common_btn common_button-typeA">"Paid Only: Festive Girl Multi-Step Summons" On Now</div>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Notes\n  </h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n    <ul>\n\n \n<li>\n        Event duration and content are subject to change without notice.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Illustrations shown in notices, etc. may differ from those in-game.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        The rarity, stats, skills, and abilities of characters and weapons displayed in notices, in the summons screen, and on the official Twitter account are shown at maximum levels.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        You cannot have more than one character with the same name in the same deck.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        "Increased rates" means that the character''s appearance rate is higher than that of other characters of the same rarity.\n      </li>\n  <li>\n  <span class="text-red">Priyet(Celebratory Werebeast) and Blackened Will may reappear in the future.</span>\n  </li>\n      <li>\n        Once the exchange period has passed, <span class="text-red">you will be unable to exchange medals</span>.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Event-specific medals can only be used during the exchange period and <span class="text-red">cannot be carried over to the next event.</span>\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        This event may reappear in the future.\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<br>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/5f95ac265aab93ca58664ce71522091fe96c2d4570f8bbf0f97ffd665f48b6a9');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1275,0,3,'Festive Hunter Summons On Now',1691719200000,replace('<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/575a4a7888844ed43aea105a2446c2f585c58e31dfd9ea967050613ec08506b9">\n</div>\n\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n<br />\n\nThe <span class="text-red">Festive Hunter Summons</span> is available as of Aug. 10 18:00 PST.<br />\nThe new featured character <span class="text-red">Gayle (Festive Hunter)</span> <span class="text-red">will have the Karma feature</span> after the Aug. 17 PST update.\n</p>\n\n<section>\n<h3>New Costume Series: Festive Summons</h3>\n<p>\nThe summons are scheduled as follows. Paid Only summons will be available at the same time.\n</p>\n<br />\n\n\n<h4>Festive Girl Summons</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nAug. 3 18:00 - Aug. 10 17:59 PST\n</div>\n\n\n<h4><span class="text-red">Festive Hunter Summons</span></h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\n<span class="text-red">Aug. 10 18:00 - Aug. 17 14:59 PST</span>\n</div>\n\n\n<h4>Festive Weapon Summons</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nAug. 17 18:00 - Aug. 24 17:59 PST\n</div>\n\n\n<h4>Festive Monster Summons</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nAug. 24 18:00 - Aug. 31 17:59 PST\n</div>\n\n\n<h4>Reverie''s Garb Summons (all 4 new costumes listed above will appear)</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nAug. 31 18:00 - Sep. 10 17:59 PST\n</div>\n<br /><br />\n\n\n\n<p>\nSummon shard summons and exchange periods are as follows.\n</p>\n<br />\n\n\n<h4>Summon Shards (Festive) Exchange</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nAug. 3 18:00 - Sep. 2 17:59 PST\n</div>\n<p>\n・ Shards (Festive) can be obtained from the <span class="text-red">Festive Girl Summons</span>, <span class="text-red">Festive Hunter Summons</span>, <span class="text-red">Festive Weapon Summons</span>, and <span class="text-red">Festive Monster Summons</span>.<br />・ Exchangeable weapons will be added <span class="text-red">as each summons period begins</span>.\n\n\n\n<br /><br />\n\n<h4>Summon Shards (Reverie''s Garb) Exchange</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nAug. 31 18:00 - Sep. 12 17:59 PST\n</div>\n<p>\n・ Shards (Reverie''s Garb) can be obtained from the <span class="text-red">Reverie''s Garb Summons</span>.\n</p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n<section>\n\n<h3>Limited-time Characters &amp; Weapons</h3>\n<p>In this summons, the <span class="text-red">following limited-time characters have featured rates</span>.<br />\n\n\n\nInformation on stats, skills, and abilities can be found on the summons screen.</p>\n\n<h4>Limited-Time Characters</h4>\n<p>\n<img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/></p>\n\n<p><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/a3d9b1ca15fb529592b8b9c8db37b868813c4912cdb642212ca1d2f474f7ac68" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Gayle (Festive Hunter)<br />\n* You can get this character by acquiring the <span class="text-red">Falling Petals</span> weapon.</p>\n<br />\n\n\n<h4>Limited-Time Weapons</h4>\n<p><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/></p>\n\n<p><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/8e7921c10098f49d517d61dd80464b8845a1358bd4bf7e602ac416b0535b9498" class="weapon_icon" width="6%">Falling Petals<br /></p>\n\n<br />\n<p>\nIn addition, weapons that come with the previously appearing Celebratory costume series characters will reappear in this summons. For more information, please check Rates on the summons page.<br /><br />\n<span class="text-red">* Celebratory character weapons will not have featured rates.</span>\n</p>\n\n\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Summons Details\n  </h3>\n    <div class="information_table">\n    <table style="width:58%">\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th style="width:6%">\n            Type\n          </th>\n          <th style="width:12%">\n            Required Gems\n          </th>\n          <th style="width:40%">\n            Obtainable Shards (Festive)\n          </th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            1x summons\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/gem_icon.png" width="20%"> 300\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/consumable118192_icon.png" width="6%"> 1\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            10x summons\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/gem_icon.png" width="20%"> 3,000\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/consumable118192_icon.png" width="6%"> 10\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n\n<p>\n<span class="text-red">At least one ★★★ or higher weapon is guaranteed</span> in each <span class="text-red">10x summon</span>.<br />\n* You will also earn the appropriate number of shards (Festive) for summons performed using premium summon tickets (including 10x summon tickets).\n</p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Summon Shards (Festive)</h3>\n<p>\nYou will earn <span class="text-red">Shards (Festive)</span> every time you use the Festive Hunter Summons.<br />\nTrade <span class="text-red">150 Shards (Festive)</span> at the Shard (Festive) Exchange to acquire limited-time characters. New items will be added for exchange <span class="text-red">as each Festive summons period begins</span>.<br />\n<br />\n* The Exchange <span class="text-red">is only available for a limited time.</span> Once the exchange period ends, you will be unable to exchange shards.<br />\n* Once the exchange period ends, each remaining shard <span class="text-red">will be converted into a bookmark</span> upon entering the summons screen.<br />\n* If you exchange for a character weapon you already own, you will earn <span class="text-red">10 ascension materials and 1 Awakening Stone for the character in addition to the weapon</span>.<br />\n* Shards can only be used at the exchange of the same name.<br />\n* Shards earned from both free and paid versions of the <span class="text-red">Festive Girl Summons</span>, <span class="text-red">Festive Hunter Summons</span>, <span class="text-red">Festive Weapon Summons</span>, and <span class="text-red">Festive Monster Summons</span> are the same item.<br />\n\n* Shards earned from both free and paid versions of the <span class="text-red">Reverie''s Garb Summons</span> are <span class="text-red">different items</span>.<br />\n\n* You will also earn shards for summons performed using premium summon tickets (including 10x summon tickets).<br />\n\n<section>\n<h3>Resonant Costume Bonuses in Subjugation Battles</h3>\n<p>\n\nSeason 006 of Subjugation Battles will have a resonant costume quest bonus. The bonus effect of the resonant costumes <span class="text-red">reduces cooldown time for weapon skills in certain Subjugation Battle quests</span> and <span class="text-red">activates an attack increase based on the ascension count</span>.<br />\n</p>\n\n</section>\n<section>\n\n   <div class="information_table weapon_table">\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n\n\n          <th colSpan="5" class="al-center">Ascension Count and Effects</th>\n　　　　　　　　　\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n\n          <th style="width:10%">None</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">1</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">2</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">3</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">4</th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n   　　　　　<tr>\n\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+25%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n+10%<br /></td>\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+30%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n+10%<br /></td>\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+35%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n+10%<br /></td>\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+40%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n+10%<br /></td>\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+50%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n+10%<br /></td>\n\n        </tr>\n         \n\n        <tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n</section>\n<br />\n\n<section>\n<h4>Quest Bonus: Resonant Costume Effect</h4>\n  <div class="information_table powerup_rate_table">\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th>\n            Resonant Costume\n          </th>\n          <th>\n            Quests\n          </th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <th>\n            <img class="chara_image" src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/a3d9b1ca15fb529592b8b9c8db37b868813c4912cdb642212ca1d2f474f7ac68" alt=""> Gayle (Festive Hunter)\n          </th>\n\n          <td>\n           <span class="text-red">Manifestation: Soggy Cursed God</span>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n \n\n    \n\n    </table>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>Event Quest Bonuses</h3>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/5bb839e87224494376cc56fb5bc4e22bb74b1d395565aad0ed2e832a634af83d">\n</div>\n<p>\nThe characters and weapons featured in this summons grant <span class="text-red">quest bonuses</span> in the event quest "Record: Happy Home". Playing the quest with these costumes will activate <span class="text-red">various effects</span>, and some effects will <span class="text-red">increase depending on the ascension count</span>.</span><br />\n<p/>\n<section>\n\n   <div class="information_table weapon_table">\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n\n         \n          <th colSpan="5" class="al-center">Resonant Costume "Festive Hunter" Ascension Count Effect</th>\n　　　　　　　　　\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n\n          <th style="width:10%">None</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">1</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">2</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">3</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">4</th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n   　　　　　<tr>\n          \n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+100%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+125%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+150%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+175%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+200%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>\n\n        </tr>\n         \n        <tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n\n<p>\n<br />\n\nIn addition, resonant weapons will have an effect that <span class="text-red">increases the amount of Happy Home Medals dropped</span>.</span><br />\n\n\n<h4> Quest Bonus: Resonance Weapon Effect</h4>\n<div class="information_table weapon_table">\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th rowSpan="2" style="width:28%">Weapon</th>\n<th rowSpan="2" style="width:14%; text-align:center;">Event Tickets</th>\n<th colspan="5" style="text-align:center">Ascension Count</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th style="text-align:center">None</th>\n<th style="text-align:center">1</th>\n<th style="text-align:center">2</th>\n<th style="text-align:center">3</th>\n<th style="text-align:center">4</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n    <tbody>\n      \n\n      <tr>\n        <th><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/8e7921c10098f49d517d61dd80464b8845a1358bd4bf7e602ac416b0535b9498" class="weapon_icon">Falling Petals</th>\n        <td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center"><img class="coin_icon" src="/images/en/operations/coin/7a59d1c16765c471ea700f22a996e89c8ad48d8d3f0e96f0bf2601fcd7972a41"><br />\n\n          <img class="coin_icon" src="/images/en/operations/coin/e33c1c76b54eac5cc42a8a835a14638bb94c797e42b3d91532630c6b80353ca6">\n          <img class="coin_icon" src="/images/en/operations/coin/e285379997f716f2520112601d9e40aa1d98356951af0fab1f4bb498e38e5fb4">\n        </td>\n        <td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center">+5</td>\n        <td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center">+11</td>\n        <td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center">+17</td>\n        <td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center">+23</td>\n        <td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center">+30</td>\n      </tr>\n\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div>\n\n<p>\nFor more information on the event quest, check the "Resurrected Event Quest "Record: Happy Home" On Now" notice.\n<p/>\n<div data-category="information" data-informationId="1269" class="other-link-btn common_btn common_button-typeA">Resurrected Event Quest "Record: Happy Home" On Now</div>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Notes\n  </h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n    <ul>\n      <li>\n        Event duration and content are subject to change without notice.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Illustrations shown in notices, etc. may differ from those in-game.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        The rarity, stats, skills, and abilities of characters and weapons displayed on the summons screen and on the official Twitter account are shown at maximum levels.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        "Increased rates" means that the character''s appearance rate is higher than that of other characters of the same rarity.\n      </li>\n<li>\n<span class="text-red">Gayle (Festive Hunter) &amp; Falling Petals will appear in future summons.</span><br />\n</li>\n<li>\n        <span class="text-red">Gayle (Festive Hunter) &amp; Falling Petals will not appear when using ★★★+ Premium Summon Tickets or ★★★★ Premium Summon Tickets.</span>\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        You cannot have more than one character with the same name in the same deck.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        For more information about rates, please check the Rates button on the summons page.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        If you perform a summons using the 10x summon button, a ★★★ or higher weapon will always appear on the 10th summon, regardless of the results of the first 9 summons.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        The video clip that plays when pressing the Skill button was recorded in a development environment.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        The skill introduction video shows the character at level 20 equipped with only a primary weapon at level 1 and all skill levels at level 1.\n      </li>\n            <li>\n        Shards (Festive) can only be used during the exchange period and cannot be carried over to the next event.\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n<br />\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n  </section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/123b952c5d058525cdea32a369717f9c7ab355a8ff8fbdd35a023c7166991e4f');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1276,0,3,'Paid Only: Festive Hunter Multi-Step Summons On Now',1691719200000,replace('<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/9cb2bfd9acdf205080ebb3e58788f7a830f65c61a366aeb3621383dced368c46">\n</div>\n\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n<br />\n\nThe <span class="text-red">Paid Only: Festive Hunter Multi-Step Summons</span> is available as of Aug. 10 18:00 PST.<br />\nThe new featured character <span class="text-red">Gayle (Festive Hunter)</span> <span class="text-red">will have the Karma feature</span> after the Aug. 17 PST update.\n</p>\n\n<section>\n<h3>New Costume Series: Festive Summons</h3>\n<p>\nThe summons are scheduled as follows. Paid Only summons will be available at the same time.\n</p>\n<br />\n\n\n<h4>Festive Girl Summons</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nAug. 3 18:00 - Aug. 10 17:59 PST\n</div>\n\n\n<h4><span class="text-red">Festive Hunter Summons</span></h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\n<span class="text-red">Aug. 10 18:00 - Aug. 17 14:59 PST</span>\n</div>\n\n\n<h4>Festive Weapon Summons</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nAug. 17 18:00 - Aug. 24 17:59 PST\n</div>\n\n\n<h4>Festive Monster Summons</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nAug. 24 18:00 - Aug. 31 17:59 PST\n</div>\n\n\n<h4>Reverie''s Garb Summons (all 4 new costumes listed above will appear)</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nAug. 31 18:00 - Sep. 10 17:59 PST\n</div>\n<br /><br />\n\n\n\n<p>\nSummon shard summons and exchange periods are as follows.\n</p>\n<br />\n\n\n<h4>Summon Shards (Festive) Exchange</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nAug. 3 18:00 - Sep. 2 17:59 PST\n</div>\n<p>\n・ Shards (Festive) can be obtained from the <span class="text-red">Festive Girl Summons</span>, <span class="text-red">Festive Hunter Summons</span>, <span class="text-red">Festive Weapon Summons</span>, and <span class="text-red">Festive Monster Summons</span>.<br />・ Exchangeable weapons will be added <span class="text-red">as each summons period begins</span>.\n\n\n\n<br /><br />\n\n<h4>Summon Shards (Reverie''s Garb) Exchange</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nAug. 31 18:00 - Sep. 12 17:59 PST\n</div>\n<p>\n・ Shards (Reverie''s Garb) can be obtained from the <span class="text-red">Reverie''s Garb Summons</span>.\n</p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n<section>\n\n<h3>Limited-time Characters &amp; Weapons</h3>\n<p>In this summons, the <span class="text-red">following limited-time characters have featured rates</span>.<br />\n\n\n\nInformation on stats, skills, and abilities can be found on the summons screen.</p>\n\n<h4>Limited-Time Characters</h4>\n<p>\n<img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/></p>\n\n<p><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/a3d9b1ca15fb529592b8b9c8db37b868813c4912cdb642212ca1d2f474f7ac68" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Gayle (Festive Hunter)<br />\n* You can get this character by acquiring the <span class="text-red">Falling Petals</span> weapon.</p>\n<br />\n\n\n<h4>Limited-Time Weapons</h4>\n<p><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/></p>\n\n<p><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/8e7921c10098f49d517d61dd80464b8845a1358bd4bf7e602ac416b0535b9498" class="weapon_icon" width="6%">Falling Petals<br /></p>\n\n<br />\n<p>\nIn addition, weapons that come with the previously appearing Celebratory costume series characters will reappear in this summons. For more information, please check Rates on the summons page.<br /><br />\n<span class="text-red">* Celebratory character weapons will not have featured rates.</span>\n</p>\n\n\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Summons Details\n  </h3>\n    <div class="information_table">\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th style="width:10%">\n            Step\n          </th>\n          <th style="width:10%">\n            Type\n          </th>\n          <th style="width:13%">\n            Required Gems\n          </th>\n          <th style="width:67%">\n            Obtainable Shards, Bonuses, and Other\n          </th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            Step 1\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            x10 summons\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/gem_icon.png" width="20%"> 3,000\n          </td>\n          <td>\n<img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/consumable118192_icon.png" width="6%"> Shard (Festive) x10<br> <span class="text-red">Insignia of Skill x2, Advanced Handbook x40</span>\n\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            Step 2\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            x10 summons\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/gem_icon.png" width="20%"> 3,000\n          </td>\n          <td>\n<img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/consumable118192_icon.png" width="6%"> Shards (Festive) x10<br> <span class="text-red">Festive Hunter or past Celebratory character</span> is guaranteed in the 10th slot\n\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            Step 3\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            x10 summons\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/gem_icon.png" width="20%"> 3,000\n          </td>\n          </td>\n          <td>\n<img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/consumable118192_icon.png" width="6%"> Shards (Festive) x10 <br><span class="text-red">Festive Hunter</span>  guaranteed in the 10th slot<br>\n\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n\n<p>\n</span>\n\n<p>\n* A <span class="text-red">★★★ or above weapon</span> is guaranteed on the 10th summon on Step 1, and a <span class="text-red">Festive Hunter or past Celebratory character</span> is guaranteed on the 10th summon on Step 2, a <span class="text-red">Festive Hunter</span> is guaranteed on the 10th summon on Step 3. <br />\n* You will proceed through Steps 1-3 in order, and then return to Step 1 after finishing Step 3.<br />\n* The Paid Only: Festive Hunter Multi-Step Summons does not have a limit to how many times you can loop back to Step 1.<br />\n* Any bonus you earn will be sent to your gift box.\n</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Summon Shards (Festive)</h3>\n<p>\nYou will earn <span class="text-red">Shards (Festive)</span> every time you use the Paid Only: Festive Hunter Multi-Step Summons.<br />\nTrade <span class="text-red">150 Shards (Festive)</span> at the Shard (Festive) Exchange to acquire limited-time characters. New items will be added for exchange <span class="text-red">as each Festive summons period begins</span>.<br />\n<br />\n* The Exchange <span class="text-red">is only available for a limited time.</span> Once the exchange period ends, you will be unable to exchange shards.<br />\n* Once the exchange period ends, each remaining shard <span class="text-red">will be converted into a bookmark</span> upon entering the summons screen.<br />\n* If you exchange for a character weapon you already own, you will earn <span class="text-red">10 ascension materials and 1 Awakening Stone for the character in addition to the weapon</span>.<br />\n* Shards can only be used at the exchange of the same name.<br />\n* Shards earned from both free and paid versions of the <span class="text-red">Festive Girl Summons</span>, <span class="text-red">Festive Hunter Summons</span>, <span class="text-red">Festive Weapon Summons</span>, and <span class="text-red">Festive Monster Summons</span> are the same item.<br />\n\n* Shards earned from both free and paid versions of the <span class="text-red">Reverie''s Garb Summons</span> are <span class="text-red">different items</span>.<br />\n\n<section>\n<h3>Resonant Costume Bonuses in Subjugation Battles</h3>\n<p>\n\nSeason 006 of Subjugation Battles will have a resonant costume quest bonus. The bonus effect of the resonant costumes <span class="text-red">reduces cooldown time for weapon skills in certain Subjugation Battle quests</span> and <span class="text-red">activates an attack increase based on the ascension count</span>.<br />\n</p>\n\n</section>\n<section>\n\n   <div class="information_table weapon_table">\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n\n\n          <th colSpan="5" class="al-center">Ascension Count and Effects</th>\n　　　　　　　　　\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n\n          <th style="width:10%">None</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">1</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">2</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">3</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">4</th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n   　　　　　<tr>\n\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+25%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n+10%<br /></td>\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+30%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n+10%<br /></td>\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+35%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n+10%<br /></td>\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+40%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n+10%<br /></td>\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+50%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n+10%<br /></td>\n\n        </tr>\n         \n\n        <tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n</section>\n<br />\n\n<section>\n<h4>Quest Bonus: Resonant Costume Effect</h4>\n  <div class="information_table powerup_rate_table">\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th>\n            Resonant Costume\n          </th>\n          <th>\n            Quests\n          </th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <th>\n            <img class="chara_image" src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/a3d9b1ca15fb529592b8b9c8db37b868813c4912cdb642212ca1d2f474f7ac68" alt=""> Gayle (Festive Hunter)\n          </th>\n\n          <td>\n           <span class="text-red">Manifestation: Soggy Cursed God</span>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n \n\n    \n\n    </table>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>Event Quest Bonuses</h3>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/5bb839e87224494376cc56fb5bc4e22bb74b1d395565aad0ed2e832a634af83d">\n</div>\n<p>\nThe characters and weapons featured in this summons grant <span class="text-red">quest bonuses</span> in the event quest "Record: Happy Home". Playing the quest with these costumes will activate <span class="text-red">various effects</span>, and some effects will <span class="text-red">increase depending on the ascension count</span>.</span><br />\n<p/>\n<section>\n\n   <div class="information_table weapon_table">\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n\n         \n          <th colSpan="5" class="al-center">Resonant Costume "Festive Hunter" Ascension Count Effect</th>\n　　　　　　　　　\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n\n          <th style="width:10%">None</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">1</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">2</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">3</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">4</th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n   　　　　　<tr>\n          \n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+100%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+125%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+150%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+175%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>\n          <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+200%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>\n\n        </tr>\n         \n        <tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n\n<p>\n<br />\n\nIn addition, resonant weapons will have an effect that <span class="text-red">increases the amount of Happy Home Medals dropped</span>.</span><br />\n\n\n<h4> Quest Bonus: Resonance Weapon Effect</h4>\n<div class="information_table weapon_table">\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th rowSpan="2" style="width:28%">Weapon</th>\n<th rowSpan="2" style="width:14%; text-align:center;">Event Tickets</th>\n<th colspan="5" style="text-align:center">Ascension Count</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th style="text-align:center">None</th>\n<th style="text-align:center">1</th>\n<th style="text-align:center">2</th>\n<th style="text-align:center">3</th>\n<th style="text-align:center">4</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n    <tbody>\n      \n\n      <tr>\n        <th><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/8e7921c10098f49d517d61dd80464b8845a1358bd4bf7e602ac416b0535b9498" class="weapon_icon">Falling Petals</th>\n        <td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center"><img class="coin_icon" src="/images/en/operations/coin/7a59d1c16765c471ea700f22a996e89c8ad48d8d3f0e96f0bf2601fcd7972a41"><br />\n\n          <img class="coin_icon" src="/images/en/operations/coin/e33c1c76b54eac5cc42a8a835a14638bb94c797e42b3d91532630c6b80353ca6">\n          <img class="coin_icon" src="/images/en/operations/coin/e285379997f716f2520112601d9e40aa1d98356951af0fab1f4bb498e38e5fb4">\n        </td>\n        <td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center">+5</td>\n        <td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center">+11</td>\n        <td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center">+17</td>\n        <td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center">+23</td>\n        <td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center">+30</td>\n      </tr>\n\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div>\n\n<p>\nFor more information on the event quest, check the "Resurrected Event Quest "Record: Happy Home" On Now" notice.\n<p/>\n<div data-category="information" data-informationId="1269" class="other-link-btn common_btn common_button-typeA">Resurrected Event Quest "Record: Happy Home" On Now</div>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Notes\n  </h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n    <ul>\n      <li>\n        Event duration and content are subject to change without notice.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Illustrations shown in notices, etc. may differ from those in-game.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        The rarity, stats, skills, and abilities of characters and weapons displayed on the summons screen and on the official Twitter account are shown at maximum levels.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        "Increased rates" means that the character''s appearance rate is higher than that of other characters of the same rarity.\n      </li>\n<li>\n<span class="text-red">Gayle (Festive Hunter) &amp; Falling Petals will appear in future summons.</span><br />\n</li>\n<li>\n        <span class="text-red">Gayle (Festive Hunter) &amp; Falling Petals will not appear when using ★★★+ Premium Summon Tickets or ★★★★ Premium Summon Tickets.</span>\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        You cannot have more than one character with the same name in the same deck.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        For more information about rates, please check the Rates button on the summons page.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        If you perform a summons using the 10x summon button, a ★★★ or higher weapon will always appear on the 10th summon, regardless of the results of the first 9 summons.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        The video clip that plays when pressing the Skill button was recorded in a development environment.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        The skill introduction video shows the character at level 20 equipped with only a primary weapon at level 1 and all skill levels at level 1.\n      </li>\n            <li>\n        Shards (Festive) can only be used during the exchange period and cannot be carried over to the next event.\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n<br />\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n  </section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/9d81a6025590c1f6ad1b2879b5b1bb945fb33379dcf99cc147b4186ff900ae5d');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1288,0,1,'Dust Weapon Series Added',1692324000000,replace('<section>\n<p>\n Hello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\n This is a message from the management team.<br />\n</p>\n<p>\nThe following weapons have been added for arena medal exchange on Aug. 17.\n</p>\n<h3>Affected Weapons</h3>\n</div><p>\nSword of Dust<br />\nGreatsword of Dust<br />\nStaff of Dust<br />\nSpear of Dust<br />\nKnuckles of Dust<br />\nPistol of Dust<br />\n</p>\n\n\n<h4>Stat Details</h4>\n<section>\n  <div class="pickup_weapon-content">\n    <div class="chara_image" style="background-image:url(/images/en/operations/weapon/1c0a8b93352c171e59bd20a97e60076b421c36b58739390282465547b3774529)">\n      <div class="pickup_character-chara_image_area">\n        <div class="chara_profile">\n          <div class="chara_rarity"><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star" /><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star" /><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star" /><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star" /><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star" /></div>\n          <div class="item_name"><img class="weapon_icon" src="/images/common/icon/attribute_icon_2.png" /><img class="weapon_icon" src="/images/common/icon/weapon_icon_1.png" />Sword of Dust</div>\n          <div class="right_icon_1"><img class="weapon_icon" src="/images/common/icon/weapon_awaken_icon.png" /></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class="pickup_character-status_area">\n        <div class="type-a">\n          <h5>Status</h5>\n          <ul>\n            <li><img class="status_icon" src="/images/common/icon/status_hp_icon_white.png" />HP <span class="status-value">31295</span></li>\n            <li><img class="status_icon" src="/images/common/icon/status_attack_icon_white.png" />Attack <span class="status