e x10</span></td>\n     </tr>\n        \n     <tr>\n        <td><span class="text-red">Ruby x10</span></td>\n     </tr>\n\n     <tr>\n        <td><span class="text-red">Tanzanite x10</span></td>\n     </tr>\n\n      <tr>\n        <td><span class="text-red">Gold x70,000</span></td>\n     </tr>\n\n      <tr>\n        <td>Growth Agent x10</td>\n     </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Secret Growth Agent x10</td>\n     </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Curing Agent x10</td>\n     </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Potent Curing Agent x10</td>\n     </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Enhancement Agent x10</td>\n     </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Rare Enhancement Agent x10</td>\n     </tr>      <tr>\n        <td>Elongator x10</td>\n     </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>High-quality Elongator x10</td>\n     </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Active Agent x10</td>\n     </tr>      <tr>\n        <td>Superior Active Agent x10</td>\n     </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Refining Agent x10</td>\n     </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Valuable Refining Agent x10</td>\n     </tr>\n\n\n      </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div>\n\n</section>\n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Notes\n  </h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n    <ul>\n      <li>\nThis content is subject to change without notice.\n      </li>\n\n      <li>\n        Quests that can be played only once a day reset at midnight every day.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Quest clear counts are determined based on the time you start the quest. If you start a quest before 0:00 and it passes 0:00 during the quest, your clear count will count for the previous day and not the new day.\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<br>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/5c2831946405f5432e9ebd0644ec48c6143f391593ef5c16d9e60df0ab64377e','/images/en/operations/banner/4f1305a8b0b37ab2ff52e9c4306eed022bc96994ec55be32d101c153d1368f15');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1302,0,7,'Shop Medal Exchange Updated',1692345600000,replace('<p>\n Hello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation. <br />\n This is a message from the management team.<br />\n <br />\nThe <span class="text-red">Shop Medal Exchange</span> was updated on Aug. 18 0:00 PST.<br />\n\n</p>\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Update Details</h3>\n<p>The following characters have been added for shop medal exchange.</p>\n\n<h4>Character</h4>\n<p>\n<img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/095ea6ad6cc491d68a4928ddba03b7ec0ba3e175f9c3b652d771fbde8fca8537" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Priyet(Shadowbound Werebeast)<br />\n<img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/591b971899c3d9fe68e688f7a38979bc4d7543e7f00ea7b579c46cb6f686abe9" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Hina(Abstract Pupil)<br />\n<img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/f9c1291a506e23858c8f2d04cf8e060d133952793ed3155d7680e4da92a01881" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Sarafa(Abstract Belle)<br />\n<img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/e3ed8c59b581da7111d63d14b2bc51c6c780cac0f38abf4ed878f3c5e8f87821" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Marie(Fractured Songstress)<br />\n<img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/7cb785e7b565d30143adbed4f20981353677d19ee503788870519d31eb4009f5" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Dimos(Bloodless Gunman)<br />\n<img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/90f07dd0075125b9d29e418ec7f255ff2af43efbc6686c8022c77d6589207ca4" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Argo(Shadowbound Traveler)<br />\n</p>\n</section>\n \n <section>\n <p>\n Thank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n </p>\n </section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1367,0,5,'Regarding the Issue in ''The People and the World'' New Chapter',1695866400000,replace('<section>\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br>\n<br>\nAs of Sep. 27 18:00 PST, we have confirmed the following issues with the new chapter addition of The People and the World.\n</p>\n<h3>Known Issues</h3>\n<p>\n・In Story 5 of The People and the World Overture III: Emerald, some icons may not be tappable<br>\n<br>\n・In Story 5 of The People and the World Overture III: Emerald, there may be a wait time that makes skipping impossible.<br>\n<br>\n<br>\nWe are currently working on finding out the cause of the issues and appreciate your patience and understanding.<br />\n<br>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),1689832800000,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1387,0,7,'Arena Season 031 On Now',1696903200000,replace('<section>\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation. <br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n<br />\nArena <span class="text-red">Season 031</span> of the Arena was made available starting Oct. 9 18:00 PST.\n</p>\n\n\n\n\n<h3>Starting Arena Point</h3>\n<p>\nPlayers'' starting Arena Points will change depending on their <span class="text-red">total force.</span><br />\nThis is applicable to players who began playing the Arena prior to Oct. 15 23:59 PST and reached over a specific total force.<br />\n</p>\n   <div class="information_table weapon_table">\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n\n          <th style="width:10%">Total Force</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">Starting Arena Points</th>\n\n\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n   　　　　　<tr>\n          <td>320,000 or over</td>\n          <td>36,000</td>\n        </tr>\n\n   　　　　　<tr>\n          <td>220,000 and over, but under 320,000</td>\n          <td>29,000</td>\n        </tr>\n\n   　　　　　<tr>\n          <td>120,000 and over, but under 220,000</td>\n          <td>22,000</td>\n        </tr>\n\n   　　　　　<tr>\n          <td>Under 120,000</td>\n          <td>18,000</td>\n        </tr>\n\n        <tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n<p>\nNote: As long as you have completed the <span class="text-red">"Reach XXXX total force"</span> mission in the challenge tab, your total force will be counted even if your current loadout has a lower total force.<br />\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>Duration</h3>\n<p>Season 031 will be open during the following period.</p>\n<br />\n<div class="holding-period">Oct. 9 18:00 - Nov. 5 23:59 PST</div>\n</section>\n\n\n</p>\n<section>\n<h3>Notes</h3>\n<div class="attention_content">\n<ul>\n<li>Event duration and content are subject to change without notice.</li>\n<li>If you do not participate in the Arena, you may not receive the Arena weekly rewards.</li>\n<li>If a battle goes past 0:00 on Monday, Arena Points will not be awarded for that battle.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n<br />\n<section>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1429,0,7,'Game Balance Notice for "Recollections of Dusk"',1699236000000,replace('<section>\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation. <br />\nThis is a message from the management team. <br />\n<br />\nIn order to provide a better gaming experience for players, we will be adjusting the game balance for some aspects of <span class="text-red">Recollections of Dusk</span> on Nov. 19 18:00 PST.\n<br/></div>\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Recollections of Dusk Maintenance Period</h3>\n<div class="holding-period">Nov. 12 17:00 - Nov. 19 17:59 PST</div>\n\n<p>\n* The maintenance period is subject to change without notice.</br>\n* If you have an active "Recollections of Dusk" challenge when maintenance begins, <span class="text-red">your Chamber of Dusk attempt clear status will be reset after the maintenance</span>.</br>\n* The Chambers of Dusk quests you have already cleared will not be.</br>\n* The issue that forces players back to the title screen after the maintenance announcement appears if they were in one of the Chambers of Dusk and cleared a quest or subquest.<br />\n* For "Recollections of Dusk" other than Dimos, you can challenge them as usual.\n</p>\n\n</section>\n\n<p>\n<h3>Adjustment Details</h3>\n</p>\n\n<p>\n<h4>Applies to:</h4>\n</p>\n\n    <div class="information_table">\n    <table style="width:20%">\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th rowSpan="1" style="width:20%; text-align:center">\n            Recollections of Dusk\n          </th>\n         \n      </thead>\n      <tbody>       \n <tr>\n          <td>\nFrozen-Heart Automaton\n          </td>\n\n        </tr>\n\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n\n<p>\n\n<h4>Frozen-Heart Automaton Details</h4>\n\n</p>\n</section>\n\n    <div class="information_table">\n    <table style="width:100%">\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th colspan="1" style="width:20%; text-align:center">Adjustments</th>\n\n          <th colspan="1" style="width:40%; text-align:center">Before Adjustments</th>\n\n          <th colspan="1" style="width:40%; text-align:center">After Adjustments</th>\n\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            Central Door<br/>Other Quests\n          </td>\n\n          <td>\n            For each battle:<br/>Loadout designated characters\n          </td>\n\n          <td>\n            For each battle:<br />Loadout 1-2 costumes of proficient affinity\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            Quests inside the Chamber\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            Weapons used to complete quests can<br />now be loaded out in the same level\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            Weapons used to complete quests cannot<br />be loaded out in the same level\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n\n\n<p>\n* If you have an active "Recollections of Dusk" challenge when maintenance begins, <span class="text-red">your Chamber of Dusk attempt clear status will be reset</span>.</br>\n* The Chambers of Dusk quests you have already cleared will not be.</br>\n</p>\n\n\n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Notes\n  </h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n    <ul>\n\n   <li>\n        Duration and content are subject to change without notice.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Illustrations shown in notices, etc. may differ from those in-game.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n       The Recollections of Frozen-Heart Contractor, Frozen-Heart Beast, and Recollections of Dusk are scheduled to be adjusted over time.\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1500,0,7,'Required Materials for Karma Flux Adjustment',1701828000000,replace('<section>\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.</p>\n<section>\n\n\n<p>\nFrom Dec. 7 18:00 PST, the balance of the number of materials required for Karma Flux will be adjusted in consideration of the current item possession, acquisition, and consumption status.<br>\n\n\n</p>\n\n\n<h3>Adjusted Content</h3>\n<p>\nBefore Adjustments</br>\n・XL Character Enhancement x300</br>\n・XL Weapon Enhancement x100</br>\n・Small Slab Fragment x50</br>\n・Medium Slab Fragment x10</br>\n・Weapon-evolution materials x1</br>\n</br>\nAfter Adjustments</br>\n・XL Character Enhancement x<span class="text-red">150</span></br>\n・XL Weapon Enhancement x<span class="text-red">75</span></br>\n・Small Slab Fragment x<span class="text-red">30</span></br>\n・Medium Slab Fragment x10</br>\n・Weapon-evolution materials x1</br>\n\n</p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n</br>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1576,0,7,'Game Balance Notice for "Recollections of Dusk"',1705197600000,replace('<section>\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation. <br />\nThis is a message from the management team. <br />\n<br />\nIn order to provide a better gaming experience for players, we will be adjusting the game balance for some aspects of <span class="text-red">Recollections of Dusk</span> on Jan. 14 18:00 PST.\n<br/></div>\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Recollections of Dusk Maintenance Period</h3>\n<div class="holding-period">Jan. 14 17:00 - 17:59 PST</div>\n\n<p>\n* The maintenance period is subject to change without notice.</br>\n* If you have an active "Recollections of Dusk" challenge when maintenance begins, <span class="text-red">your Chamber of Dusk attempt clear status will be reset after the maintenance</span>.</br>\n* The Chambers of Dusk quests you have already cleared will not be.</br>\n* The issue that forces players back to the title screen after the maintenance announcement appears if they were in one of the Chambers of Dusk and cleared a quest or subquest.<br />\n* For "Recollections of Dusk" other than Levania, you can challenge them as usual.<br>\n<br>\n</p>\n\n</section>\n\n<p>\n<h3>Adjustment Details</h3>\n</p>\n\n<p>\n<h4>Applies to:</h4>\n</p>\n\n    <div class="information_table">\n    <table style="width:20%">\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th rowSpan="1" style="width:20%; text-align:center">\n            Recollections of Dusk\n          </th>\n         \n      </thead>\n      <tbody>       \n <tr>\n          <td>\nFrozen-Heart Beast\n          </td>\n\n        </tr>\n\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n\n<p>\n\n<h4>Frozen-Heart Beast Details</h4>\n\n</p>\n</section>\n\n    <div class="information_table">\n    <table style="width:100%">\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th colspan="1" style="width:20%; text-align:center">Adjustments</th>\n\n          <th colspan="1" style="width:40%; text-align:center">Before Adjustments</th>\n\n          <th colspan="1" style="width:40%; text-align:center">After Adjustments</th>\n\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            Central Door<br/>Other Quests\n          </td>\n\n          <td>\n            For each battle:<br/>Loadout designated characters\n          </td>\n\n          <td>\n            For each battle:<br />Loadout 1-2 costumes of proficient affinity\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            Quests inside the Chamber\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            Weapons used to complete quests cannot<br />now be loaded out in the same level\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            Weapons used to complete quests can<br />be loaded out in the same level\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n\n\n<p>\n* If you have an active "Recollections of Dusk" challenge when maintenance begins, <span class="text-red">your Chamber of Dusk attempt clear status will be reset</span>.</br>\n* The Chambers of Dusk quests you have already cleared will not be.</br>\n</p>\n\n\n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Notes\n  </h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n    <ul>\n\n   <li>\n        Duration and content are subject to change without notice.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Illustrations shown in notices, etc. may differ from those in-game.\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1582,0,5,'Issues Regarding the Karma Flux Effect of Abyssal Songstress',1705056600000,replace('<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br>\nThis is a message from the management team.<br>\n<br>\nWe have confirmed the following issue with Marie (Abyssal Songstress)''s Karma Flux effect, which was added on Jan. 11 PST.<br>\nThe issue has been resolved as of Jan. 12 2:00 PST.\n</p>\n\n<h3>Issue Details</h3>\n<p>\nMarie (Abyssal Songstress) did not include "Agility up by 50% for 60 seconds" which should have been included in the Karma: III slot, as well as the ★★★★ and ★★★ effects.\n</p>\n\n\n<h3>Corrections</h3>\n<p>\nThe effect <span class="text-red">"Agility up by 50% for 60 seconds"</span> and the corresponding ★★★ and ★★ effects have been added to the effects that Marie (Abyssal Songstress) can obtain in the Karma: III slot.<br>\n* There will be no change in the appearance rate of the ★★★★ effect and the ★★★ effect respectively.<br>\n* Only the appearance rate of the ★★ effect, which can be obtained in the Karma: III slot, has been changed and allocated to the appearance rate of the ★★★★ effect and the ★★ effect, which will be added to the list.<br>\n<br>\nWe apologize for any inconvenience this may cause.<br>\n<br>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>','\n',char(10)),NULL,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1587,0,4,'Story Completion Countdown Campaign On Now',1705975200000,replace('<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/10fbff56c7981ef729c89bf9f66d65e679091e3b5e77239341f568f87a7aaa25">\n</div>\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.  <br />\nThis is a message from the management team. <br />\n<br />\nThe <span class="text-red">Story Completion Countdown Campaign</span> has begun as of Jan. 22 18:00 PST.\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>Story Completion Countdown Campaign List</h3>\n<section>\n<h4>Story Completion Countdown Login Bonus</h4>\n\n\n<div class="holding-period">\nJan. 23 0:00 - Mar. 28 23:59 PST\n</div>\n<p>\n <p>\n Get <span class="text-red">Premium Summon Ticket</span> from a new login bonus.<br>\n </p>\n <div class="information_table">\n  <table>\n  <tbody>\n  <tr>\n  <th width="120">Day</td>\n  <th>Rewards</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n  <td>Day 1</td>\n  <td>Premium Summon Ticket x1</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n  <td>Day 2</td>\n  <td>Premium Summon Ticket x1</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n  <td>Day 3</td>\n  <td>Premium Summon Ticket x1</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n  <td>Day 4</td>\n  <td><span class="text-red">Premium Summon Ticket x2</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n  <td>Day 5</td>\n  <td>Premium Summon Ticket x1</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n  <td>Day 6</td>\n  <td>Premium Summon Ticket x1</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n  <td>Day 7</td>\n  <td><span class="text-red">Premium Summon Ticket x3</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  </table>\n </div>\n <p>\n* You can receive login bonuses by going to Mama''s Room or The Cage.<br />\n* Login resets at 0:00 PST every day.<br />\n* You can retrieve your rewards by logging in during the period until Apr. 29  PST.<br>\n</p>\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<h4>Story Completion Countdown every week Gift</h4>\n<p>\n<span class="text-red">Gems</span> will be gifted to all players.\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<div class="information_table">\n  <table>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <th width="300">Duration</td>\n        <th>Details</td>\n      </tr>\n    <tbody><tr><td>Jan. 22 18:00 - Feb. 2 23:59</td><td>Gem x3,000</td></tr></tbody>\n    <tbody><tr><td>Feb. 2 0:00 - Feb. 12 23:59</td><td>Gem x3,000</td></tr></tbody>\n    <tbody><tr><td>Feb. 9 0:00 - Feb. 19 23:59</td><td>Gem x3,000</td></tr></tbody>\n    <tbody><tr><td>Feb. 17 18:00 - Feb. 28 23:59</td><td>Gem <span class="text-red">x5,000</span></td></tr></tbody>\n    <tbody><tr><td>Feb. 23 0:00 - Mar. 4 23:59</td><td>Gem <span class="text-red">x5,000</span></td></tr>\n    <tbody><tr><td>Mar. 1 0:00 - Mar. 11 23:59</td><td>Gem x3,000</td></tr>\n    <tbody><tr><td>Mar. 8 0:00 - Mar. 18 23:59</td><td>Gem x3,000</td></tr>\n    <tbody><tr><td>Mar. 15 0:00 - Mar. 25 23:59</td><td>Gem x3,000</td></tr>\n    <tbody><tr><td>Mar. 22 0:00 - Apr. 1 23:59</td><td>Gem x3,000</td></tr>\n\n  </table>\n</div>\n</section><br>\n\n\n<section>\n<h4>Story Completion Countdown Missions</h4>\n<p>\nYou can earn the following items based on the stamina you consume during the period.\n</p>\n\n<div class="information_table">\n  <table>\n    <tbody>\n    　<tr><th colspan="2">Duration：Jan. 22 18:00 - Feb. 1 23:59 PST</td></tr>\n      <tr><th>Missions</td><th>Rewards</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 500 stamina in total</td><td>Insignia of Quality x4</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 1,000 stamina in total</td><td>Insignia of Quality x8</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 2,000 stamina in total</td><td>Insignia of Quality x8</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 3,000 stamina in total</td><td>Insignia of Quality x8</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 4,000 stamina in total</td><td>Insignia of Quality x8</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 5,000 stamina in total</td><td>Insignia of Quality x20</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 7,500 stamina in total</td><td>Insignia of Quality x12</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 10,000 stamina in total</td><td>Insignia of Quality x12</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 13,000 stamina in total</td><td>Insignia of Quality x40</td></tr>\n      </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div>\n\n<div class="information_table">\n  <table>\n    <tbody>\n    　<tr><th colspan="2">Duration：Feb. 2 0:00 - Feb. 8 23:59 PST</td></tr>\n      <tr><th>Missions</td><th>Rewards</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 500 stamina in total</td><td>Insignia of Skill x1</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 1,000 stamina in total</td><td>Insignia of Skill x1</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 2,000 stamina in total</td><td>Insignia of Skill x2</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 3,000 stamina in total</td><td>Insignia of Skill x2</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 4,000 stamina in total</td><td>Insignia of Skill x2</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 5,000 stamina in total</td><td>Insignia of Skill x3</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 7,500 stamina in total</td><td>Insignia of Skill x2</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 10,000 stamina in total</td><td>Insignia of Skill x2</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 13,000 stamina in total</td><td>Insignia of Skill x5</td></tr>\n      </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class="information_table">\n  <table>\n    <tbody>\n    　<tr><th colspan="2">Duration：Feb. 9 0:00 - Feb. 15 23:59 PST</td></tr>\n      <tr><th>Missions</td><th>Rewards</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 500 stamina in total</td><td>Dark Karma Stone x10</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 1,000 stamina in total</td><td>Dark Karma Stone x20</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 2,000 stamina in total</td><td>Dark Karma Stone x20</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 3,000 stamina in total</td><td>Dark Karma Stone x20</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 4,000 stamina in total</td><td>Dark Karma Stone x20</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 5,000 stamina in total</td><td>Dark Karma Stone x50<