l x8</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 5,000 stamina in total</td><td>Black Pearl x20</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 7,500 stamina in total</td><td>Black Pearl x12</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 10,000 stamina in total</td><td>Black Pearl x12</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 13,000 stamina in total</td><td>Black Pearl x40</td></tr>\n      </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div>\n\n<div class="information_table">\n  <table>\n    <tbody>\n    　<tr><th colspan="2">Duration：Mar. 1 0:00 - Mar. 7 23:59 PST</td></tr>\n      <tr><th>Missions</td><th>Rewards</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 500 stamina in total</td><td>Advanced Handbook x10</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 1,000 stamina in total</td><td>Advanced Handbook x10</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 2,000 stamina in total</td><td>Advanced Handbook x20</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 3,000 stamina in total</td><td>Advanced Handbook x20</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 4,000 stamina in total</td><td>Advanced Handbook x30</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 5,000 stamina in total</td><td>Advanced Handbook x100</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 7,500 stamina in total</td><td>Advanced Handbook x30</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 10,000 stamina in total</td><td>Advanced Handbook x30</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 13,000 stamina in total</td><td>Advanced Handbook x150</td></tr>\n      </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div>\n\n<div class="information_table">\n  <table>\n    <tbody>\n    　<tr><th colspan="2">Duration：Mar. 8 0:00 - Mar. 14 23:59 PST</td></tr>\n      <tr><th>Missions</td><th>Rewards</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 500 stamina in total</td><td>Adamant x10</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 1,000 stamina in total</td><td>Adamant x20</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 2,000 stamina in total</td><td>Adamant x20</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 3,000 stamina in total</td><td>Adamant x20</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 4,000 stamina in total</td><td>Adamant x20</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 5,000 stamina in total</td><td>Adamant x50</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 7,500 stamina in total</td><td>Adamant x30</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 10,000 stamina in total</td><td>Adamant x30</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 13,000 stamina in total</td><td>Adamant x100</td></tr>\n      </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div>\n\n<div class="information_table">\n  <table>\n    <tbody>\n    　<tr><th colspan="2">Duration：Mar. 15 0:00 - Mar. 29 23:59 PST</td></tr>\n      <tr><th>Missions</td><th>Rewards</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 500 stamina in total</td><td>Verse of Truth x1</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 1,000 stamina in total</td><td>Verse of Truth x2</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 2,000 stamina in total</td><td>Verse of Truth x2</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 3,000 stamina in total</td><td>Verse of Truth x2</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 4,000 stamina in total</td><td>Verse of Truth x3</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 5,000 stamina in total</td><td>Verse of Truth x10</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 7,500 stamina in total</td><td>Verse of Truth x5</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 10,000 stamina in total</td><td>Verse of Truth x5</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Clear quests using 13,000 stamina in total</td><td>Verse of Truth x20</td></tr>\n      </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div>\n\n\n\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<br>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>\nNotes\n</h3>\n<div class="attention_content">\n<ul>\n<li>\nCampaign duration and content are subject to change without notice.\n</li>\n<li>\nThis campaign and its content may reappear in the future.\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<br />\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/10fbff56c7981ef729c89bf9f66d65e679091e3b5e77239341f568f87a7aaa25','/images/en/operations/banner/60e20849baa319c5e1d5e2befb230fceb2dd75fcfb6251866163820a18ecb429');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1590,0,7,'In-Game: What''s to Come',1705975200000,replace('<section>\n<p>\n<span class="text-red">Update: Feb. 5 0:20 PST</span><br />\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.  <br />\nThis is a message from the management team. <br />\n<br />\nThere are no Summons currently available in which Premium Summon Tickets can be used.<br />\nIt will be possible to use them in the Raiments of Rebirth Summons starting Feb. 17 and Abstract *** Summons starting Mar. 7 until the end of app service.<br />\n<br />\nWe apologize for any inconveniences.\n</p>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation. </p>\n<hr style="border:0;border-top:1px solid #423B3A;"><br>\n</section>\n\n\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.  <br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n</br>\nWe would like to inform you about future plans for NieR Re[in]carnation so that you can enjoy the time until service ends on Apr. 29 22:00 PST.\n</br></p>\n\n<h3>Pre-End of Service Events &amp; Campaigns</h3>\n<p>\nTo allow players to enjoy your time until service ends on Apr. 29 22:00 PST, we are planning various events such as the Story Completion Countdown Event and the Japanese 3rd Anniversary Campaign.</br>\nFor more details, please refer to the respective event or campaign notice.</br>\n</p>\n</br>\n<div class="information_table">\n    <table style="width:100%">\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th style="width:10%" rowspan="2">\n            Duration\n          </th>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <th style="width:20%">\n            Event\n          </th>\n\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n\n      <tbody>\n\n        <tr>\n          <td>Jan. 22 18:00 - Apr. 1 23:59 PST</td>\n          <td>Story Completion Countdown Event</td>       \n\n        <tr>\n\n          <td>Jan. 22 18:00 - Feb. 4 23:59 PST</td>\n          <td>New Chapter Campaign</td>\n\n        <tr>\n          <td>Feb. 1 18:00 - Feb. 17 23:59 PST</td>\n          <td>Japanese 3rd Anniversary Countdown Campaign</td>\n\n        <tr>\n          <td>Feb. 17 18:00 - Mar. 7 23:59 PST</td>\n          <td>Japanese 3rd Anniversary Campaign</td>\n\n        <tr>\n          <td>Mar. 7 18:00 - Mar. 28 23:59 PST</td>\n          <td>Final Chapter Release Countdown Campaign</td>\n\n        <tr>\n          <td>Mar. 28 18:00 - Apr. 29 21:59 PST</td>\n          <td>Story Completion Event</td>\n\n    </table>\n\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n\n\n<h3>In-Game Content Updates</h3>\n<h4>Main Story</h4>\n<p>\nNieR Re[in]carnation will conclude with The People and the World Act III: Transmigration. Act III: Transmigration is scheduled to be released on Mar. 28 18:00 PST.\n</br>\n</p>\n\n<h4>Record/Variation Event Quests</h4>\n<p>\nThe schedule for the Record and Variation event quests that will be held after Jan. 22 18:00 PST is as follows.</br>\nAdditionally, from Feb. 8 18:00 PST, the Countdown Resurrected Event Medal Exchange, a shared Exchange for all resurrected Record events, will be added at the same time.</br>\n</p>\n</br>\n<div class="information_table">\n    <table style="width:100%">\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th style="width:5%" rowspan="2">\n            Duration\n          </th>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <th style="width:15%">\n            Event Quests\n          </th>\n\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n           Jan. 30 18:00 - Feb. 17 17:59 PST\n          </td>\n          <td>\n             <span class="text-red">Variation: Blazing Binding Oculus (New Event)</span>\n          </td>\n       \n         \n          \n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            Feb. 8 18:00 - Feb. 25 17:59 PST\n          </td>\n       \n                 <td rowspan="1">\n           Record: Garden of Benediction (Resurrected Event)\n          </td>\n   </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            Feb. 17 18:00 - Apr. 29 21:59 PST\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <span class="text-red">Record: The Cage of Rebirth (New Event)</span>\n          </td>\n       \n    \n    </tr>\n\n\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            Feb. 22 18:00 - Mar. 10 17:59 PST\n          </td>\n          <td>\n           Record: Foundation of Fortune (Resurrected Event)\n          </td>\n   \n  </tr>\n\n          <td>\n            Feb. 28 18:00 - Mar. 17 17:59 PST\n          </td>\n          <td>\n              Record: Happy Home (Resurrected Event)\n          </td>\n \n       \n<tr>\n          <td>\n             Mar. 7 18:00 - Apr. 29 21:59 PST\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            Record: Eternal Steps (Resurrected Event)\n          </td>\n   \n\n        </tr>\n       \n<tr>\n          <td>\n             Mar. 14 18:00 - Apr. 29 21:59 PST\n          </td>\n          <td>\n          Record: Ritual of Reverie (Resurrected Event)\n          </td>\n\n\n  </tr>\n\n \n          \n        </tr>\n\n    </table>\n  </div>\n<p>\n\n* Resurrected Record Event Quests will <span class="text-red">start in the same uncleared state for all players</span>, regardless of whether previous runs of these events were cleared.<br />\n* For more information on exchanges and quests, please see the in-game notices as they are updated.\n</p>\n\n<h4>Countdown Resurrected Event Medal Exchange</h4>\n<p>\nFrom Feb. 8 18:00 PST, a Countdown Resurrected Event Medal Exchange will be added where you can exchange for characters, weapons, companions, and memoirs from past Record and Variation event quests.</br>\n\n\nCountdown Resurrected Event Medals can be obtained from all resurrected Record event quests starting from Feb. 8.</br>\n* See the Exchange in game for details on the items available.</br>\n</br>\n</p>\n\n<h4>Adjustments to Reward Amount from Daily Missions</h4>\n<p>\nDue to the end of item sales in the Premium Shop, we will adjust the amount of Skip Tickets that can be obtained from daily missions starting Jan. 23 0:00 PST.</br>\n</p>\n<div class="information_table">\n    <table style="width:100%">\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th style="width:5%" rowspan="2">\n            Mission\n          </th>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <th style="width:10%">\n            Rewards (before change)\n          </th>\n          <th style="width:10%">\n           Rewards (after change)\n          </th>\n\n      \n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n\n      <tbody>\n          \n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            Clear quests 5 times\n          </td>\n          <td>\n           Skip Ticket x50\n          </td>\n                 <td rowspan="1">\n            <span class="text-red">Skip Ticket x100</span>\n          </td>\n\n\n\n    </table>\n  </div>\n\n\n</br>\n\n<h4>Mama Point Missions</h4>\n<p>\nIn order to make it easier to obtain Remnants, we are planning to hold a campaign where you can earn double the monthly Mama Points, starting February.</br>\n\nWe are also planning to hold a campaign that halves the number of Mama Points required to acquire any Remnant in the Mama Point Exchange.\n</br>\n* For details, please check the in-game notice that will be posted at a later date.\n</p>\n\n\n<h4>Recollections of Dusk Quests</h4>\n<p>\nRecollections of Dusk Quests for Argo (Frozen-Heart Adventurer) will release as of Feb. 8 18:00 PST.</br>\nThis will be the final update for Recollections of Dusk.</br>\n</br>\n</p>\n\n\n<h4>Subjugations</h4>\n<p>\nSeason 008, which started Nov. 13 18:00 PST, will be the final season, and will be extended until Apr. 29 21:59.\n\n<section>\n\n<div class="information_table">\n    <table style="width:100%">\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th style="width:5%" rowspan="2">\n            Duration\n          </th>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <th style="width:10%">\n            Season\n          </th>\n\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n           Nov. 13 18:00 - Apr. 29 21:59 PST\n          </td>\n          <td>\n             Season 008\n          </td>\n       \n    </table>\n  </div>\n</p>\n<h4>Arena</h4>\n<p>\nThe Arena will be open according to the following schedule.</br>\nAdditionally, Arena Season 037, which will be held from Feb. 19 18:00, will be the final update.\n<div class="information_table">\n    <table style="width:100%">\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th style="width:5%" rowspan="2">\n            Duration\n          </th>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <th style="width:10%">\n            Season\n          </th>\n\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n           Jan. 22 18:00 - Feb. 18 23:59 PST\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            Season 036\n          </td>       \n\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n           Feb. 19 18:00 - Mar. 31 23:59 PST\n          </td>\n          <td>\n             Season 037\n          </td>\n\n      \n    </table>\n\n  </div>\n</section>\n<p>\n* For more information on each season, please see the in-game notices as they are updated.\n</p>\n\n</br>\n<h4>Fate Boards</h4>\n<p>\nFate Board: Ternary, released on Jan. 18 18:00 PST, will be the last stage added.</br>\n* After Feb, 1 18:00 PST, both Fate Board: Ternary and Fate Board: Shadow will be permanently available. For details, please check the notice that will be posted at a later date.\n\n</p>\n</br>\n\n<h4>Library Stories</h4>\n<p>\nWe plan to make all event stories and card stories available for reading on Mar. 28 18:00 PST so that players can enjoy as many stories as possible. (* Excluding crossover quest)<br>\n</br>\n</p>\n\n<h3>Summons Schedule</h3>\n<p>\nThe schedule for summons that will be held after Jan. 22 18:00 PST is as follows.</br>\n</p>\n<div class="information_table">\n    <table style="width:100%">\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th style="width:5%" rowspan="2">\n            Duration\n          </th>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <th style="width:15%">\n            Summons\n          </th>\n          <th style="width:10%">\n           Featured Characters\n          </th>\n\n      \n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n\n      <tbody>\n   <tr>\n          <td>\n            Jan. 28 18:00 - <br>Feb. 11 17:59 PST\n          </td>\n           <td>\n           Recollections of Dusk Resonant Characters Guaranteed <br>Frozen-Heart Inmate Conquest Summons\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            5 Recollections of Dusk Frozen-Heart Inmate Resonant Characters\n          </td>\n   </tr>\n\n\n\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n           Feb. 1 18:00 - <br>Mar. 29 23:59 PST\n          </td>\n          <td>\n              Story Completion Countdown <br>Limited-Time Character Festival Summons Vol. 1\n          </td>\n          <td rowspan="1">\n            For more information on the summons, check the notice to be published at a later date.\n          </td>\n         \n          \n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            Feb. 1 18:00 - <br>Mar. 29 23:59 PST\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            Story Completion Countdown <br>Limited-Time Character Festival Summons Vol. 2\n          </td>\n                 <td rowspan="1">\n            For more information on the summons, check the notice to be published at a later date.\n          </td>\n   </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            Feb. 1 18:00 - <br>Mar. 29 23:59 PST\n          </td>\n          <td>\n             Story Completion Countdown <br>Limited-Time Character Festival Summons Vol. 3\n          </td>\n              <td rowspan="1">\n            For more information on the summons, check the notice to be published at a later date.\n          </td>\n    \n    </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            Feb. 8 18:00 - <br>Mar. 29 23:59 PST\n          </td>\n          <td>\n           Recollections of Dusk Resonant Characters Guaranteed <br>Frozen-Heart Adventurer Conquest Summons\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            5 Recollections of Dusk Frozen-Heart Adventurer Resonant Characters\n          </td>\n  </tr>\n\n             <tr>\n          <td>\n            Feb. 17 18:00 - <br>Apr. 29 21:59 PST\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            Raiments of Rebirth Summons\n          </td>\n          <td rowspan="1">\n           <span class="text-red">3 New Festive Characters</span>\n          </td>\n          </tr>\n       \n<tr>\n          <td>\n             Feb. 17 18:00 - <br>Apr. 29 21:59 PST\n          </td>\n          <td>\n             Paid-Only Japanese 3rd Anniversary<br>Multi-Step Summons\n          </td>\n          <td rowspan="1">\n            <span class="text-red">3 New Festive Characters</span>\n          </td>\n           </tr>\n        </tr>\n       \n<tr>\n          <td>\n             Mar. 7 18:00 - <br>Apr. 29 21:59 PST\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            Abstract *** Summons\n          </td>\n          <td rowspan="1">\n           <span class="text-red">New Character Costume</span>\n          </td>\n\n  </tr>\n                <tr>\n          <td>\n            Mar. 7 18:00 - <br>Apr. 29 21:59 PST\n          </td>\n          <td>\n             Paid-Only Abstract *** <br>Multi-Step Summons\n          </td>\n          <td rowspan="1">\n           <span class="text-red">New Character Costume</span>\n          </td>　\n </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            Mar. 28 18:00 - <br>Apr. 29 21:59 PST\n          </td>\n          <td>\n             Story Completion <br>Limited-Time Character Festival Summons Vol. 1\n          </td>\n              <td rowspan="1">\nSummer, Yuletide, or New Year''s Costumes\n          </td>\n    \n    </tr>\n\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            Mar. 28 18:00 - <br>Apr. 29 21:59 PST\n          </td>\n          <td>\n             Story Completion <br>Limited-Time Character Festival Summons Vol. 2\n          </td>\n              <td rowspan="1">\nAbyssal or Devine Costumes\n          </td>\n    \n    </tr>\n\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            Mar. 28 18:00 - <br>Apr. 29 21:59 PST\n          </td>\n          <td>\n             Story Completion <br>Limited-Time Character Festival Summons Vol. 3\n          </td>\n              <td rowspan="1">\nCelebratory or Festive Costumes\n          </td>\n    \n    </tr>\n\n\n\n        </tr>\n\n    </table>\n  </div>\n<p>\n* Paid-only summons will only include summons where newly added costumes will appear.</br>\n* More details on each summons will be provided in a subsequent announcement.</br>\n</p>\n\n<section>\n  <h3>Notes</h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n    <ul>\n      <li> Duration and content are subject to change without notice.</br></br></li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),1707121200000,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1591,0,7,'[Important] End of Service Announcement',1705975200000,replace('<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.</br>　\n</br>\n\nWe regret to inform you that NieR Re[in]carnation will be ending service with the conclusion of The People and the World.</br>\n</br>\nThe final chapter of The People and the World is planned to release Mar. 28, 2024. The game will run for a month following the final chapter''s release until Apr. 29, 2024 22:00 PST when service will officially end.</br>\n</br>\nWe would like to express our deepest gratitude to our players for your patronage over the three years since we launched on July 28, 2021. <br>\nUntil the end of service, we will continue to add content and characters, as well as hold various events and campaigns, so we hope you will continue to enjoy NieR Re[in]carnation until the end.</br>\n</p>\n\n<h3>Schedule Until the End of Service</h3>\n<h4>End of Service Announcement (this announcement)</h4>\n<p>\nJan. 22, 2024 18:00 PST </br>\n</p>\n\n<h4>End of Gems Sale (as of this announcement)</h4>\n<p>\nJan. 22, 2024 18:00 PST</br>\n* You will still be able to use gems you currently own until service ends.\n</p>\n\n<h4>Story Completion Countdown Event</h4>\n<p>\nJan. 22, 2024 18:00 - Mar. 29, 2024 23:59 PST</br>\n</p>\n<h4>The People and the World Final Chapter Countdown Stream</h4>\n<p>\nAround early March</br>\n</p>\n<h4>Story Completion Event</h4>\n<p>\nMar. 28, 2024 18:00 - Apr. 29, 2024 21:59 PST</br>\n</p>\n<h4>End of Service</h4>\n<p>\nApr. 29, 2024 22:00 PST</br>\n* We plan to continue updating in-game events until end of service.</br>\n</p>\n\n<h3>About Special Gift Roulette</h3>\n<p>\nSpecial Gift Roulette has ended.<br>\nNot available after Jan. 22 18:00 PST.<br>\n</p>\n\n<h3>Operation Plans for NieR Re[in]carnation</h3>\n\n<h4>In-Game Campaigns and Events</h4>\n<p>\nIn-game campaigns and events will continue to be held so that you can enjoy every moment until service ends on Apr. 29, 2024 at 22:00 PST.</br>\nWe are planning various events such as the Story Conclusion Countdown Event and the Japanese 3rd Anniversary Celebration Campaign.</br>\n</br>\n* Details of new chapters, events, and campaigns will be announced separately when they are added.</br>\n</br>\nWe hope you will continue to enjoy NieR Re[in]carnation until service officially ends on Apr. 29, 2024 PST.</br>\n</br>\n\n\nJan. 22, 2024</br>\nNieR Re[in]carnation Management Team</br>\n</p>','\n',char(10)),NULL,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1592,0,3,'Story Completion Countdown Once per day x10 Free Summons On Now',1705975200000,replace('<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/bfc3699fad9b9a5937e0371fa230d55c91f20d8b3f645868ecdcfa93b415c0b0">\n</div>\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n<br />\nThe <span class="text-red">Story Completion Countdown Once per day x10 Free Summons</span> opened on Jan. 23 0:00 PST.<br />\nDuring the period, you can use the x10 summons for free per day.\n</p>\n\n<section>\n<h3>Duration</h3>\n<div class="holding-period">\nJan. 23 0:00 - Feb. 1 23:59 PST\n</div>\n<p>*All ★★★★ weapons (w/ character) summoned for the duration will be <span class="text-red">Summer</span> costumes.\n</p>\n<br>\n<br>\n\n<div class="holding-period">\nFeb. 2 0:00 - Feb. 8 23:59 PST\n</div>\n<p>*All ★★★★ weapons (w/ character) summoned for the duration will be <span class="text-red">Celebratory</span> costumes.\n</p>\n<br>\n<br>\n<div class="holding-period">\nFeb. 9 0:00 - Feb. 15 23:59 PST\n</div>\n<p>*All ★★★★ weapons (w/ character) summoned for the duration will be <span class="text-red">Abyssal</span> costumes.\n</p>\n<br>\n<br>\n<div class="holding-period">\nFeb. 16 0:00 - Feb. 22 23:59 PST\n</div>\n<p>*All ★★★★ weapons (w/ character) summoned for the duration will be <span class="text-red">Festive</span> costumes.\n</p>\n<br>\n<br>\n<div class="holding-period">\nFeb. 23 0:00 - Feb. 29 23:59 PST\n</div>\n<p>*All ★★★★ weapons (w/ character) summoned for the duration will be <span class="text-red">Divine</span> costumes.\n</p>\n<br>\n<br>\n<div class="holding-period">\nMar. 1 0:00 - Mar. 7 23:59 PST\n</div>\n<p>*All ★★★★ weapons (w/ character) summoned for the duration will be <span class="text-red">Yuletide</span> costumes.\n</p>\n<br>\n<br>\n<div class="holding-period">\nMar. 8 0:00 - Mar. 14 23:59 PST\n</div>\n<p>*All ★★★★ weapons (w/ character) summoned for the duration will be <span class="text-red">New Year''s</span> costumes.\n</p>\n<br>\n<br>\n<div class="holding-period">\nMar. 15 0:00 - Mar. 29 23:59 PST\n</div>\n<p>*All ★★★★ weapons (w/ character) summoned for the duration will be <span class="text-red">the past 7 weeks</span> costumes.\n</p>\n</section>\n                                                \n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Notes\n  </h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n    <ul>\n      <li>\n        Duration and content are subject to change without notice.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Illustrations shown in notices, etc. may differ from those in-game.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        The rarity, stats, skills, and abilities of characters and weapons displayed on the summons screen and on the official X account are shown at maximum levels.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        You cannot have more than one character with the same name in the same deck.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        For more information about rates, please check the Rates button on the summons page.\n      </li>\n<li>\n      <span class="text-red">There are no featured characters or weapons in this summons.</span>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n<br />\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/bfc3699fad9b9a5937e0371fa230d55c91f20d8b3f645868ecdcfa93b415c0b0','/images/en/operations/banner/9b9fde71b83487b7e1affdd16397745a87828592ace827926f69fd7544d80ef6');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1597,0,4,'Mama Point Update',1706666400000,replace('<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/fdc48fed255c98cd12549f1c6a1d0067a721fa22580b7c631d726e5f3dfabaa2">\n</div>\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.  <br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n<br />\nThe <span class="text-red">Mama Point</span> have updated on Jan. 30 18:00 PST.<br>\nThis campaign can get 100% more Mama Points from missions and halve the cost of exchanging Remnants.<br>\nMama Point Missions willl updated on Feb. 1 0:00 PST.<br>\nMission rewards that have been cleared but not yet claimed when <span class="text-red">Mama Point Missions</span> are updated will not be available after the update. Please claim rewards before then.<br>\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>Added Remnants</h3>\n<p>\nRemnants: A Chance Meeting XIV will be added to the Exchange on Feb. 1 0:00 PST. Check the Mama Points Exchange for more information.</p>\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>How to Play Mama Point Missions</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>\n<span class="text-red">Mama Points</span> are special points that can be earned by completing missions.<br />\nSave up Mama Points to trade in for <span class="text-red">Remnants</span>, <span class="text-red">Premium Summons Ticket x10</span>, and other items.<br />\n<span class="text-red">Excluding Remnants</span>, the items at the Exchange will refresh every 1st of the month at 0:00 PST.<br />\nMore Remnants will be added to the Exchange at a later date.<br /><br /></p>\n\n<h4>About Remnants</h4>\n<p>\nAcquiring Remnants will raise the stats of the corresponding character.<br />\nWhile they come at a high cost, Remnant boosts apply to all your acquired costumes for one character.<br />\n<br />\n\n* View your acquired Remnants on the Important tab in View List/Sell or in Extra Stories in the Library.<br />\n* You can acquire <span class="text-red">up to 3,500</span> Mama Points per month. For this reason, <span class="text-red">you may not be able to trade for all the items at the Exchange</span>.<br />\n* Mama Point Missions will take the place of previously held Mama Medal Marathons.<br />\n\n<br />\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>Mama Point Missions</h3>\n<p>\nMama Points can be earned by completing missions related to the Arena, Subjugation Battles, events, and more. Event-related missions will be added when each event opens.<br />\n* Please check the Special tab on the Missions page for details.<br />\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Notes\n  </h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n      <li>\n        Duration and content are subject to change without notice.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Some of the items in the Exchange will <span class="text-red">refresh the 1st of every month at 0:00 PST</span>.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Mama Points will not expire and can be used during any month.</span>\n      </li>\n</span>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n<br />\n</section>\n\n\n\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/fdc48fed255c98cd12549f1c6a1d0067a721fa22580b7c631d726e5f3dfabaa2','/images/en/operations/banner/3492e45864b191e11da8a8d273abac84edfaec11169a41a041908fcc1f7deb66');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1601,0,2,'Event Quest "Fate Board" On Now',1706839200000,replace('<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/900362239868895a50c610d64422e3a6a670bde08fa75a8cd8bdb3dac46b49e4">\n</div>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/d1888a5e42a40dce9b6f1df11a73e74e81c05bcc0eca4d04aafca3ffb8835ab3">\n</div>\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n<br />\nThe Event Quest <span class="text-red">Fate Board</span> open on Feb. 1 18:00 PST.  <br>\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>Duration</h3>\n<p>\n<div class="holding-period">Feb. 1 18:00 - Apr. 29 21:59 PST</div>\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>How to Play Event Quests</h3>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/8b06e7521b786aa1dc476b0a7fe0d53a94643fc5c543e354738329d13a0d379b">\n</div>\n\n<p>\nFate Board is a <span class="text-red">high-difficulty event quest centered around creating affinity-based loadouts</span>.<br />\nIn each quest, there are <span class="text-red">Loadout Bonus</span> that further enhance stats when equipping weapons of certain affinities in your loadout. Make use of the effects to gain the upper hand.<br />\nSince the enemies have high HP and use powerful attacks, use your allies'' <span class="text-red">recovery skills</span> to your advantage in battle.<br />\nRewards include items needed to <span class="text-red">Exalt</span> your characters or <span class="text-red">Refine</span> your weapons.<br />\n<br />\n\n* This event quest will be unlocked upon completing Main Quest Ch. 2.<br />\n<br />\n</p>\n\n\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/051934b7eec5dfb3a45a7605326d535cb5d43837819aadac91a615328b8c31ac">\n</div>\n\n<p>\nEach quest comes with <span class="text-red">Loadout Bonus </span>.<br />\nLoadout Bonus affect weapons with specific affinities, <span class="text-red">further enhancing their stats when added to your loadout</span>.<br />\nBoost your battle strategies by adding them to your loadout when preparing for a quest.\n<br />\n\n<br />\n</p>\n\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/497dbc29949534c1da19c811685f9d9822daaebb88b8ace695cb059d8b562fb8">\n</div>\n\n<p>\nIn addition to the quest clear rewards, there are also <span class="text-red">period achievement rewards</span>, <span class="text-red">quest mission rewards</span>, and <span class="text-red">stage clear rewards</span>.<br />\n<br />\nPeriod achievement rewards are rewards for quests completed up to a point that can be obtained by logging in after the availability period, either in The Cage or on the main screen of the event.<br />\nRewards can be claimed during the event of the same name.<br />\n* Rewards will vary depending on the quest reached at the end of each event.<br />\n<br />\nYou can only get the quest mission rewards once. They are earned based on <span class="text-red">the total number of quest missions completed for each stage</span>.<br />\n<br />\nYou can only claim stage clear rewards once, from <span class="text-red">a treasure chest that appears upon clearing each stage</span>.<br />\n\n<br />\n* You may not be able to claim period achievement rewards if you have not opened the event''s main screen even once during the event period.\n<br />\n</p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>\nNotes\n</h3>\n<div class="attention_content">\n<ul>\n<li>\nDuration and content are subject to change without notice.\n</li>\n<li>\nIllustrations shown in notices, etc. may differ from those in-game.\n</li>\n<li>\nYou cannot have more than one character with the same name in the same deck.\n</li>\n<li>\n <span class="text-red">Note: Force Bonus is not available for Fate Boards quests.</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</section>\n<br />\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/900362239868895a50c610d64422e3a6a670bde08fa75a8cd8bdb3dac46b49e4','/images/en/operations/banner/d41152e0481ab4e5926efcce7be70a8bc9ace564d91bac6778d0d5d207d6216f');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1602,0,3,'Story Completion Countdown Limited-time Character Festival Summons On Now',1706839200000,replace('<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/6f96ac59bf28a3d9e3d7787154217f4a4fa88147fa3971875e0d3ba1608e50bc">\n</div>\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n<br />\nThe <span class="text-red">Story Completion Countdown Limited-time Character Festival Summons Vol.1 ~ 3</span> is available as of Feb. 1 18:00 PST.<br />\nThese Summons that limited-time characters guaranteed upon summoning a ★★★★. <br />\n <br />\nThe <span class="text-red">Countdown Festival Summons Medal Exchange</span> has also begun.<br>\n<br>\n* The medals obtained by summoning from Vol.1-3 will be medal across Story Completion Countdown Limited-time Character Festival Summons. <br />\n* Check Rates for a list of selected ★★★★ weapons that appear in this summons.<br />\n* No new characters or weapons will appear in these summons.<br />\n\n</p>\n\n<section>\n<h3>Duration</h3>\n<div class="holding-period">\nFeb. 1 18:00 - Mar. 29 23:59 PST\n</div>\n</section>\n\n\n\n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Summons Details\n  </h3>\n  <div class="information_table">\n    <table style="width:58%">\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th style="width:6%">\n            Type\n          </th>\n          <th style="width:5%">\n            Required Gems\n          </th>\n          <th style="width:80%">\n            Other\n\n          </th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n       \n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            x10 summon\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/gem_icon.png" width="20%"> 3,000\n          </td>\n          <td>\n★★★★ appearance rate 10％<br>\nLimited-time characters guaranteed upon summoning a ★★★★\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n<p>\n* You will also earn the appropriate number of medals for summons performed using Premium Summon Ticket x10.<br>\n</p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Countdown Festival Summons Medals</h3>\n<p>\nYou will receive <span class="text-red">Countdown Festival Summons Medals</span> each time you use this summons.<br />\nYou can exchange <span class="text-red">50 summon medals</span> at the Countdown Festival Summons Medal Exchange and <span class="text-red">choose from a limited-time characters</span>.<br />\nPlease check the Countdown Festival Summons Medal Exchange for eligible ★★★★ character weapons that can be exchanged.<br />\n<br />\nNote: The Countdown Festival Summons Medal Exchange <span class="text-red">is only available for a limited time.</span> Once the exchange period ends, you will be unable to exchange medals.<br />\nNote: Once the exchange period ends, each remaining medal <span class="text-red">will be converted into a bookmark</span> when you visit the summons screen.<br />\nNote: If you exchange for a character weapon you already own, you will earn <span class="text-red">10 ascension materials and 1 Awakening Stone for the character in addition to the weapon</span>.<br />\n\n<p/>\n</section>\n\n\n\n\n\n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Notes\n  </h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n    <ul>\n      <li>\n        Duration and content are subject to change without notice.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Illustrations shown in notices, etc. may differ from those in-game.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        The rarity, stats, skills, and abilities of characters and weapons displayed on the summons screen and on the official X account are shown at maximum levels.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        You cannot have more than one character with the same name in the same deck.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Refer to Rates to confirm which characters and weapons can appear in this summons.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Limited-time characters in this summons may reappear in the future.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        For more information about rates, please check the Rates button on the summons page.\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n<br />\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/6f96ac59bf28a3d9e3d7787154217f4a4fa88147fa3971875e0d3ba1608e50bc','/images/en/operations/banner/5c53e7be216001e8e5d8249ce184c0c7c87b3a5d026675da2c246dbb0d554bb2');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1608,0,3,'RoD Resonant Character Guaranteed Frozen-Heart Adventurer Conquest Summons On Now',1707444000000,replace('<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/23b1c72aecf2bede58c41ace52c9e6a3be12a3934287067904f3fd3e49eed64b">\n</div>\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Reincarnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n<br />\nThe RoD Resonant Character Guaranteed Frozen-Heart Adventurer Conquest Summons is available as of Feb. 8 18:00 PST.<br />\nThis Summon can be drawn for 3,000 gems, and <span class="text-red">Recollections of Dusk Frozen-Heart Adventurer Resonance</span> characters as well as <span class="text-red">Light ★★★★ Weapons</span> with <span class="text-red">effective barrier skills</span>. Plus, <span class="text-red">★★★★ have double the chance</span> this summon.<br />\nIn addition, this <span class="text-red">x10 summon</span> is <span class="text-red">guaranteed a Resonance character from the lineup in the 10th slot</span>.<br />\n<br />\n\nThe <span class="text-red">Frozen-Heart Adventurer Summons Medal Exchange</span> has also begun.<br />\n<span class="text-red">Frozen-Heart Adventurer Summon Medals</span> from the Recollections of Dusk Resonant Characters Guaranteed Frozen-Heart Adventurer Conquest Summons</span> and exchange <span class="text-red">50 medals</span> for a Recollections of Dusk Frozen-Heart Adventurer Resonant <span class="text-red">★★★★ character weapons</span> or <span class="text-red">Light ★★★★ weapons</span> with <span class="text-red">effective barrier skills</span><br />\n\n\n<br />\n* No new characters or weapons will appear in these summons.<br />\n* Please check the Frozen-Heart Adventurer Summons Summon Medal Exchange for what you can exchange with Summon Medals.<br />\n</p>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Resonant Characters for this Summons</h3>\n<p>\nThere are characters that will have <span class="text-red">HP and attack stat bonus effects</span> in Recollections of Dusk Frozen-Heart Adventurer.<br />\nCheck the increased stats'' details in the quest content.\n</p>\n\n<h4>Quest Bonus: Resonant Costumes Effect Duration</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nFeb. 8 18:00 - Apr. 2 23:59 PST\n</div>\n<p>\n* It is different the summons period.</br>\n</p>\n\n<h4>Resonant Costumes Effect List</h4>\n<section>\n\n   <div class="information_table weapon_table">\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n\n          <th rowSpan="1"style="width:35%">Costume</th>\n          <th colSpan="1" class="al-center">Effect</th>\n　　　　　　　　　\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n\n      <tbody>\n   　　　　　<tr>\n          <th> Griff (Abyssal Captain)<br />\n\n          <td rowSpan="5"style">Attack +200%<br />HP +200%<br /></td></tr>\n         \n   　　　　　<tr><th>  Marie (New Year''s Songstress)</th></tr>\n                        <tr><th>Saryu (Celebratory Witch)</th></tr>\n                        <tr><th>Levania (Yuletide Monster)</th></tr>\n                        <tr><th>Priyet (Shadowbound Werebeast)</th></tr>                                                \n        <tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Duration</h3>\n<div class="holding-period">\nFeb. 8 18:00 - Mar. 29 23:59 PST\n</div>\n<p>\n* The Exchange can be used until two days after the event duration ends. Please see the exchange in game for details.\n</p>\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Resonant Characters</h3>\n<p>You are guaranteed one of the following <span class="text-red">Resonant Characters</span> in each 10th summon in Recollections of Dusk Frozen-Heart Adventurer.<br />\n\n\n<br />\n<p><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/bc994dea92e801683d662c52262b8b560b068e11bcf771ac8b2065be38e0a382" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Griff(Abyssal Captain)<br />\n      Note: You can get this character by acquiring the <span class="text-red">Coward''s Sin</span> weapon.</p>\n    \n<p><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/ef408a7e86c2e03d9a9c0f846ea46d442df7e19ed684b96011faac4bed058e79" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Marie(New Year''s Songstress)<br />\n      Note: You can get this character by acquiring the <span class="text-red">Blade of Early Spring</span> weapon.</p>\n    \n<p><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/c3ae6022f405f3f382240efb15e8c86a469915fcdee76b0075dfcd6571715331" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Saryu(Celebratory Witch)<br />\n      Note: You can get this character by acquiring the <span class="text-red">Thorn of the Last Blossom</span> weapon.</p>\n    \n<p><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/277a9f8784c464dc36e6db66845d80b126634fa99c95918510b1e78278dca3d1" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Levania(Yuletide Monster)<br />\n      Note: You can get this character by acquiring the <span class="text-red">Predilection Antler</span> weapon.</p>\n    \n<p><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/095ea6ad6cc491d68a4928ddba03b7ec0ba3e175f9c3b652d771fbde8fca8537" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Priyet(Shadowbound Werebeast)<br />\n      Note: You can get this character by acquiring the <span class="text-red">Leaden Blessing</span> weapon.</p>\n\n\n\n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Summons Details\n  </h3>\n  <div class="information_table">\n    <table style="width:58%">\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th style="width:6%">\n            Type\n          </th>\n          <th style="width:12%">\n            Required Gems\n          </th>\n          <th style="width:80%">\n            Other\n\n          </th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n       \n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            10x summon\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/gem_icon.png" width="20%"> 3,000\n          </td>\n          <td>\n             <span class="text-red">★★★★ appearance rate doubled</span><br />\n             <span class="text-red">Resonant Characters Guaranteed on the 10th summon</span><br />\n            Frozen-Heart Adventurer Summon Medal x10</br>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n\n<p>\n* This is a x10 summon that can <span class="text-red">only be used 15 times during the availability period</span>.<br>\n* You will also earn the appropriate number of Medals for summons performed using x10 premium summon tickets.<br>\n* For more information about the characters available in the summons, please check Rates from the summons page.\n\n</p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Frozen-Heart Adventurer Summons Medals</h3>\n<p>\nYou will receive <span class="text-red">Frozen-Heart Adventurer Summon Medals</span> each time you use this summons.<br />\nYou can exchange <span class="text-red">50 summon medals</span> at the Frozen-Heart Adventurer Summons Exchange and <span class="text-red">choose from a selection of eligible ★★★★ character weapons or ★★★★ weapons</span>.<br />\nPlease check the Frozen-Heart Adventurer Summons Medal Exchange for eligible ★★★★ character weapons that can be exchanged.<br />\n<br />\nNote: The Frozen-Heart Adventurer Summons Medal Exchange <span class="text-red">is only available for a limited time.</span> Once the exchange period ends, you will be unable to exchange medals.<br />\nNote: Once the exchange period ends, each remaining medal <span class="text-red">will be converted into a bookmark</span> when you visit the summons screen.<br />\nNote: If you exchange for a character weapon you already own, you will earn <span class="text-red">10 ascension materials and 1 Awakening Stone for the character in addition to the weapon</span>.<br /><br />\n\n<p/>\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Notes\n  </h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n    <ul>\n      <li>\n        Duration and content are subject to change without notice.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Illustrations shown in notices, etc. may differ from those in-game.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        The rarity, stats, skills, and abilities of characters and weapons displayed on the summons screen and on the official X account are shown at maximum levels.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        You cannot have more than one character with the same name in the same deck.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Refer to Rates to confirm which characters and weapons can appear in this summons.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Limited-time characters in this summons may reappear in the future.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        For more information about rates, please check the Rates button on the summons page.\n      </li>\n<li>\n      <span class="text-red">No characters or weapons will have featured rates.</span>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n<br />\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Reincarnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/23b1c72aecf2bede58c41ace52c9e6a3be12a3934287067904f3fd3e49eed64b','/images/en/operations/banner/424a85bec7583a3953eb67cea8689408f9988d0a1e8884aec46668efaaf97139');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1614,0,3,'Raiments of Rebirth Summons On Now',1708221600000,replace('<div class="info-largeimage">\n <img src="/images/en/operations/banner/21b6d5ed1c75e3ca42c921e62cb5fe4d2e9aa749c3520b944a126d0207f8d9fb">\n </div>\n <p>\n Hello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br /> \n This is a message from the management team.<br />\n <br />\n The <span class="text-red">Raiments of Rebirth Summons</span> has begun as of Feb. 17 18:00 PST.<br />\n The <span class="text-red">Shard (Raiments of Rebirth) Exchange</span> has also begun.<br />\n* The Summon Shards that can be obtained in the <span class="text-red">Paid Only: Japanese 3rd Anniversary Multi-Step Summons</span> are <span class="text-red">different</span> from the shards that can be obtained in this summons.<br />\n\n </p>\n \n <section>\n <h3>Duration</h3>\n <h4>Summons</h4>\n <div class="holding-period">\nFeb. 17 18:00 - Apr. 29 21:59 PST\n </div>\n \n </section>\n \n <section>\n \n <h3>Featured Characters &amp; Weapons</h3>\n <p>In this summons, the <span class="text-red">following limited-time characters and weapons have increased appearance rates</span>.<br />\n \n \n \n Information on stats, skills, abilities and available debris can be found on the summons screen.</p>\n \n <h4>Limited-Time Characters</h4>\n <p>\n <img/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/></p>\n \n<p><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/8c4306009c450efc8f06b2cbb35e5d7f56ef64a518734c4c53290fb5266afb2c" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Akeha (Festive Assassin)<br />\nNote: You can get this character by acquiring the <span class="text-red">Bramble</span> weapon.</p>\n<br />\n\n <p><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/c5f2170936dfea6ecf1ff047ea114382b6e3d4446dc50d05d8e5872b229efd55" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Yurie (Festive Ruler)<br />\n Note: You can get this character by acquiring the <span class="text-red">Alpha and Omega Salute</span> weapon.</p>\n <br />\n\n <p><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/c38d973e4047936c84953ef31da2761afb8722702de484a2c9cd52ecb2296256" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Saryu (Festive Witch)<br />\n Note: You can get this character by acquiring the <span class="text-red">Crown Rod</span> weapon.</p>\n <br />\n \n\n <h4>Limited-Time Weapons</h4>\n <p><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/></p>\n \n<p><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/0eaeffe50a5bf25f56daac2cfd53d9e5d3bd1848686c3912fc07ee029db0f0f2" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Bramble<br /></p><br />\n\n<p><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/4e4817dfc70c7e1ee2683f4c9fd7c50fa0d222f003ff048a575c57a46bf81ac4" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Alpha and Omega Salute<br /></p><br />\n\n<p><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/a4e34d92b9538e80a3c20173e835ae8ccc49c467172b0e5fdd8175041db552d6" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Crown Rod<br /></p><br />\n \n </p>\n </div>\n</section>\n\n \n <section>\n <h3>\n Summons Details\n </h3>\n <div class="information_table">\n <table style="width:58%">\n <thead>\n <tr>\n <th style="width:6%">\n Type\n </th>\n <th style="width:12%">\n Required Gems\n </th>\n <th style="width:40%">\n Obtainable Shards (Raiments of Rebirth)\n </th>\n </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n <tr>\n <td>\n 1x summon\n </td>\n <td>\n <img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/gem_icon.png" width="20%"> 300\n </td>\n <td>\n  1\n </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n <td>\n 10x summon\n </td>\n <td>\n <img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/gem_icon.png" width="20%"> 3,000\n </td>\n <td>\n  10\n </td>\n </tr>\n </tbody>\n </table>\n </div>\n \n <p>\n <span class="text-red">At least one ★★★ or higher weapon is guaranteed</span> in each <span class="text-red">10x summon</span>.<br />\n Note: You will also earn the appropriate number of Shards (Raiments of Rebirth) for summons performed using premium summon tickets (including 10x summon tickets).\n </p>\n \n </section>\n \n \n <section>\n <h3>Shards (Raiments of Rebirth)</h3>\n <p>\n You will earn <span class="text-red">Shards (Raiments of Rebirth)</span> each time you use the Raiments of Rebirth Summons.<br />\n These items can be used at the Shard (Raiments of Rebirth) Exchange to acquire new characters and weapons.<br />\n <br />\n Note: The Exchange <span class="text-red">is only available for a limited time.</span> Once the exchange period ends, you will be unable to exchange Summon Shards.<br />\n Note: If you exchange for a character weapon you already own, you will earn 10 ascension materials for the character, 1 Awakening Stone of that character in addition to the weapon.<br />\n Note: Summon Shards can only be used at the Exchange of the same name.<br />\n Note: You will also earn Summon Shards for summons performed using premium summon tickets (including 10x summon tickets).<br />\n \n \n <p/>\n </section>\n \n \n <section>\n <h3>Resonant Costume Bonuses in Subjugation Battles</h3>\n\n <p>\n \n Season 008 of Subjugation Battles will have a resonant costume quest bonus. The bonus effect of the resonant costumes <span class="text-red">reduces cooldown time for weapon skills in certain Subjugation Battle quests</span> and <span class="text-red">activates an attack power increase based on the ascension count</span>.<br />\n </p>\n \n </section>\n <section>\n \n <div class="information_table weapon_table">\n <table>\n <thead>\n <tr>\n \n \n <th colSpan="5" class="al-center">Ascension Count Effects</th>\n \n </tr>\n <tr>\n \n <th style="width:10%">None</th>\n <th style="width:10%">1</th>\n <th style="width:10%">2</th>\n <th style="width:10%">3</th>\n <th style="width:10%">4</th>\n </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n \n <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+25(%)</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n Reduced by 10%<br /></td>\n <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+30%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n Reduced by 10%<br /></td>\n <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+35%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n Reduced by 10%<br /></td>\n <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+40%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n Reduced by 10%<br /></td>\n <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+50%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n Reduced by 10%<br /></td>\n \n </tr>\n \n \n <tr>\n </tbody>\n </table>\n </div>\n </section>\n <br />\n \n \n <section>\n <h4>Quest Bonus: Resonant Costume Effect</h4>\n <div class="information_table powerup_rate_table">\n <table>\n <thead>\n <tr>\n <th>\n Resonant Costume\n </th>\n <th>\n Quests\n </th>\n </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n <tr>\n <th>\n <img class="chara_image" src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/8c4306009c450efc8f06b2cbb35e5d7f56ef64a518734c4c53290fb5266afb2c" alt=""> Akeha (Festive Assassin)\n </th>\n \n <td>\n <span class="text-red">Manifestation: Windy Cursed God</span>\n </td>\n </tr>\n\n <tr>\n <th>\n <img class="chara_image" src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/c5f2170936dfea6ecf1ff047ea114382b6e3d4446dc50d05d8e5872b229efd55" alt=""> Yurie (Festive Ruler)\n </th>\n \n <td>\n <span class="text-red">Manifestation: Bleak Cursed God</span>\n </td>\n </tr>\n\n <tr>\n <th>\n <img class="chara_image" src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/c38d973e4047936c84953ef31da2761afb8722702de484a2c9cd52ecb2296256" alt=""> Saryu (Festive Witch)\n </th>\n \n <td>\n <span class="text-red">Manifestation: Bleak Cursed God</span>\n </td>\n </tr>\n </tbody>\n \n \n \n \n </table>\n </div>\n </section>\n \n \n <section>\n <h3>Event Quest Bonuses</h3>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/a360600bcebdfebbe9127ae162146d888e597f7bef55203f462cd7cb2291abdd">\n</div>\n <p>\n The characters and weapons featured in this summons grant <span class="text-red">quest bonuses</span> in the event quest "Record: The Cage of Rebirth". Playing the quest with these costumes will activate <span class="text-red">various effects</span>, and some effects.</span><br />\n <p/>\n <section>\n <h4>Quest Bonus: Resonant Costumes Effect List</h4>\n\n\n    <div class="information_table weapon_table">\n  <table>\n   <thead>\n    <tr>\n\n     \n     <th colSpan="5" class="al-center">Resonant Costume "Festive Assassin" and "Festive Ruler" Ascension Count Effect</th>\n　　　　　　　　　\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n\n     <th style="width:10%">None</th>\n     <th style="width:10%">1</th>\n     <th style="width:10%">2</th>\n     <th style="width:10%">3</th>\n     <th style="width:10%">4</th>\n    </tr>\n   </thead>\n   <tbody>\n   　　　　　  　　　　　<tr>\n     \n     <td>Attack<span class="text-red">＋100%</span><br />HP＋50%<br /></td>\n     <td>Attack<span class="text-red">＋125%</span><br />HP＋50%<br /></td>\n     <td>Attack<span class="text-red">＋150%</span><br />HP＋50%<br /></td>\n     <td>Attack<span class="text-red">＋175%</span><br />HP＋50%<br /></td>\n     <td>Attack<span class="text-red">＋200%</span><br />HP＋50%<br /></td>\n\n    </tr>\n     \n    <tr>\n   </tbody>\n  </table>\n </div>\n </section>\n\n\n<section>\n  <div class="information_table weapon_table">\n  <table>\n   <thead>\n    <tr>\n\n     \n     <th colSpan="5" class="al-center">Resonant Costume "Festive Witch" Ascension Count Effect</th>\n　　　　　　　　　\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n\n     <th style="width:10%">None</th>\n     <th style="width:10%">1</th>\n     <th style="width:10%">2</th>\n     <th style="width:10%">3</th>\n     <th style="width:10%">4</th>\n    </tr>\n   </thead>\n   <tbody>\n   　　　　　<tr>                      <td>Character Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+30%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>           <td>Character Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+30%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+10%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>           <td>Character Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+40%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+10%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>           <td>Character Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+40%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+20%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>           <td>Character Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+50%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+20%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>          </tr>\n         \n        <tr>\n     \n    <tr>\n   </tbody>\n  </table>\n </div>\n </section>\n \n <p>\n <br />\n \nResonant weapons will have an effect that <span class="text-red">increases the amount of The Cage of Rebirth Medals dropped</span>.</span><br />\n \n \n <h4>\n Quest Bonus: Resonant Weapons Effect List\n </h4>\n<div class="information_table weapon_table">\n <table>\n  <thead>\n   <tr>\n    <th rowSpan="2" style="width:30%">Weapon</th>\n    <th rowSpan="2" style="width:13%; text-align:center;">Medals</th>\n    <th colspan="5" style="text-align:center">Ascension Count</th>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <th style="text-align:center">None</th>\n    <th style="text-align:center">1</th>\n    <th style="text-align:center">2</th>\n    <th style="text-align:center">3</th>\n    <th style="text-align:center">4</th>\n   </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n   \n   \n   <tr>\n    <th><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/0eaeffe50a5bf25f56daac2cfd53d9e5d3bd1848686c3912fc07ee029db0f0f2" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Bramble</th>\n    <td rowSpan="3" style="text-align:center"><img class="coin_icon" src="/images/en/operations/coin/b0dd4629325e7fd46f5ee720bc75a954e84e08003a44cfa3b53559c01122f91c"><br />\n\n     <img class="coin_icon" src="/images/en/operations/coin/71779da015c5ff4fe624621ed336221ce068a738aeb6a490df6ec410ded8b661">\n     <img class="coin_icon" src="/images/en/operations/coin/3b1d5ad04fc31b5a41996dc8dd3c77faa2afebebf10ea57179a10c2d9f0af5a1">\n    </td>\n    <td rowSpan="3" style="text-align:center">+5</td>\n    <td rowSpan="3" style="text-align:center">+11</td>\n    <td rowSpan="3" style="text-align:center">+17</td>\n    <td rowSpan="3" style="text-align:center">+23</td>\n    <td rowSpan="3" style="text-align:center">+30</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <th><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/4e4817dfc70c7e1ee2683f4c9fd7c50fa0d222f003ff048a575c57a46bf81ac4" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Alpha and Omega Salute</th>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <th><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/a4e34d92b9538e80a3c20173e835ae8ccc49c467172b0e5fdd8175041db552d6" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Crown Rod</th>\n   </tr>\n  </tbody>\n </table>\n</div>\n\n\n \n <p>\n For more information on the event quests, check the following notices.\n <p/>\n <div data-category="information" data-informationId="1616" class="other-link-btn common_btn common_button-typeA">Event Quest "Record: The Cage of Rebirth" On Now</div>\n \n </section>\n \n<section>\n<div class="mama_balloon">\n   <div class="mama_img">\n    <img src="/images/common/other/webview_parts_mama.png" alt="">\n   </div>\n   <div class="balloon">We found these memories together. Memories slumbering in the same place within The Cage tend to interfere with one another, you see.</div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n \n\n <section>\n <h3>\n Notes\n </h3>\n <div class="attention_content">\n <ul>\n <li>\n Event duration and content are subject to change without notice.\n </li>\n <li>\n Illustrations shown in notices, etc. may differ from those in-game.\n </li>\n <li>\n The rarity, stats, skills, and abilities of characters and weapons displayed on the summons screen and on the official Twitter account are shown at maximum levels.\n </li>\n <li>\n "Increased rates" means that the character''s appearance rate is higher than that of other characters of the same rarity.\n </li>\n\n <li>\n <span class="text-red">Akeha (Festive Assassin) & Bramble, Yurie (Festive Ruler) & Alpha and Omega Salute, Saryu (Festive Witch) & Crown Rod will not appear when using ★★★+ Premium Summon Tickets or ★★★★ Premium Summon Tickets.</span>\n </li>\n <li>\n You cannot have more than one character with the same name in the same deck.\n </li>\n <li>\n For more information about rates, please check the Rates button on the summons page.\n </li>\n <li>\n If you perform a summons using the 10x summon button, a ★★★ or higher weapon will always appear on the 10th summon, regardless of the results of the first 9 summons.\n </li>\n <li>\n The video clip that plays when pressing the Skill button was recorded in a development environment.\n </li>\n <li>\n Summon Shards (Raiments of Rebirth) can only be used during the exchange period and cannot be carried over to the next event.\n </li>\n </ul>\n </div>\n <br />\n </section>\n \n <section>\n <p>\n Thank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n </p>\n </section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/21b6d5ed1c75e3ca42c921e62cb5fe4d2e9aa749c3520b944a126d0207f8d9fb','/images/en/operations/banner/9b0b91dfbb66a9b5fe58eb9b49745debb7942fac7a786a8af197832edff69e47');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1615,0,3,'Paid Only: Japanese 3rd Anniversary Multi-Step Summons On Now',1708221600000,replace('<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/ca3f415e2d0c0ca22d563c0437f3ee7f3c53e01589a8da6bde45931ce392d283">\n</div>\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n<br />\nThe <span class="text-red">Paid Only: Japanese 3rd Anniversary Multi-Step Summons</span> has begun as of Feb. 17 18:00 PST.<br />\nIn this summon Step 2 and 4 are <span class="text-red">free</span>.<br> \nAlso the rate for ★★★★ is doubled at Step 5 and <span class="text-red">New limited-time characters</span> is guaranteed in the 10th.<br />\n<br />\nPlease see the summons page for more details on each step and bonuses that can be obtained. <br>\n<br>\nShard (JP 3rd Anniversary) Exchange will also be available allowing you to exchange 150 Summon Shards in for New limited-time characters. <br />\n* The Summon Shards that can be obtained in the <span class="text-red">Raiments of Rebirth Summons</span> are <span class="text-red">different</span> from the shards that can be obtained in this summons.<br />\n<p/>\n</p>\n\n  <section>\n <h3>Duration</h3>\n <h4>Summons</h4>\n <div class="holding-period">\nFeb. 17 18:00 - Apr. 29 21:59 PST\n </div>\n \n </section>\n \n <section>\n \n <h3>Featured Characters &amp; Weapons</h3>\n <p>In this summons, the <span class="text-red">following limited-time characters and weapons have increased appearance rates</span>.<br />\n \n \n \n Information on stats, skills, abilities and available debris can be found on the summons screen.</p>\n \n <h4>Limited-Time Characters</h4>\n <p>\n <img/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/></p>\n \n<p><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/8c4306009c450efc8f06b2cbb35e5d7f56ef64a518734c4c53290fb5266afb2c" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Akeha (Festive Assassin)<br />\nNote: You can get this character by acquiring the <span class="text-red">Bramble</span> weapon.</p>\n<br />\n\n <p><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/c5f2170936dfea6ecf1ff047ea114382b6e3d4446dc50d05d8e5872b229efd55" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Yurie (Festive Ruler)<br />\n Note: You can get this character by acquiring the <span class="text-red">Alpha and Omega Salute</span> weapon.</p>\n <br />\n\n <p><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/c38d973e4047936c84953ef31da2761afb8722702de484a2c9cd52ecb2296256" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Saryu (Festive Witch)<br />\n Note: You can get this character by acquiring the <span class="text-red">Crown Rod</span> weapon.</p>\n <br />\n \n\n <h4>Limited-Time Weapons</h4>\n <p><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/></p>\n \n<p><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/0eaeffe50a5bf25f56daac2cfd53d9e5d3bd1848686c3912fc07ee029db0f0f2" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Bramble<br /></p><br />\n\n<p><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/4e4817dfc70c7e1ee2683f4c9fd7c50fa0d222f003ff048a575c57a46bf81ac4" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Alpha and Omega Salute<br /></p><br />\n\n<p><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/a4e34d92b9538e80a3c20173e835ae8ccc49c467172b0e5fdd8175041db552d6" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Crown Rod<br /></p><br />\n \n </p>\n </div>\n</section>\n\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Summons Details</h3>\n</section>\n<section>\n\n    <div class="information_table">\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th style="width:10%">\n            Step\n          </th>\n          <th style="width:10%">\n            Type\n          </th>\n          <th style="width:13%">\n            Required Gems\n          </th>\n          <th style="width:67%">\n            Other\n          </th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            STEP1\n          </td>\n          <td>\n       10x summon\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/gem_icon.png" width="20%">\n           <span class="text-red">2000</span>\n         </td>\n          <td>\n<span class="text-red">Featured character guaranteed upon summoning a ★★★★ (w/ character)<br /></span>\nInsignia of Skill x2<br>\nAdvanced Handbook x40<br>\n\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            STEP2\n          </td>\n          <td>\n       10x summon\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/gem_icon.png" width="20%">\n           <span class="text-red">Free</span>\n          </td>\n          <td>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            STEP3\n          </td>\n          <td>\n       10x summon\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/gem_icon.png" width="20%">\n           3000\n          </td>\n          <td>\n<span class="text-red">Featured character guaranteed upon summoning a ★★★★ (w/ character)<br />\n★★★★ x1.5 appearance rate<br /></span>\nVerse of Truth x1<br>\nAdamant x10<br>\nWeapon-Skill Enhancement Material x20 for each weapon type\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            STEP4\n          </td>\n          <td>\n       10x summon\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/gem_icon.png" width="20%">\n           <span class="text-red">Free</span>\n          </td>\n          <td>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n　　　　　  <tr>\n          <td>\n            STEP5\n          </td>\n          <td>\n       10x summon\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/gem_icon.png" width="20%">\n           <span class="text-red">5000</span>\n          </td>\n          <td>\n<span class="text-red">Featured character guaranteed upon summoning a ★★★★ (w/ character)<br />\n★★★★ x2 appearance rate<br />\nNew limited-time Characters guaranteed on the 10th summon<br /></span>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class="information_table">\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th style="width:10%">\n            Step 3\n Weapon Skill Enhancement Materials\n          </th>\n          \n         \n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n\n\n          <td>\nAngrite, Moldavite, Aubrite, Chondrite, Eucrite, Merlinite, Sturdy Nail, Pure Machine Oil, Stainless Steel Wire, Large Nut, Stainless Steel Bolt, Flawless Timber, Fine Wax, Natural Cloth, Intricate Gear, Prized Charcoal, Pristine Coil, Reinforced Glass\n          </td>\n\n\n      </tbody>\n    </table><br />\n\n\n<p>\nThis Summon is only available in <span class="text-red">Paid Gems</span>.<br />\nAlso, you would get <span class="text-red">Shard (JP 3rd Anniversary) x10</span> in every steps.<br>\n<br>\n\n\n* <span class="text-red">At least one ★★★ or higher weapon is guaranteed</span> in each <span class="text-red">10x summon</span> at Step 1-4.<br />\n* You will proceed through Steps 1-5 in order, and then return to Step 1 after finishing Step 5.<br />\n* Paid Only: Japanese 3rd Anniversary Multi-Step Summons does not have a limit on how many times you can loop back to Step 1.<br />\n* Any bonus you earn will be sent to your gift box.</p>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>Summon Shards (JP 3rd Anniversary)</h3>\n<p>\n<span class="text-red">Summon Shards (JP 3rd Anniversary)</span> can be obtained from the Paid Only: Japanese 3rd Anniversary Multi-Step Summons.<br />\nCollect <span class="text-red">150 Summon Shards</span> and trade them at the Summon Shard (JP 3rd Anniversary) Exchange for exclusive characters. \n<br />\n* The Exchange <span class="text-red">is only available for a limited time.</span> Once the exchange period ends, you will be unable to exchange shards.<br />\n* If you exchange for a character weapon you already own, you will earn <span class="text-red">10 ascension materials and 1 Awakening Stone for the character in addition to the weapon</span>.<br />\n* Summon Shards can only be used at the exchange of the same name.<br />\n* The Summon Shards that can be obtained in the <span class="text-red">Raiments of Rebirth Summons</span> are <span class="text-red">different</span> from the shards that can be obtained in this summons.<br />\n<p/>\n</section>\n\n\n\n  <section>\n <h3>Resonant Costume Bonuses in Subjugation Battles</h3>\n\n <p>\n \n Season 008 of Subjugation Battles will have a resonant costume quest bonus. The bonus effect of the resonant costumes <span class="text-red">reduces cooldown time for weapon skills in certain Subjugation Battle quests</span> and <span class="text-red">activates an attack power increase based on the ascension count</span>.<br />\n </p>\n \n </section>\n <section>\n \n <div class="information_table weapon_table">\n <table>\n <thead>\n <tr>\n \n \n <th colSpan="5" class="al-center">Ascension Count Effects</th>\n \n </tr>\n <tr>\n \n <th style="width:10%">None</th>\n <th style="width:10%">1</th>\n <th style="width:10%">2</th>\n <th style="width:10%">3</th>\n <th style="width:10%">4</th>\n </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n \n <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+25%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n Reduced by 10%<br /></td>\n <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+30%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n Reduced by 10%<br /></td>\n <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+35%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n Reduced by 10%<br /></td>\n <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+40%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n Reduced by 10%<br /></td>\n <td>Attack <span class="text-red">+50%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n Reduced by 10%<br /></td>\n \n </tr>\n \n \n <tr>\n </tbody>\n </table>\n </div>\n </section>\n <br />\n \n \n <section>\n <h4>Quest Bonus: Resonant Costume Effect</h4>\n <div class="information_table powerup_rate_table">\n <table>\n <thead>\n <tr>\n <th>\n Resonant Costume\n </th>\n <th>\n Quests\n </th>\n </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n <tr>\n <th>\n <img class="chara_image" src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/8c4306009c450efc8f06b2cbb35e5d7f56ef64a518734c4c53290fb5266afb2c" alt=""> Akeha (Festive Assassin)\n </th>\n \n <td>\n <span class="text-red">Manifestation: Windy Cursed God</span>\n </td>\n </tr>\n\n <tr>\n <th>\n <img class="chara_image" src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/c5f2170936dfea6ecf1ff047ea114382b6e3d4446dc50d05d8e5872b229efd55" alt=""> Yurie (Festive Ruler)\n </th>\n \n <td>\n <span class="text-red">Manifestation: Bleak Cursed God</span>\n </td>\n </tr>\n\n <tr>\n <th>\n <img class="chara_image" src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/c38d973e4047936c84953ef31da2761afb8722702de484a2c9cd52ecb2296256" alt=""> Saryu (Festive Witch)\n </th>\n \n <td>\n <span class="text-red">Manifestation: Bleak Cursed God</span>\n </td>\n </tr>\n </tbody>\n \n \n \n \n </table>\n </div>\n </section>\n \n \n <section>\n <h3>Event Quest Bonuses</h3>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/a360600bcebdfebbe9127ae162146d888e597f7bef55203f462cd7cb2291abdd">\n</div>\n <p>\n The characters and weapons featured in this summons grant <span class="text-red">quest bonuses</span> in the event quest "Record: The Cage of Rebirth". Playing the quest with these costumes will activate <span class="text-red">various effects</span>, and some effects.</span><br />\n <p/>\n <section>\n <h4>Quest Bonus: Resonant Costumes Effect List</h4>\n\n\n  <div class="information_table weapon_table">\n  <table>\n   <thead>\n    <tr>\n\n     \n     <th colSpan="5" class="al-center">Resonant Costume "Festive Assassin" and "Festive Ruler" Ascension Count Effect</th>\n　　　　　　　　　\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n\n     <th style="width:10%">None</th>\n     <th style="width:10%">1</th>\n     <th style="width:10%">2</th>\n     <th style="width:10%">3</th>\n     <th style="width:10%">4</th>\n    </tr>\n   </thead>\n   <tbody>\n   　　　　　  　　　　　<tr>\n     \n     <td>Attack<span class="text-red">＋100%</span><br />HP＋50%<br /></td>\n     <td>Attack<span class="text-red">＋125%</span><br />HP＋50%<br /></td>\n     <td>Attack<span class="text-red">＋150%</span><br />HP＋50%<br /></td>\n     <td>Attack<span class="text-red">＋175%</span><br />HP＋50%<br /></td>\n     <td>Attack<span class="text-red">＋200%</span><br />HP＋50%<br /></td>\n\n    </tr>\n     \n    <tr>\n   </tbody>\n  </table>\n </div>\n </section>\n\n\n<section>\n  <div class="information_table weapon_table">\n  <table>\n   <thead>\n    <tr>\n\n     \n     <th colSpan="5" class="al-center">Resonant Costume "Festive Witch" Ascension Count Effect</th>\n　　　　　　　　　\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n\n     <th style="width:10%">None</th>\n     <th style="width:10%">1</th>\n     <th style="width:10%">2</th>\n     <th style="width:10%">3</th>\n     <th style="width:10%">4</th>\n    </tr>\n   </thead>\n   <tbody>\n   　　　　　<tr>                      <td>Character Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+30%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>           <td>Character Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+30%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+10%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>           <td>Character Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+40%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+10%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>           <td>Character Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+40%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+20%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>           <td>Character Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+50%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+20%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>          </tr>\n         \n        <tr>\n     \n    <tr>\n   </tbody>\n  </table>\n </div>\n </section>\n <p>\n <br />\n \nResonant weapons will have an effect that <span class="text-red">increases the amount of The Cage of Rebirth Medals dropped</span>.</span><br />\n \n \n <h4>\n Quest Bonus: Resonant Weapons Effect List\n </h4>\n<div class="information_table weapon_table">\n <table>\n  <thead>\n   <tr>\n    <th rowSpan="2" style="width:30%">Weapon</th>\n    <th rowSpan="2" style="width:13%; text-align:center;">Medals</th>\n    <th colspan="5" style="text-align:center">Ascension Count</th>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <th style="text-align:center">None</th>\n    <th style="text-align:center">1</th>\n    <th style="text-align:center">2</th>\n    <th style="text-align:center">3</th>\n    <th style="text-align:center">4</th>\n   </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n   \n   \n   <tr>\n    <th><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/0eaeffe50a5bf25f56daac2cfd53d9e5d3bd1848686c3912fc07ee029db0f0f2" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Bramble</th>\n    <td rowSpan="3" style="text-align:center"><img class="coin_icon" src="/images/en/operations/coin/b0dd4629325e7fd46f5ee720bc75a954e84e08003a44cfa3b53559c01122f91c"><br />\n\n     <img class="coin_icon" src="/images/en/operations/coin/71779da015c5ff4fe624621ed336221ce068a738aeb6a490df6ec410ded8b661">\n     <img class="coin_icon" src="/images/en/operations/coin/3b1d5ad04fc31b5a41996dc8dd3c77faa2afebebf10ea57179a10c2d9f0af5a1">\n    </td>\n    <td rowSpan="3" style="text-align:center">+5</td>\n    <td rowSpan="3" style="text-align:center">+11</td>\n    <td rowSpan="3" style="text-align:center">+17</td>\n    <td rowSpan="3" style="text-align:center">+23</td>\n    <td rowSpan="3" style="text-align:center">+30</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <th><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/4e4817dfc70c7e1ee2683f4c9fd7c50fa0d222f003ff048a575c57a46bf81ac4" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Alpha and Omega Salute</th>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <th><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/a4e34d92b9538e80a3c20173e835ae8ccc49c467172b0e5fdd8175041db552d6" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Crown Rod</th>\n   </tr>\n  </tbody>\n </table>\n</div>\n\n\n \n <p>\n For more information on the event quests, check the following notices.\n <p/>\n <div data-category="information" data-informationId="1616" class="other-link-btn common_btn common_button-typeA">Event Quest "Record: The Cage of Rebirth" On Now</div>\n \n </section>\n \n<section>\n<div class="mama_balloon">\n   <div class="mama_img">\n    <img src="/images/common/other/webview_parts_mama.png" alt="">\n   </div>\n   <div class="balloon">We found these memories together. Memories slumbering in the same place within The Cage tend to interfere with one another, you see.</div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Notes\n  </h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n    <ul>\n      <li>\n        Event duration and content are subject to change without notice.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Illustrations shown in notices, etc. may differ from those in-game.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        The rarity, stats, skills, and abilities of characters and weapons displayed on the summons screen and on the official X account are shown at maximum levels.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        "Increased rates" means that the character''s appearance rate is higher than that of other characters of the same rarity.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        You cannot have more than one character with the same name in the same deck.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        For more information about rates, please check the Rates button on the summons page.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        If you perform a summons using the 10x summon button, a ★★★ or higher weapon will always appear on the 10th summon, regardless of the results of the first 9 summons.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        The video clip that plays when pressing the Skill button was recorded in a development environment.\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n<br />\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n  </section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/ca3f415e2d0c0ca22d563c0437f3ee7f3c53e01589a8da6bde45931ce392d283','/images/en/operations/banner/067036d71df2131727c23bf68b897a343a6c6f66d72761c4ecad5319ea8db128');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1616,0,2,'Event Quest "Record: The Cage of Rebirth" On Now',1708221600000,replace('<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/a360600bcebdfebbe9127ae162146d888e597f7bef55203f462cd7cb2291abdd">\n</div>\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n<br />\nThe event quest "<span class="text-red">Record: The Cage of Rebirth</span>" is available starting Feb. 17 at 18:00 PST.<br />\n<span class="text-red">Event Small Stamina Boost x300</span> have also been gifted to all players.<br />\n\n* Once the event quest ends, you will be unable to claim or use Event Small Stamina Boosts.\n\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>Duration</h3>\n<div class="holding-period">\nFeb. 17 18:00 - Apr. 29 21:59 PST\n</div>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>How to Play Event Quests</h3>\n\n<p>\n\n\nSave up the <span class="text-red">The Cage of Rebirth Medals</span> you receive for completing quests to trade in at the <span class="text-red">The Cage of Rebirth Medal Exchange</span> for enhancements and other items.<br />\n<br>\nThe more difficult the quest, the more Medals you will earn as a reward.<br />\nAdditionally, using certain characters, costumes, or weapons while playing the event quest will grant you a <span class="text-red">quest bonus</span> that will allow you to play more efficiently.<br>\n\n</p>\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Quest Bonus: Resonant Weapon</h3>\n<p>\nEquipping certain weapons while playing the event quests will grant the <span class="text-red">quest bonus for resonant weapons.</span><br>\nThis bonus <span class="text-red">increases the amount of different kinds of The Cage of Rebirth Medals dropped</span>, depending on the weapon.<br>\nAscending these weapons <span class="text-red">further increases the bonus effect.</span><br>\n<br>\n</p>\n<br />\n\n\n</div>\n<h4>\nQuest Bonus: Resonant Weapons Effect List\n</h4>\n<div class="information_table weapon_table">\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th rowSpan="2" style="width:24%">Weapon</th>\n<th rowSpan="2" style="width:13%; text-align:center;">Medals</th>\n<th colspan="5" style="text-align:center">Ascension Count</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th style="text-align:center">None</th>\n<th style="text-align:center">1</th>\n<th style="text-align:center">2</th>\n<th style="text-align:center">3</th>\n<th style="text-align:center">4</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <th><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/975616e6a0391d6ec97fd1ec733687dc7231a5f4527f7f4198f4215d6027fa50" class="weapon_icon">Wand</th>\n        <td style="text-align:center">\n          <img class="coin_icon" src="/images/en/operations/coin/b0dd4629325e7fd46f5ee720bc75a954e84e08003a44cfa3b53559c01122f91c">\n        </td>\n        <td style="text-align:center">+1</td>\n        <td style="text-align:center">+3</td>\n        <td style="text-align:center">+5</td>\n        <td style="text-align:center">+7</td>\n        <td style="text-align:center">+10</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n\n      \n\n      <th><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/0eaeffe50a5bf25f56daac2cfd53d9e5d3bd1848686c3912fc07ee029db0f0f2" class="weapon_icon">Bramble</th>\n\n<td rowSpan="3" style="text-align:center"><img class="coin_icon" src="/images/en/operations/coin/b0dd4629325e7fd46f5ee720bc75a954e84e08003a44cfa3b53559c01122f91c"><br />\n\n          <img class="coin_icon" src="/images/en/operations/coin/71779da015c5ff4fe624621ed336221ce068a738aeb6a490df6ec410ded8b661">\n          <img class="coin_icon" src="/images/en/operations/coin/3b1d5ad04fc31b5a41996dc8dd3c77faa2afebebf10ea57179a10c2d9f0af5a1">\n        </td>\n\n        \n        </td>\n        <td rowSpan="3" style="text-align:center">+5</td>\n        <td rowSpan="3" style="text-align:center">+11</td>\n        <td rowSpan="3" style="text-align:center">+17</td>\n        <td rowSpan="3" style="text-align:center">+23</td>\n        <td rowSpan="3" style="text-align:center">+30</td>\n      </tr>\n\n       <tr>     \n      <th><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/4e4817dfc70c7e1ee2683f4c9fd7c50fa0d222f003ff048a575c57a46bf81ac4" class="weapon_icon">Alpha and Omega Salute</th>\n      </tr>\n\n      <tr>\n      <th><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/a4e34d92b9538e80a3c20173e835ae8ccc49c467172b0e5fdd8175041db552d6" class="weapon_icon">Crown Rod</th>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div>\n\n<p>\n* Equipping resonant weapons will grant you this bonus regardless of whether they are equipped as primary or secondary weapons.<br>\n* Resonant weapon drop increases will stack if multiple resonant weapons are equipped.\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>Quest Bonus: Resonant Costume</h3>\n\n<p>\n\nUsing certain costumes will grant the <span class="text-red">quest bonus for resonant costumes</span>.<br />\nThese bonuses activate <span class="text-red">various effects</span> for associated costumes when playing the event quests. Plus, some bonuses will have <span class="text-red">increased effects depending on the ascension count</span> of a costume.<br /><br />\n</p>\n\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h4>Quest Bonus: Resonant Costumes Effect List</h4>\n<div class="information_table powerup_rate_table">\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Resonant Costume Characters</th><th>Effect</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>\nRion<br>\n</th><td rowSpan="1" style="text-align:center">Attack＋50%</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n\n\n  </div>\n  <div class="information_table weapon_table">\n  <table>\n   <thead>\n    <tr>\n\n     \n     <th colSpan="5" class="al-center">Resonant Costume "Festive Assassin" and "Festive Ruler" Ascension Count Effect</th>\n　　　　　　　　　\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n\n     <th style="width:10%">None</th>\n     <th style="width:10%">1</th>\n     <th style="width:10%">2</th>\n     <th style="width:10%">3</th>\n     <th style="width:10%">4</th>\n    </tr>\n   </thead>\n   <tbody>\n   　　　　　  　　　　　<tr>\n     \n     <td>Attack<span class="text-red">＋100%</span><br />HP＋50%<br /></td>\n     <td>Attack<span class="text-red">＋125%</span><br />HP＋50%<br /></td>\n     <td>Attack<span class="text-red">＋150%</span><br />HP＋50%<br /></td>\n     <td>Attack<span class="text-red">＋175%</span><br />HP＋50%<br /></td>\n     <td>Attack<span class="text-red">＋200%</span><br />HP＋50%<br /></td>\n\n    </tr>\n     \n    <tr>\n   </tbody>\n  </table>\n </div>\n </section>\n\n\n<section>\n  <div class="information_table weapon_table">\n  <table>\n   <thead>\n    <tr>\n\n     \n     <th colSpan="5" class="al-center">Resonant Costume "Festive Witch" Ascension Count Effect</th>\n　　　　　　　　　\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n\n     <th style="width:10%">None</th>\n     <th style="width:10%">1</th>\n     <th style="width:10%">2</th>\n     <th style="width:10%">3</th>\n     <th style="width:10%">4</th>\n    </tr>\n   </thead>\n   <tbody>\n   　　　　　<tr>                      <td>Character Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+30%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>           <td>Character Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+30%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+10%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>           <td>Character Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+40%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+10%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>           <td>Character Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+40%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+20%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>           <td>Character Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+50%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+20%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>          </tr>\n         \n        <tr>\n     \n    <tr>\n   </tbody>\n  </table>\n </div>\n </section>\n\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Selected Costumes and Resonant Weapons Enhancement Glorious Success Rate Tripled</h3>\n\n\n<p>\n<span class="text-red">The chance of getting a "Glorious Success" result will be tripled</span> when upgrading resonant weapons and <span class="text-red">Akeha</span>, <span class="text-red">Yurie</span>, <span class="text-red">Saryu</span>, and <span class="text-red">Rion</span>''s costumes.<br>\n<br>\n* Excess materials and weapons used in enhancement will be returned if the maximum level is exceeded.<br />\n* This campaign''s effects do not stack with other "Glorious Success" rate up campaigns.<br />\n</p>\n\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>Mama Point Missions</h3>\n<p>\nCompleting missions will earn you <span class="text-red">Mama Points</span>.<br />\nCheck the Special tab on the Missions page for details.<br />\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>\nRaiments of Rebirth Summons</h3>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/21b6d5ed1c75e3ca42c921e62cb5fe4d2e9aa749c3520b944a126d0207f8d9fb">\n</div>\n<br />\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/ca3f415e2d0c0ca22d563c0437f3ee7f3c53e01589a8da6bde45931ce392d283">\n</div>\n<br />\n\n\n<p>\nStarting Feb. 17 at 18:00 PST, the Raiments of Rebirth Summons and the Paid Only: Japanese 3rd Anniversary Multi-Step Summons will be available with <span class="text-red">increased appearance rates for costumes and weapons that grant a quest bonus in "Record: The Cage of Rebirth"</span>.<br />\nPlease check the corresponding notices for more details on these summons.<br>\n</p>\n<div data-category="information" data-informationId="1614" class="other-link-btn common_btn common_button-typeA">Raiments of Rebirth Summons On Now</div>\n<div data-category="information" data-informationId="1615" class="other-link-btn common_btn common_button-typeA">Paid Only: Japanese 3rd Anniversary Multi-Step Summons On Now</div>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>\nNotes\n</h3>\n<div class="attention_content">\n<ul>\n\n\n<li>\nEvent duration and content are subject to change without notice.\n</li>\n<li>\nIllustrations shown in notices, etc. may differ from those in-game.\n</li>\n<li>\nThe rarity, stats, skills, and abilities of characters and weapons displayed in notices, in the summons screen, and on the official X account are shown at maximum levels.\n</li>\n<li>\nYou cannot have more than one character with the same name in the same deck.\n</li>\n<li>\n"Increased rates" means that the character''s appearance rate is higher than that of other characters of the same rarity.\n</li>\n<li>\nOnce the exchange period has passed, <span class="text-red">you will be unable to exchange medals</span>.\n</li>\n<li>\nEvent-specific medals can only be used during the exchange period and <span class="text-red">cannot be carried over to the next event.</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<br>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/a360600bcebdfebbe9127ae162146d888e597f7bef55203f462cd7cb2291abdd','/images/en/operations/banner/fb82c74ccfa11a9d134ebc4d9bf5d31968cfc17e0c99bf3cb214c06a19727f67');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1617,0,4,'Japanese 3rd Anniversary Campaign On Now',1708221600000,replace('<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/7c30a430bb68bc65da78473aa50856296b3344615cdfca985fae27462641162e">\n</div>\n\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n<br />\nThe <span class="text-red">Japanese 3rd Anniversary Campaign</span> will be held from Feb. 17 18:00 PST.<br /></p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Japanese 3rd Anniversary Campaign List</h3>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h4>Japanese 3rd Anniversary Mama''s Dream Summons</h4>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/ffe756ae6c5e405c251755771f8e1035c430d44082ca713cca810b9c97aa6065">\n</div><br>\n\n<div class="holding-period">\nFeb. 17 18:00 - Mar. 7 17:59 PST\n</div>\n<p>\nThe <span class="text-red">Japanese 3rd Anniversary Mama''s Dream Summons</span> will be held.<br />\nYou could win a grand prize of 2,800,000 gems, or other fantastic items in this limited-time event summons.<br />\n<br />\nPlease check the "Japanese 3rd Anniversary Mama''s Dream Summons On Now" notice for more details.\n\n<div data-category="information" data-informationId="1618" class="other-link-btn common_btn common_button-typeA">Japanese 3rd Anniversary Mama''s Dream Summons On Now</div>\n\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<br />\n\n<section>\n<h4>Japanese 3rd Anniversary Oracle Card Login Bonus</h4>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/eff89a291a62cbad480390a8c4cfb118c41199c9cfbc9b8f833c91e9dd42137b">\n</div><br>\n\n<div class="holding-period">\nFeb. 18 0:00 - Mar. 7 23:59 PST\n</div>\n<p>\nThe <span class="text-red">Japanese 3rd Anniversary Oracle Card Login Bonus</span> will be available Feb. 18 0:00 PST.<br />\nBy logging in during the period, you will be able to draw an oracle card once a day.<br />\nThe rewards you earn will depend on the character depicted on the oracle card.<br />\n\n<br />\nPlease check the upcoming "Japanese 3rd Anniv. Oracle Card Login Bonus On Now" notice for more details.\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<br />\n\n\n\n\n<section>\n<h4>Japanese 3rd Anniversary Gifts</h4>\n\n<p>\n<div class="holding-period">\nFeb. 17 18:00 - Mar. 7 17:59 PST\n</div>\n<p>\nAll players will be gifted <span class="text-red">Premium Summon Ticket x28</span>.\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<br>\n\n <section>\n<h4>Japanese 3rd Anniversary Guerrilla Quest Drop Bonus</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nFeb. 17 18:00 - Mar. 7 17:59 PST\n</div>\n<p>\nThe drop rate of all items in the guerrilla quests will increase by <span class="text-red">x10.</span><br>\nIn addition, Clear the guerrilla quest during the campaign period, to always get a guaranteed Large Cursed-God Antler Bit x2 and Large Slab Fragment x2.\n</p>\n</section>\n\n\n<br>\n \n <section>\n <h4>Japanese 3rd Anniversary Guerrilla Quest Stamina 50% Off</h4>\n <div class="holding-period">\nFeb. 17 18:00 - Mar. 7 17:59 PST\n </div>\n \n <p>\nGuerrilla quests will only require <span class="text-red">half the normal amount of stamina</span>.<br>\n <br>\n Note: If the original stamina cost is an odd number, the adjusted cost will be rounded down to the nearest integer.<br>\n \n </p>\n\n \n </section>\n<section>\n<h3>\nNotes\n</h3>\n<div class="attention_content">\n<ul>\n<li>\nDuration and content are subject to change without notice.\n</li>\n<li>\nIllustrations shown in notices, etc. may differ from those in-game.\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</section>\n<br />\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.<br /><br />\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/509f89378283ff24ecc8fcf91488bd3bb08d782d634aa20ec1e247348d0ebe23');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1618,0,3,'Japanese 3rd Anniversary Mama''s Dream Summons On Now',1708221600000,replace('<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/ffe756ae6c5e405c251755771f8e1035c430d44082ca713cca810b9c97aa6065">\n</div>\n\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n<br />\nThe <span class="text-red">Japanese 3rd Anniversary Mama''s Dream Summons</span> has begun as of Feb. 17 18:00 PST.<br />\n\nYou can get up to 2,800,000 gems in this limited-time event summons.\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>Duration</h3>\n<p>\n<div class="holding-period">Feb. 17 18:00 - Mar. 7 17:59 PST</div>\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>Japanese 3rd Anniversary Mama''s Dream Summons</h3>\n\n<p>\nThe Japanese 3rd Anniversary Mama''s Dream Summons can be accessed from the Event Summons screen and requires one <span class="text-red">Mama''s Dream Summon Ticket</span> per 1x summon.<br />\nMama''s Dream Summon Tickets will be added to the <span class="text-red">Once per Day Mama''s Dream Summons Special Quest</span> on Feb. 17 18:00.<br />\n* Once per Day Mama''s Dream Summons Special Quest will be unlocked upon completing Main Quest Ch. 2.<br />\n\n\n</section>\n\n\n</p>\n<section>\n<h3>Obtainable Prizes</h3>\n\n<p>\nSome prizes will only be awarded to a limited number of winners in the Japanese 3rd Anniversary Mama''s Dream Summons, while other prizes are unlimited.<br />\nSince <span class="text-red">the total number of prizes is shared between all users, the number of remaining limited prizes will go down when any player wins them.</span><br />\nWhen all remaining limited prizes reach 0, only unlimited items will appear.<br />\n<br />\n\nThe following items can appear from this summons.\n\n<br/>\n</p>\n<div class="information_table">\n   <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n<p>\n<table>\n    <tbody>\n    <tr><th width="300">Items</td><th>Winners</td></tr>\n      <tr><td><span class="text-red">Gems x2,800,000</span></td><td><span class="text-red">1</span></br> </td></tr>\n      <tr><td><span class="text-red">Gems x280,000</span></td><td><span class="text-red">6</span></br> </td></tr>\n     <tr><td><span class="text-red">Gems x28,000</span></td><td><span class="text-red">100</span></br> </td></tr>\n      <tr><td><span class="text-red">Gems x2,800</span></td><td><span class="text-red">600</span></br> </td></tr>\n      <tr><td><span class="text-red">Gems x280</span></td><td><span class="text-red">6,000</span></br> </td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Karma Stone x10</td><td>Unlimited</br> </td></tr>\n        <tr><td>Verse of Truth x1</td><td>Unlimited</br> </td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Adamant x10</td><td>Unlimited</br> </td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Dark Karma Stone x10</td><td>Unlimited</br> </td></tr>\n        <tr><td>Dark Awakening Stone x1</td><td>Unlimited</br> </td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Insignia of Skill x1</td><td>Unlimited</br> </td></tr>\n        <tr><td>Insignia of Quality x2</td><td>Unlimited</br> </td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Ruby x100</td><td>Unlimited</br> </td></tr>\n        <tr><td>Aquamarine x100</td><td>Unlimited</br> </td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Emerald x100</td><td>Unlimited</br> </td></tr>\n        <tr><td>Topaz x100</td><td>Unlimited</br> </td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Tanzanite x100</td><td>Unlimited</br> </td></tr>\n        <tr><td>Advanced Handbook x10</td><td>Unlimited</br> </td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Black Pearl x1</td><td>Unlimited</br> </td></tr>\n        <tr><td>Zenith''s Brilliance x1</td><td>Unlimited</br> </td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Supreme Adoration x1</td><td>Unlimited</br> </td></tr>\n        <tr><td>Polycrystal of Thought x1</td><td>Unlimited</br> </td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Skip Ticket x10</td><td>Unlimited</br> </td></tr>\n   \n</p>\n      </tbody>\n  </table>\n\n<p>\n<br/>\nCheck remaining stock of each prize from the Japanese 3rd Anniversary Mama''s Dream Summons screen or the Summons Details screen.\n\n<br /><br />\n\n\n* Remaining prizes shown on the summons screen will refresh when you move to another screen and back again.<br />\n* Remaining prizes shown in Summons Details will refresh when reopening the window.<br />\n* Any gems you earn will be sent to your gift box. All other prizes will not be sent to your gift box, but will be added directly to your inventory.\n</p>\n\n</section>\n\n<p>\n<section>\n<h3>\nNotes\n</h3>\n<div class="attention_content">\n<ul>\n<li>\nDuration and content are subject to change without notice.\n</li>\n<li>\nIllustrations shown in notices, etc. may differ from those in-game.\n</li>\n<li>\nAfter the Event Summons ends, <span class="text-red">you will no longer be able to use Event Summon Tickets and they will disappear from your item list.\n</li>\n<li>\nEvent-limited summon tickets will expire and <span class="text-red">cannot be carried over to the next event.</span>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</section>\n<br />\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/6ed863a6d579c90c5973c25a295aebfcd4907f12ce7b6b490a9a0b0bdb0487b9');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1619,0,3,'Daily Summons and Ticket Summons Update',1708243200000,replace('<section>\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.  <br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n<br />\nThe Daily Summons and Ticket Summons were updated on <span class="text-red">Feb. 18 0:00 PST</span>.<br />\n<br />\n<span class="text-red">Weapons and characters up to December 2023</span> have been added to the pool.<br>\nCheck the relevant Summons for more information on rates.<br>\n<span class="text-red">Limited-time weapons/characters and crossover-exclusive weapons/characters are not included</span> in the updated rates.<br />\n</p>\n</section>\n\n\n\n\n\n<section>\n<p>\n\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Notes\n  </h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n    <ul>\n      <li>\n        The rates are equally divided within each rarity category (★★★★ character weapons &amp; ★★★★ weapons only, ★★★ character weapons &amp; ★★★ weapons only).\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        The update''s time and content are subject to change without notice.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        If there are no new additions, there will be no update to the rates.\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1620,0,3,'Healer & Support ★★★★ Guaranteed Summons Updated',1708243200000,replace('<div class="info-largeimage">\n <img src="/images/en/operations/banner/5f7dc0acf6267b6f7d9d98c6c134ec6a4a28d5ffdc428c86b66ca4d9a1763c60">\n </div>\n <p>\n Hello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br /> \n This is a message from the management team.<br />\n <br />\n The <span class="text-red">Healer & Support ★★★★ Guaranteed Summons</span> were updated on Feb. 18 0:00 PST.<br /><br />\n \n The <span class="text-red">Healer and Support ★★★★ Guaranteed Summons</span> is split into two banners based on attribute: <span class="text-red">Fire, Water, Wind Healer & Support ★★★★ Guaranteed Summons</span> and <span class="text-red">Light, Dark Healer & Support ★★★★ Guaranteed Summons</span>. The ★★★★ weapon lineups consist of select <span class="text-red">weapons and characters with Healer or support skills</span>.</br></br>\n \n \n The summons can be used <span class="text-red">only once a day each</span>, with at least one <span class="text-red">★★★★ weapon guaranteed to appear</span>.</br>\n <br />\n The <span class="text-red">Healer & Support Summon Medal Exchange</span> has also begun.<br />\n <span class="text-red">Healer & Support Summon Medals</span> can be earned from either of these summons, and <span class="text-red">100</span> medals can be collected to exchange for a ★★★★ weapon that appears in this summons.<br />\n <br />\n * Check Rates for a list of selected ★★★★ weapons that appear in this summons.<br />\n * No new characters or weapons will appear in this summons.<br />\n \n <section>\n <h3>Duration</h3>\n <h4>Summons</h4>\n <div class="holding-period">\nFeb. 18 0:00 - Apr. 29 21:59 PST\n </div>\n \n \n </section>\n \n \n <section>\n  <h3>\n  Summon Details\n  </h3>\n  <div class="information_table">\n  <table style="width:58%">\n  <thead>\n  <tr>\n  <th style="width:6%">\n  Type\n  </th>\n  <th style="width:12%">\n  Required Gems\n  </th>\n  <th style="width:40%">\n  Healer & Support Summon Medals Received\n  </th>\n  </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n  <tr>\n  <td>\n  x10 summon\n  </td>\n  <td>\n  <img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/gem_icon.png" width="20%">\n  3,000\n  </td>\n  <td>\n  <img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/consumable118170_icon.png" width="6%">\n  10\n  </td>\n  </tr>\n  </tbody>\n  </table>\n  </div>\n \n <p>\n This is a x10 summon that can only be used once a day.<br />\n The <span class="text-red">x10</span> summon will have <span class="text-red">at least one ★★★★ weapon</span> guaranteed.<br />\n ★★★★ weapons that appear are guaranteed to be from the Healer & support lineup.<br />\n * Check Rates on the summons screen for a list of selected ★★★★ weapons that appear in this summons.<br />\n </p>\n \n </section>\n <section>\n <h3>Healer & Support Summon Medal Exchange</h3>\n <h4>Exchange Duration</h4>\n <div class="holding-period">\nFeb. 18 0:00 - Apr. 29 21:59 PST\n </div>\n <p>\n <br />\n You will receive <span class="text-red">Healer & Support Summon Medals</span> each time you use this summons.<br />\n You can exchange <span class="text-red">100 summon medals</span> at the Healer & Support Summon Medal Exchange and choose from a selection of eligible ★★★★ weapons.<br />\n Please check the Healer & Support Summon Medal Exchange for eligible ★★★★ weapons that can be exchanged.<br />\n <br />\n \n\n * If you exchange for a character weapon you already own, you will earn <span class="text-red">10 ascension materials and 1 Awakening Stone for the character in addition to the weapon</span>.<br /><br />\n \n <p/>\n </section>\n \n <section>\n  <h3>\n  Notes\n  </h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n  <ul>\n  <li>\n  Event periods and content are subject to change without notice.\n  </li>\n  <li>\n  Illustrations shown in notices, etc. may differ from those in-game.\n  </li>\n  <li>\n  The rarity, stats, skills, and abilities of characters and weapons displayed on the summons screen and on the official X account are shown at maximum levels.\n  </li>\n  <li>\n  You cannot have more than one character with the same name in the same deck.\n  </li>\n  <li>\n  Refer to Rates to confirm which characters and weapons can appear in this summons.\n  </li>\n  <li>\n  For more information about rates, please check the Rates button on the summon page.\n  </li>\n <li>\n  <span class="text-red">No characters or weapons will have featured rates.</span>\n </li>\n  </ul>\n  </div>\n <br />\n </section>\n <section>\n <p>\n Thank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n </p>\n </section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/5f7dc0acf6267b6f7d9d98c6c134ec6a4a28d5ffdc428c86b66ca4d9a1763c60','/images/en/operations/banner/5dc0760b73bf0b106ea78fd3b233dbc7a0e8ca1627c86c53794f15f169c1a2b3');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1621,0,4,'Japanese 3rd Anniversary Oracle Card Login Bonus On Now',1708243200000,replace('<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/eff89a291a62cbad480390a8c4cfb118c41199c9cfbc9b8f833c91e9dd42137b">\n</div>\n\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.  <br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n<br />\nThe <span class="text-red">Japanese 3rd Anniversar Oracle Card Login Bonus</span> started on Feb. 18 0:00 PST.<br />\n</p>\n\n<h4>Duration</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nFeb. 18 0:00 - Mar. 7 23:59 PST\n</div>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n\n<p>\nBy logging in during the period, you will be able to draw an oracle card once a day.<br />\nThe rewards you earn will depend on the character depicted on the oracle card.<br />\nIf you do not pull a Mama card by the 18th attempt, <span class="text-red">you are guaranteed one on the 19th attempt</span>.<br />\n</p>\n\n<div class="information_table">\n  <table>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <th width=120>Character</td>\n        <th>Rewards</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Mama</td>\n        <td>Skip Ticket x200<br/>\nSmall Stamina Recovery x300<br/>\n<span class="text-red">Karma Stone x100</span><br/>\n<span class="text-red">Dark Karma Stone x100</span></span>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td><span class="text-red">10H</span></td>\n        <td>Moldavite x50<br/>\nSkip Ticket x20<br/>\nSmall Stamina Recovery x50<br/>\nXL Character Enhancement x1,000<br/>\nXL Weapon Enhancement x1,000</td>\n      </tr>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Exile</td>\n        <td>Topaz x50<br/>\nSkip Ticket x20<br/>\nSmall Stamina Recovery x50<br/>\nXL Character Enhancement x1,000<br/>\nXL Weapon Enhancement x1,000</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Hunter</td>\n        <td>Gold Coin x500<br/>\nSkip Ticket x20<br/>\nSmall Stamina Recovery x50<br/>\nXL Character Enhancement x1,000<br/>\nXL Weapon Enhancement x1,000</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Gunman</td>\n        <td>XL Battery x200<br/>\nSkip Ticket x20<br/>\nSmall Stamina Recovery x50<br/>\nXL Character Enhancement x1,000<br/>\nXL Weapon Enhancement x1,000</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Assassin</td>\n        <td>Tanzanite x50<br/>\nSkip Ticket x20<br/>\nSmall Stamina Recovery x50<br/>\nXL Character Enhancement x1,000<br/>\nXL Weapon Enhancement x1,000</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Traveler</td>\n        <td>Explorer''s Ticket x50<br/>\nSkip Ticket x20<br/>\nSmall Stamina Recovery x50<br/>\nXL Character Enhancement x1,000<br/>\nXL Weapon Enhancement x1,000</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Monster</td>\n        <td>Large Stamina Recovery x10<br/>\nSkip Ticket x20<br/>\nSmall Stamina Recovery x50<br/>\nXL Character Enhancement x1,000<br/>\nXL Weapon Enhancement x1,000</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Prisoner</td>\n        <td>Piece: Black Pearl x2<br/>\nSkip Ticket x20<br/>\nSmall Stamina Recovery x50<br/>\nXL Character Enhancement x1,000<br/>\nXL Weapon Enhancement x1,000</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Captive</td>\n        <td>Piece: Black Pearl x2<br/>\nSkip Ticket x20<br/>\nSmall Stamina Recovery x50<br/>\nXL Character Enhancement x1,000<br/>\nXL Weapon Enhancement x1,000</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Soldier</td>\n        <td>Small BP Recovery x100<br/>\nSkip Ticket x20<br/>\nSmall Stamina Recovery x50<br/>\nXL Character Enhancement x1,000<br/>\nXL Weapon Enhancement x1,000</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Captain</td>\n        <td>Superb-quality Ink x200<br/>\nSkip Ticket x20<br/>\nSmall Stamina Recovery x50<br/>\nXL Character Enhancement x1,000<br/>\nXL Weapon Enhancement x1,000</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Weapon</td>\n        <td>Supreme Adoration x1<br/>\nSkip Ticket x20<br/>\nSmall Stamina Recovery x50<br/>\nXL Character Enhancement x1,000<br/>\nXL Weapon Enhancement x1,000</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Girl</td>\n        <td>Medium Slab Fragment x100<br/>\nSkip Ticket x20<br/>\nSmall Stamina Recovery x50<br/>\nXL Character Enhancement x1,000<br/>\nXL Weapon Enhancement x1,000</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Witch</td>\n        <td>XL Feather Duster x200<br/>\nSkip Ticket x20<br/>\nSmall Stamina Recovery x50<br/>\nXL Character Enhancement x1,000<br/>\nXL Weapon Enhancement x1,000</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Werebeast</td>\n        <td>Ruby x50<br/>\nSkip Ticket x20<br/>\nSmall Stamina Recovery x50<br/>\nXL Character Enhancement x1,000<br/>\nXL Weapon Enhancement x1,000</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Songstress</td>\n        <td>Premium Summon Ticket x3<br/>\nSkip Ticket x20<br/>\nSmall Stamina Recovery x50<br/>\nXL Character Enhancement x1,000<br/>\nXL Weapon Enhancement x1,000</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Ruler</td>\n        <td>XL Circuit x200<br/>\nSkip Ticket x20<br/>\nSmall Stamina Recovery x50<br/>\nXL Character Enhancement x1,000<br/>\nXL Weapon Enhancement x1,000</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Boor</td>\n        <td>Aquamarine x50<br/>\nSkip Ticket x20<br/>\nSmall Stamina Recovery x50<br/>\nXL Character Enhancement x1,000<br/>\nXL Weapon Enhancement x1,000</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Belle</td>\n        <td>Emerald x50<br/>\nSkip Ticket x20<br/>\nSmall Stamina Recovery x50<br/>\nXL Character Enhancement x1,000<br/>\nXL Weapon Enhancement x1,000</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Student</td>\n        <td>Valuable Refining Agent x50<br/>\nSkip Ticket x20<br/>\nSmall Stamina Recovery x50<br/>\nXL Character Enhancement x1,000<br/>\nXL Weapon Enhancement x1,000</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Pupil</td>\n        <td>Stainless Steel Wire x50<br/>\nSkip Ticket x20<br/>\nSmall Stamina Recovery x50<br/>\nXL Character Enhancement x1,000<br/>\nXL Weapon Enhancement x1,000</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div>\n\n<p>\n*Login resets at 0:00 PST every day.<br />\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Notes\n  </h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n      <li>\n        During the period, you can draw oracle cards up to 19 times.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        The rewards will be sent to your gift box.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        If the login bonus does not start, please try restarting the app.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Event duration and content are subject to change without notice.\n      </li>\n\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n<br />\n</section>\n\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/4ce78890cfcde5d496737f501c31c4deed1805df607a91d79791fab666df051e');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1623,0,7,'Arena Season 037 On Now',1708394400000,replace('<section>\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation. <br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n<br />\nArena <span class="text-red">Season 037</span> of the Arena was made available starting Feb. 19 18:00 PST.\n</p>\n\n<h3>Changes</h3>\n<p>\n- Merge into one group.\n</p>\n\n\n<h3>Starting Arena Point</h3>\n<p>\nPlayers'' starting Arena Points will change depending on their <span class="text-red">total force.</span><br />\nThis is applicable to players who began playing the Arena prior to Feb. 25 23:59 PST and reached over a specific total force.<br />\n</p>\n   <div class="information_table weapon_table">\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n\n          <th style="width:10%">Total Force</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">Starting Arena Points</th>\n\n\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n   　　　　　<tr>\n          <td>320,000 or over</td>\n          <td>36,000</td>\n        </tr>\n\n   　　　　　<tr>\n          <td>220,000 and over, but under 320,000</td>\n          <td>29,000</td>\n        </tr>\n\n   　　　　　<tr>\n          <td>120,000 and over, but under 220,000</td>\n          <td>22,000</td>\n        </tr>\n\n   　　　　　<tr>\n          <td>Under 120,000</td>\n          <td>18,000</td>\n        </tr>\n\n        <tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n<p>\nNote: As long as you have completed the <span class="text-red">"Reach XXXX total force"</span> mission in the challenge tab, your total force will be counted even if your current loadout has a lower total force.<br />\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>Duration</h3>\n<p>Season 037 will be open during the following period.</p>\n<br />\n<div class="holding-period">Feb. 19 18:00 - Mar. 31 23:59 PST</div>\n</section>\n\n\n</p>\n<section>\n<h3>Notes</h3>\n<div class="attention_content">\n<ul>\n<li>Event duration and content are subject to change without notice.</li>\n<li>If you do not participate in the Arena, you may not receive the Arena weekly rewards.</li>\n<li>If a battle goes past 0:00 on Monday, Arena Points will not be awarded for that battle.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n<br />\n<section>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1624,0,7,'Shop Medal Exchange Updated',1708243200000,replace('<p>\n Hello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation. <br />\n This is a message from the management team.<br />\n <br />\nThe <span class="text-red">Shop Medal Exchange</span> was updated on Feb. 18 0:00 PST.<br />\n\n</p>\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Update Details</h3>\n<p>The following characters have been added for shop medal exchange.</p></br>\n\n<h4>Character</h4>\n<p><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/a0c860955b3f71cdd744fa5069ff4f149434592b2f371157a58813b97d5745d5" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Sarafa (Shadowbound Belle)<br />\n<p><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/1967cd236b5b2b5ae27f0fa99cc330f6bda5c30bf28a1056e56298451f5f0259" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Yuzuki (Abstract Student)<br />\n<br />\n</section>\n \n <section>\n <p>\n Thank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n </p>\n </section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1629,0,4,'Dark Character Unlock Campaign On Now',1708221600000,replace('<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/c4aad1eb0ad587447d62b6bd34ad8bf07add0bf1cfb4ebd7f86c23a07bcb0975">\n</div>\n\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n<br />\nThe <span class="text-red">Dark Character Unlock Campaign</span> started on Feb. 17 18:00 PST.<br /></p>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>Dark Character Unlock Campaign List</h3>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n</div>\n\n<br>\n\n<section>\n<h4>Dark Character Unlock Login Bonus</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nFeb. 18 0:00 - Apr. 29 21:59 PST\n</div>\n\n <p>\n Get <span class="text-red">Zenith''s Brilliance</span> from a new login bonus.<br>\n </p>\n <div class="information_table">\n  <table>\n  <tbody>\n  <tr>\n  <th width="120">Day</td>\n  <th>Rewards</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n  <td>Day 1</td>\n  <td>Zenith''s Brilliance x1</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n  <td>Day 2</td>\n  <td>Zenith''s Brilliance x1</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n  <td>Day 3</td>\n  <td>Zenith''s Brilliance x2</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n  <td>Day 4</td>\n  <td>Zenith''s Brilliance x2</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n  <td>Day 5</td>\n  <td><span class="text-red">Zenith''s Brilliance x3</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n  <td>Day 6</td>\n  <td>Zenith''s Brilliance x2</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n  <td>Day 7</td>\n  <td>Zenith''s Brilliance x2</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n  <td>Day 8</td>\n  <td>Zenith''s Brilliance x2</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n  <td>Day 9</td>\n  <td>Zenith''s Brilliance x2</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n  <td>Day 10</td>\n  <td><span class="text-red">Zenith''s Brilliance x3</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  </table>\n </div>\n <p>\n Note: You can receive login bonuses by going to Mama''s Room or The Cage.<br />\n Note: Login resets at 0:00 PST every day.<br />\n Note: You can retrieve your rewards by logging in during the period before Apr. 29 PST.<br>\n </p>\n <br>\n \n </section>\n\n<br>\n\n<section>\n<h4>Dark Character Unlock Event Exchange</h4>\n</div><br>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n\n</div>\n<div class="holding-period">\nFeb. 17 18:00 - Apr. 29 21:59 PST\n</div>\n<p>\nUp to <span class="text-red">Zenith''s Brilliance x40</span> can be obtained from The Cage of Rebirth Medal Exchange.\n</p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Notes\n  </h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n    <ul>\n      <li>\n        Event duration and content are subject to change without notice.\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n<br />\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/c4aad1eb0ad587447d62b6bd34ad8bf07add0bf1cfb4ebd7f86c23a07bcb0975','/images/en/operations/banner/abb938a9a3699b4092551e1a637185ccbe5af32f46c605658e82fa3526efc8a2');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1631,0,2,'Resurrected Event Quest "Record: Foundation of Fortune" On Now',1708653600000,replace('<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/68902ad6e4ff269c62130f4a7ca7d481d04235f852fb579bafb96a8c58548e21">\n</div>\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n<br />\nThe Resurrected Event Quest <span class="text-red">"Record: Foundation of Fortune"</span> has begun as of Feb. 22 18:00 PST.<br />\n<span class="text-red">Event Small Stamina Boost x300</span> have also been gifted to all players.<br />\n\n* Once the event quest ends, you will be unable to claim or use Event Small Stamina Boosts.\n\n</p>\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Duration</h3>\n<div class="holding-period">Feb. 22 18:00 - Mar. 10 17:59 PST</div>\n<p>\n* The Exchange can be used until two days after the event duration ends. Please see the Exchange in game for details.\n</p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>How to Play Event Quests</h3>\n\n<p>\nSave up the <span class="text-red">Foundation of Fortune Medals</span> you receive for completing quests to trade in at the <span class="text-red">Foundation of Fortune Medal Exchange</span> for the enhancements and other items.<br />\n<br>\nThe more difficult the quest, the more Medals you will earn as a reward.<br />\n</p>\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Countdown Resurrected Event Medal Exchange</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nFeb. 8 18:00 - Apr. 29 21:59 PST\n</div>\n\n<p>\nIn addition to the event-specific medals, Countdown Resurrected Event Medals are available at EX Hard difficulty for each Resurrected Event held during the period.<br>\nSave up the <span class="text-red">Countdown Resurrected Event Medals</span> you receive for completing quests to trade in at the <span class="text-red">Countdown Resurrected Event Medal Exchange</span> for an event-exclusive costumes, as well as enhancements and other items.<br />\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Notes\n  </h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n    <ul>\n\n \n<li>\n        Event duration and content are subject to change without notice.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Illustrations shown in notices, etc. may differ from those in-game.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        The rarity, stats, skills, and abilities of characters and weapons displayed in notices, in the summons screen, and on the official X account are shown at maximum levels.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        You cannot have more than one character with the same name in the same deck.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Once the exchange period has passed, <span class="text-red">you will be unable to exchange medals</span>.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Event-specific medals can only be used during the exchange period and <span class="text-red">cannot be carried over to the next event.</span>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<br>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/c704354d1ccdfd150ebcc8f9f71dfeb9cb738277bab0a8db67e2ed062bf76f96');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1635,0,2,'Resurrected Event Quest "Record: Happy Home" On Now',1709172000000,replace('<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/5bb839e87224494376cc56fb5bc4e22bb74b1d395565aad0ed2e832a634af83d">\n</div>\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n<br />\nThe Resurrected Event Quest <span class="text-red">"Record: Happy Home"</span> has begun as of Feb. 28 18:00 PST.<br />\n<span class="text-red">Event Small Stamina Boost x300</span> have also been gifted to all players.<br />\n\n* Once the event quest ends, you will be unable to claim or use Event Small Stamina Boosts.\n\n</p>\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Duration</h3>\n<div class="holding-period">Feb. 28 18:00 - Mar. 17 17:59 PST</div>\n<p>\n* The Exchange can be used until two days after the event duration ends. Please see the Exchange in game for details.\n</p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>How to Play Event Quests</h3>\n\n<p>\nSave up the <span class="text-red">Happy Home Medals</span> you receive for completing quests to trade in at the <span class="text-red">Happy Home Medal Exchange</span> for the enhancements and other items.<br />\n<br>\nThe more difficult the quest, the more Medals you will earn as a reward.<br />\n</p>\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Countdown Resurrected Event Medal Exchange</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nFeb. 8 18:00 - Apr. 29 21:59 PST\n</div>\n\n<p>\nIn addition to the event-specific medals, Countdown Resurrected Event Medals are available at EX Hard difficulty for each Resurrected Event held during the period.<br>\nSave up the <span class="text-red">Countdown Resurrected Event Medals</span> you receive for completing quests to trade in at the <span class="text-red">Countdown Resurrected Event Medal Exchange</span> for an event-exclusive costumes, as well as enhancements and other items.<br />\n</p>\n</section>\n\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Mama Point Missions</h3>\n<p>\nCompleting missions will earn you <span class="text-red">Mama Points</span>.<br />\nCheck the Special tab on the Missions page for details.<br />\n</p>\n</section>\n\n\n\n\n\n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Notes\n  </h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n    <ul>\n\n \n<li>\n        Event duration and content are subject to change without notice.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Illustrations shown in notices, etc. may differ from those in-game.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        The rarity, stats, skills, and abilities of characters and weapons displayed in notices, in the summons screen, and on the official X account are shown at maximum levels.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        You cannot have more than one character with the same name in the same deck.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Once the exchange period has passed, <span class="text-red">you will be unable to exchange medals</span>.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Event-specific medals can only be used during the exchange period and <span class="text-red">cannot be carried over to the next event.</span>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<br>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/5f95ac265aab93ca58664ce71522091fe96c2d4570f8bbf0f97ffd665f48b6a9');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1640,0,4,'Support Campaigns in March',1709280000000,replace('<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/04e2679a33dd5eb53c46e2f4f14408a9efe5c48ab32ccfc0f37d1fcda3b7ec89">\n</div>\n<p>\n Hello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br /> \n This is a message from the management team.<br />\n <br />\n The <span class="text-red">Support Campaigns</span> for March has begun as of Mar. 1 0:00 PST.<br />\n Details of each campaign are as follows.\n </p>\n\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>Support Campaign List for March</h3>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/7a875158bfa3313992a649a83d7bf0b5919df4edd9eeab6f1441af04d4f5237d">\n</div>\n\n<section>\n<h4>Main & Guerrilla Quest Support Campaign</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nMar. 1 0:00 - Mar. 10 23:59 PST\n</div>\n\n<p>\n-The drop rate of all items in the main quest and guerrilla quest will increase by <span class="text-red">x3.</span><br>\n-The stamina cost for main quest and guerrilla quest will be <span class="text-red">halved</span>.<br>\n-At least one <span class="text-red">Small Slab Fragment and Medium Slab Fragment</span> will drop from story quests.<br>\n</p>\n\n</section>\n\n<br>\n\n<section>\n<h4>Memoir Collection and Enhancement Support Campaign</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nMar. 11 0:00 - Mar. 20 23:59 PST\n</div>\n<p>\n-The drop rate of all items in dungeons will increase by <span class="text-red">x3.</span><br>\n-The stamina cost for dungeons will be <span class="text-red">halved</span>.<br>\n-<span class="text-red">"Success" will be guaranteed</span> when enhancing memoirs.<br>\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<br>\n\n\n<section>\n<h4>Dark Memories & Daily Quest Support Campaign</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nMar. 21 0:00 - Mar. 31 23:59 PST\n</div>\n\n<p>\n-The drop rate of all items in the daily quests, Dark Coin Quest and EX Ticket Quest will increase by <span class="text-red">x3</span>.<br>\n-The stamina cost for dark memories quests and daily quests will be <span class="text-red">halved</span>.<br>\n-Completing specific quests in any of the Dark Memory quests, at least one <span class="text-red">Recalling Light</span> will be a guaranteed drop.<br>\n</p>\n\n</section>\n\n<br>\n\n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Notes\n  </h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n    <ul>\n      <li>\n        When the stamina cost is halved from an odd number, the decimal number will be rounded down to the lower value. \n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Event duration and content are subject to change without notice.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        The campaigns may reappear in the future.\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n<br />\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/04e2679a33dd5eb53c46e2f4f14408a9efe5c48ab32ccfc0f37d1fcda3b7ec89','/images/en/operations/banner/addfbd1a2ddb833f8ec8279da2a35c746a665087a4e59ccbe346e7ba0333dd0c');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1641,0,4,'Mama Point Mission Update',1709280000000,replace('<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/fdc48fed255c98cd12549f1c6a1d0067a721fa22580b7c631d726e5f3dfabaa2">\n</div>\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.  <br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n<br />\nThe <span class="text-red">Mama Point Missions</span> have updated on Mar. 1 0:00 PST.<br />\nMission rewards that have been cleared but not yet claimed when <span class="text-red">Mama Point Missions</span> are updated will not be available after the update. Please claim rewards before then.\n</p>\n</section>\n\n\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>How to Play Mama Point Missions</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>\n<span class="text-red">Mama Points</span> are special points that can be earned by completing missions.<br />\nSave up Mama Points to trade in for <span class="text-red">Remnants</span>, <span class="text-red">Premium Summons Ticket x10</span>, and other items.<br />\n<span class="text-red">Excluding Remnants</span>, the items at the Exchange will refresh every 1st of the month at 0:00 PST.<br />\nMore Remnants will be added to the Exchange at a later date.<br /><br /></p>\n\n<h4>About Remnants</h4>\n<p>\nAcquiring Remnants will raise the stats of the corresponding character.<br />\nWhile they come at a high cost, Remnant boosts apply to all your acquired costumes for one character.<br />\n<br />\n\n* View your acquired Remnants on the Important tab in View List/Sell or in Extra Stories in the Library.<br />\n* You can acquire <span class="text-red">up to 3,500</span> Mama Points per month. For this reason, <span class="text-red">you may not be able to trade for all the items at the Exchange</span>.<br />\n* Mama Point Missions will take the place of previously held Mama Medal Marathons.<br />\n\n<br />\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>Mama Point Missions</h3>\n<p>\nMama Points can be earned by completing missions related to the Arena, Subjugation Battles, events, and more. Event-related missions will be added when each event opens.<br />\n* Please check the Special tab on the Missions page for details.<br />\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Notes\n  </h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n      <li>\n        Duration and content are subject to change without notice.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Some of the items in the Exchange will <span class="text-red">refresh the 1st of every month at 0:00 PST</span>.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Mama Points will not expire and can be used during any month.</span>\n      </li>\n</span>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n<br />\n</section>\n\n\n\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/fdc48fed255c98cd12549f1c6a1d0067a721fa22580b7c631d726e5f3dfabaa2','/images/en/operations/banner/3492e45864b191e11da8a8d273abac84edfaec11169a41a041908fcc1f7deb66');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1642,0,7,'Karma Added to More Costumes',1709431200000,replace('<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/004f8882fef98fa953e5a5d807b3c8009f35d0f37f67987e257fc0c02d17c3f0">\n</div>\n\n<p>\n Hello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\n This is a message from the management team.<br />\n <br />\nAdded Karma to certain costumes on Mar. 2 PST.<br>\n</p>\n\n<h3>Affected Costumes</h3>\n<p>\n・Dimos (Bloody Gunman)<br>\n・Saryu (Bloody Witch)<br>\n・Lars (Bloody Soldier)<br>\n・Gayle (Bloody Hunter)<br>\n・F66x (Bloody Captive)<br>\n・Argo (Bloody Traveler)<br>\n・Akeha (Bloody Assassin)<br>\n・Griff (Bloody Captain)<br>\n・Noelle (Bloody Weapon)<br>\n・Levania (Bloody Monster)<br>\n・063y (Fractured Prisoner)<br>\n・Akeha (Fractured Assassin)<br>\n・Argo (Fractured Traveler)<br>\n・Lars (Fractured Soldier)<br>\n・Dimos (Fractured Gunman)<br>\n・Noelle (Fractured Weapon)<br>\n・Gayle (Fractured Hunter)<br>\n・Griff (Fractured Captain)<br>\n・Marie (Fractured Songstress)<br>\n</p>\n\n\n<section>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/004f8882fef98fa953e5a5d807b3c8009f35d0f37f67987e257fc0c02d17c3f0','/images/en/operations/banner/bf9803c9aea56fce22b7096852e83cbbbef53b6f33dcc503a989e315c56ee5de');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1645,0,3,'Abstract Savior Summons On Now',1709863200000,replace('<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/de7b4f1dfd2437043c57f11f42fded823a09c1419a63174ef2d378d532cfea6b">\n</div>\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n<br />\nThe <span class="text-red">Abstract Savior Summons</span> is now available as of Mar. 7 18:00 PST.<br />\nThe <span class="text-red">Shard (Abstract Savior) Exchange</span> has also begun.\n</p>\n\n<h3>Duration</h3>\n<h4>Summons</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nMar. 7 18:00 - Apr. 29 21:59 PST\n</div>\n<br />\n</section>\n\n\n\n<section>\n\n<h3>Featured Characters &amp; Weapons</h3>\n<p>In this summons, the <span class="text-red">following new characters and weapons have increased (featured) rates</span>.<br />\n\n\n\nInformation on stats, skills, and abilities can be found on the summons screen.</p>\n\n<h4>New Character</h4>\n<p>\n<img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/></p>\n\n<p><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/220f6eb74c5aca6c4a26e68cbd4f09e61055c421f595cb3c2ab3ab8097f6fa6c" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> 10H (Abstract Savior)<br />\n* You can get this character by acquiring the <span class="text-red">Deus Ex Machina</span> weapon.</p>\n<br />\n\n\n<h4>New Weapons</h4>\n<p><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/></p>\n\n<p><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/b2f80a38e0b1175260f69f020d62a0c9113b895414187be36710f85f8ce878f5" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Deus Ex Machina<br /></p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>\nSummons Details\n</h3>\n<div class="information_table">\n<table style="width:58%">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style="width:6%">\nType\n</th>\n<th style="width:12%">\nRequired Gems\n</th>\n<th style="width:40%">\nObtainable Shards<br> (Abstract Savior)\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n1x summon\n</td>\n<td>\n<img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/gem_icon.png" width="20%"> 300\n</td>\n<td>\n1\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n10x summon\n</td>\n<td>\n<img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/gem_icon.png" width="20%"> 3,000\n</td>\n<td>\n 10\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>\n<span class="text-red">At least one ★★★ or higher weapon is guaranteed</span> in each <span class="text-red">10x summon</span>.<br />\nNote: You will also earn the appropriate number of shards (Abstract Savior) for summons performed using premium summon tickets (including 10x summon tickets).\n</p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>About Shards (Abstract Savior)</h3>\n<p>\nYou will earn <span class="text-red">shards (Abstract Savior)</span> each time you use the Abstract Savior Summons.<br />\nThese items can be used at the Shard (Abstract Savior) Exchange to acquire new characters and weapons.<br />\n<br />\n* The Exchange <span class="text-red">is only available for a limited time.</span> Once the exchange period ends, you will be unable to exchange shards.<br />\n* Once the exchange period ends, each remaining shard <span class="text-red">will be converted into a bookmark</span> upon entering the summons screen.<br />\n* If you exchange for a character weapon you already own, you will earn <span class="text-red">10 ascension materials and 1 Awakening Stone for the character in addition to the weapon</span>.<br />\n* Shards can only be used at the exchange of the same name.<br />\n* You can earn shards from both the Abstract Savior Summons and the Paid Only: Abstract Savior Multi-Step Summons.<br />\n* You will also earn shards for summons performed using premium summon tickets (including 10x summon tickets).<br />\n\n\n<p/>\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Resonant Costume Bonuses in Subjugation Battles</h3>\n<p>\n\nSeason 008 of Subjugation Battles will have a resonant costume quest bonus. The bonus effect of the resonant costumes <span class="text-red">reduces cooldown time for weapon skills in certain Subjugation Battle quests</span> and <span class="text-red">activates an attack increase based on the ascension count</span>.<br />\n</p>\n\n</section>\n<section>\n\n<div class="information_table weapon_table">\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n\n\n<th colSpan="5" class="al-center">Ascension Count and Effects</th>\n\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\n<th style="width:10%">None</th>\n<th style="width:10%">1</th>\n<th style="width:10%">2</th>\n<th style="width:10%">3</th>\n<th style="width:10%">4</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n\n<td>Attack <span class="text-red">+25%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n+10%<br /></td>\n<td>Attack <span class="text-red">+30%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n+10%<br /></td>\n<td>Attack <span class="text-red">+35%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n+10%<br /></td>\n<td>Attack <span class="text-red">+40%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n+10%<br /></td>\n<td>Attack <span class="text-red">+50%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n+10%<br /></td>\n\n</tr>\n\n\n<tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n</section>\n<br />\n\n\n<section>\n<h4>Quest Bonus: Resonant Costume Effect</h4>\n<div class="information_table powerup_rate_table">\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>\nResonant Costume\n</th>\n<th>\nQuests\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>\n<img class="chara_image" src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/220f6eb74c5aca6c4a26e68cbd4f09e61055c421f595cb3c2ab3ab8097f6fa6c" alt=""> 10H (Abstract Savior)\n</th>\n\n<td>\n<span class="text-red"> Manifestation: Bright Cursed God</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n\n\n\n\n</table>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Event Quest Bonuses</h3>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/a360600bcebdfebbe9127ae162146d888e597f7bef55203f462cd7cb2291abdd">\n</div>\n<p>\nThe characters and weapons featured in this summons grant <span class="text-red">quest bonuses</span> in the event quest "Record: The Cage of Rebirth". Playing the quest with them will activate <span class="text-red">various effects</span> for your characters, and some effects will <span class="text-red">increase depending on the ascension count</span>.<br />\n\n\n<section>\n<h4>Quest Bonus: Resonant Costumes Effect List</h4>\n   <div class="information_table weapon_table">\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n\n         \n          <th colSpan="5" class="al-center">Resonant Costume "Abstract Savior" Ascension Count Effect</th>\n　　　　　　　　　\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n\n          <th style="width:10%">None</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">1</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">2</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">3</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">4</th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n   　　　　　<tr>                      <td>Character Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+30%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>           <td>Character Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+30%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+10%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>           <td>Character Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+40%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+10%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>           <td>Character Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+40%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+20%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>           <td>Character Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+50%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+20%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>          </tr>\n         \n        <tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n\n\n<br />\n<p>\nThe number of The Cage of Rebirth Medals dropped <span class="text-red">will increase</span> depending on the weapon.</span><br />\n</p>\n\n</div>\n<h4> Quest Bonus: Resonance Weapon Effect</h4>\n<div class="information_table weapon_table">\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th rowSpan="2" style="width:28%">Weapon</th>\n<th colspan="5" style="text-align:center">Ascension Count</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th style="text-align:center">None</th>\n<th style="text-align:center">1</th>\n<th style="text-align:center">2</th>\n<th style="text-align:center">3</th>\n<th style="text-align:center">4</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/b2f80a38e0b1175260f69f020d62a0c9113b895414187be36710f85f8ce878f5" class="weapon_icon"> Deus Ex Machina</th>\n<td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center">+5</td>\n<td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center">+11</td>\n<td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center">+17</td>\n<td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center">+23</td>\n<td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center">+30</td>\n</tr>\n\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<br />\n<p>\nCheck the "Event Quest: ''Record: The Cage of Rebirth'' On Now" notice for more information.\n<p/>\n<div data-category="information" data-informationId="1616" class="other-link-btn common_btn common_button-typeA">Event Quest "Record: The Cage of Rebirth" On Now</div>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<div class="mama_balloon">\n<div class="mama_img">\n<img src="/images/common/other/webview_parts_mama.png" alt="">\n</div>\n<div class="balloon">We found these memories together.<br/>\nMemories slumbering in the same place within The Cage tend to interfere with one another, you see.</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>\nNotes\n</h3>\n<div class="attention_content">\n<ul>\n<li>\nEvent duration and content are subject to change without notice.\n</li>\n<li>\nIllustrations shown in notices, etc. may differ from those in-game.\n</li>\n<li>\nThe rarity, stats, skills, and abilities of characters and weapons displayed on the summons screen and on the official X account are shown at maximum levels.\n</li>\n<li>\n"Increased rates" means that the character''s appearance rate is higher than that of other characters of the same rarity.\n</li>\n<li>\n<span class="text-red">10H (Abstract Savior) &amp; Deus Ex Machina cannot be obtained with ★★★+ Tickets or ★★★★ Premium Summons Tickets. However, they may be added in future updates.</span>\n</li>\n<li>\nYou cannot have more than one character with the same name in the same deck.\n</li>\n<li>\nFor more information about rates, please check the Rates button on the summons page.\n</li>\n<li>\nIf you perform a summons using the 10x summon button, a ★★★ or higher weapon will always appear on the 10th summon, regardless of the results of the first 9 summons.\n</li>\n<li>\nThe video clip that plays when pressing the Skill button was recorded in a development environment.\n</li>\n<li>\nShards can only be used during the exchange period and cannot be carried over.\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<br />\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/de7b4f1dfd2437043c57f11f42fded823a09c1419a63174ef2d378d532cfea6b','/images/en/operations/banner/b9a464ae157f0db940c2a53d5270931e57bb306027250f7413697411c9eb62f6');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1646,0,3,'Paid Only: Abstract Savior Multi-Step Summons On Now',1709863200000,replace('<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/a78b1fa5b227ee01e9b232c1e3abd375b80f983e4b1f9d0772a27b2f52a74a94">\n</div>\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n<br />\nThe <span class="text-red">Paid Only: Abstract Savior Multi-Step Summons</span> is now available as of Mar. 7 18:00 PST.<br />\n<span class="text-red">All ★★★★ weapons that appear are guaranteed to be featured weapons</span> in these summons.<br />\nThe rates for ★★★★ weapons will be <span class="text-red">1.5x</span> greater than the <span class="text-red">Abstract Savior Summons</span>.<br />\n</span>Also <span class="text-red">10H (Abstract Savior) will be guaranteed</span> on Step 4 in the 10th slot.<br /><br />\nFor every 10x summons you perform, you''ll get <span class="text-red">Piece: Black Pearl x2</span> as a bonus.<br /><br />\n\nThe <span class="text-red">Shard (Abstract Savior) Exchange</span> has also begun.<br />\nPlease check the summons details for more information on each step.<br />\n</p>\n\n<h3>Duration</h3>\n<h4>Summons</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nMar. 7 18:00 - Apr. 29 21:59 PST\n</div>\n</section>\n\n\n\n<section>\n\n<h3>Featured Characters &amp; Weapons</h3>\n<p>In this summons, the <span class="text-red">following new characters and weapons have increased (featured) rates</span>.<br />\n\n\n\nInformation on stats, skills, and abilities can be found on the summons screen.</p>\n\n<h4>New Character</h4>\n<p>\n<img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/></p>\n\n<p><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/220f6eb74c5aca6c4a26e68cbd4f09e61055c421f595cb3c2ab3ab8097f6fa6c" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> 10H (Abstract Savior)<br />\n* You can get this character by acquiring the <span class="text-red">Deus Ex Machina</span> weapon.</p>\n<br />\n\n\n<h4>New Weapons</h4>\n<p><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/><img src="/images/common/icon/thumbnail_rarity_icon_rainbow.png" class="star"/></p>\n\n<p><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/b2f80a38e0b1175260f69f020d62a0c9113b895414187be36710f85f8ce878f5" class="weapon_icon" width="6%"> Deus Ex Machina<br /></p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Summons Details\n  </h3>\n    <div class="information_table">\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th style="width:10%">\n            Step\n          </th>\n          <th style="width:10%">\n            Type\n          </th>\n          <th style="width:13%">\n            Required Gems\n          </th>\n          <th style="width:67%">\n            Obtainable Shards, Bonuses, and Other\n          </th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            Step 1\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            x10 summons\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/gem_icon.png" width="20%"> <span class="text-red">1,500</span>\n          </td>\n          <td>\n Shard (Abstract Savior) x10<br> <span class="text-red">Piece: Black Pearl x2</span>\n\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            Step 2\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            x10 summons\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/gem_icon.png" width="20%"> 3,000\n          </td>\n          <td>\n Shards (Abstract Savior) x10<br> <span class="text-red">Piece: Black Pearl x2</span>\n\n\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            Step 3\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            x10 summons\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/gem_icon.png" width="20%"> 3,000\n          </td>\n          </td>\n          <td>\n Shards (Abstract Savior) x10 <br><span class="text-red">Piece: Black Pearl x2</span>\n\n\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>\n            Step 4\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            x10 summons\n          </td>\n          <td>\n            <img class="gem_icon" src="/images/common/icon/gem_icon.png" width="20%"> 3,000\n          </td>\n          </td>\n          <td>\n Shards (Abstract Savior) x10 <br>\n<span class="text-red">Piece: Black Pearl x2</span> <br>\n<span class="text-red">Abstract Savior</span> guaranteed in the 10th slot<br>\n\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n\n<p>\n</span>\n\n<p>\n* In this summons, <span class="text-red">all ★★★★ weapons that appear are guaranteed to be featured weapons</span>.<br>\n* A <span class="text-red">★★★ or above weapon</span> is guaranteed on the 10th summon on Steps 1-3, and a <span class="text-red">Abstract Savior</span> is guaranteed on the 10th summon on Step 4. <br />\n* You will proceed through Steps 1-4 in order, and then return to Step 1 after finishing Step 4.<br />\n* The Abstract Savior Multi-Step Summons does not have a limit to how many times you can loop back to Step 1.<br />\n* Any bonus you earn will be sent to your gift box.\n</p>\n\n</section>\n\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>About Shards (Abstract Savior)</h3>\n<p>\nYou will earn <span class="text-red">shards (Abstract Savior)</span> each time you use the Abstract Savior Summons.<br />\nThese items can be used at the Shard (Abstract Savior) Exchange to acquire new characters and weapons.<br />\n<br />\n* The Exchange <span class="text-red">is only available for a limited time.</span> Once the exchange period ends, you will be unable to exchange shards.<br />\n* Once the exchange period ends, each remaining shard <span class="text-red">will be converted into a bookmark</span> upon entering the summons screen.<br />\n* If you exchange for a character weapon you already own, you will earn <span class="text-red">10 ascension materials and 1 Awakening Stone for the character in addition to the weapon</span>.<br />\n* Shards can only be used at the exchange of the same name.<br />\n* You can earn shards from both the Abstract Savior Summons and the Paid Only: Abstract Savior Multi-Step Summons.<br />\n\n\n<p/>\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Resonant Costume Bonuses in Subjugation Battles</h3>\n<p>\n\nSeason 008 of Subjugation Battles will have a resonant costume quest bonus. The bonus effect of the resonant costumes <span class="text-red">reduces cooldown time for weapon skills in certain Subjugation Battle quests</span> and <span class="text-red">activates an attack increase based on the ascension count</span>.<br />\n</p>\n\n</section>\n<section>\n\n<div class="information_table weapon_table">\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n\n\n<th colSpan="5" class="al-center">Ascension Count and Effects</th>\n\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\n<th style="width:10%">None</th>\n<th style="width:10%">1</th>\n<th style="width:10%">2</th>\n<th style="width:10%">3</th>\n<th style="width:10%">4</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n\n<td>Attack <span class="text-red">+25%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n+10%<br /></td>\n<td>Attack <span class="text-red">+30%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n+10%<br /></td>\n<td>Attack <span class="text-red">+35%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n+10%<br /></td>\n<td>Attack <span class="text-red">+40%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n+10%<br /></td>\n<td>Attack <span class="text-red">+50%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed<br />\n+10%<br /></td>\n\n</tr>\n\n\n<tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n</section>\n<br />\n\n\n<section>\n<h4>Quest Bonus: Resonant Costume Effect</h4>\n<div class="information_table powerup_rate_table">\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>\nResonant Costume\n</th>\n<th>\nQuests\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>\n<img class="chara_image" src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/01/220f6eb74c5aca6c4a26e68cbd4f09e61055c421f595cb3c2ab3ab8097f6fa6c" alt=""> 10H (Abstract Savior)\n</th>\n\n<td>\n<span class="text-red"> Manifestation: Bright Cursed God</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n\n\n\n\n</table>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Event Quest Bonuses</h3>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/a360600bcebdfebbe9127ae162146d888e597f7bef55203f462cd7cb2291abdd">\n</div>\n<p>\nThe characters and weapons featured in this summons grant <span class="text-red">quest bonuses</span> in the event quest "Record: The Cage of Rebirth". Playing the quest with them will activate <span class="text-red">various effects</span> for your characters, and some effects will <span class="text-red">increase depending on the ascension count</span>.<br />\n\n\n<section>\n<h4>Quest Bonus: Resonant Costumes Effect List</h4>\n   <div class="information_table weapon_table">\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n\n         \n          <th colSpan="5" class="al-center">Resonant Costume "Abstract Savior" Ascension Count Effect</th>\n　　　　　　　　　\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n\n          <th style="width:10%">None</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">1</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">2</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">3</th>\n          <th style="width:10%">4</th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n   　　　　　<tr>                      <td>Character Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+30%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>           <td>Character Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+30%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+10%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>           <td>Character Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+40%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+10%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>           <td>Character Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+40%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+20%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>           <td>Character Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+50%</span><br />Weapon Skill Cooldown Speed <span class="text-red">+20%</span><br />HP +50%<br /></td>          </tr>\n         \n        <tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n\n\n<br />\n<p>\nThe number of The Cage of Rebirth Medals dropped <span class="text-red">will increase</span> depending on the weapon.</span><br />\n</p>\n\n</div>\n<h4> Quest Bonus: Resonance Weapon Effect</h4>\n<div class="information_table weapon_table">\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th rowSpan="2" style="width:28%">Weapon</th>\n<th colspan="5" style="text-align:center">Ascension Count</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th style="text-align:center">None</th>\n<th style="text-align:center">1</th>\n<th style="text-align:center">2</th>\n<th style="text-align:center">3</th>\n<th style="text-align:center">4</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th><img src="/images/en/operations/thumbnail/possession/02/b2f80a38e0b1175260f69f020d62a0c9113b895414187be36710f85f8ce878f5" class="weapon_icon"> Deus Ex Machina</th>\n<td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center">+5</td>\n<td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center">+11</td>\n<td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center">+17</td>\n<td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center">+23</td>\n<td rowSpan="2" style="text-align:center">+30</td>\n</tr>\n\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<br />\n<p>\nCheck the "Event Quest: ''Record: The Cage of Rebirth'' On Now" notice for more information.\n<p/>\n<div data-category="information" data-informationId="1616" class="other-link-btn common_btn common_button-typeA">Event Quest "Record: The Cage of Rebirth" On Now</div>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<div class="mama_balloon">\n<div class="mama_img">\n<img src="/images/common/other/webview_parts_mama.png" alt="">\n</div>\n<div class="balloon">We found these memories together.<br/>\nMemories slumbering in the same place within The Cage tend to interfere with one another, you see.</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>\nNotes\n</h3>\n<div class="attention_content">\n<ul>\n<li>\nEvent duration and content are subject to change without notice.\n</li>\n<li>\nIllustrations shown in notices, etc. may differ from those in-game.\n</li>\n<li>\nThe rarity, stats, skills, and abilities of characters and weapons displayed on the summons screen and on the official X account are shown at maximum levels.\n</li>\n<li>\n"Increased rates" means that the character''s appearance rate is higher than that of other characters of the same rarity.\n</li>\n<li>\n<span class="text-red">10H (Abstract Savior) &amp; Deus Ex Machina cannot be obtained with ★★★+ Tickets or ★★★★ Premium Summons Tickets. However, they may be added in future updates.</span>\n</li>\n<li>\nYou cannot have more than one character with the same name in the same deck.\n</li>\n<li>\nFor more information about rates, please check the Rates button on the summons page.\n</li>\n<li>\nIf you perform a summons using the 10x summon button, a ★★★ or higher weapon will always appear on the 10th summon, regardless of the results of the first 9 summons.\n</li>\n<li>\nThe video clip that plays when pressing the Skill button was recorded in a development environment.\n</li>\n<li>\nShards can only be used during the exchange period and cannot be carried over.\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<br />\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/a78b1fa5b227ee01e9b232c1e3abd375b80f983e4b1f9d0772a27b2f52a74a94','/images/en/operations/banner/b452d08a2bd6280ac5b596df19c9ec129f773601243c17adfaf794fcff14b373');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1647,0,2,'Resurrected Event Quest "Record: Eternal Steps"  On Now',1709863200000,replace('<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/29cb1f75ea855916de4810816590abcd9409e2643ebbfc124406d1cca49b4c09">\n</div>\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n<br />\nThe Resurrected Event Quest <span class="text-red">"Record: Eternal Steps"</span> has begun as of Mar. 7 18:00 PST.<br />\n<span class="text-red">Event Small Stamina Boost x300</span> have also been gifted to all players.<br />\n\n* Once the event quest ends, you will be unable to claim or use Event Small Stamina Boosts.\n\n</p>\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Duration</h3>\n<div class="holding-period">Mar. 7 18:00 - Apr. 29 21:59 PST</div>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>How to Play Event Quests</h3>\n\n<p>\nSave up the <span class="text-red">Eternal Steps Medals</span> you receive for completing quests to trade in at the <span class="text-red">Eternal Steps Medal Exchange</span> for the enhancements and other items.<br />\n<br>\nThe more difficult the quest, the more Medals you will earn as a reward.<br />\n</p>\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Countdown Resurrected Event Medal Exchange</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nFeb. 8 18:00 - Apr. 29 21:59 PST\n</div>\n\n<p>\nIn addition to the event-specific medals, Countdown Resurrected Event Medals are available at EX Hard difficulty for each Resurrected Event held during the period.<br>\nSave up the <span class="text-red">Countdown Resurrected Event Medals</span> you receive for completing quests to trade in at the <span class="text-red">Countdown Resurrected Event Medal Exchange</span> for an event-exclusive costumes, as well as enhancements and other items.<br />\n</p>\n</section>\n\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Mama Point Missions</h3>\n<p>\nCompleting missions will earn you <span class="text-red">Mama Points</span>.<br />\nCheck the Special tab on the Missions page for details.<br />\n</p>\n</section>\n\n\n\n\n\n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Notes\n  </h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n    <ul>\n\n \n<li>\n        Event duration and content are subject to change without notice.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Illustrations shown in notices, etc. may differ from those in-game.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        The rarity, stats, skills, and abilities of characters and weapons displayed in notices, in the summons screen, and on the official X account are shown at maximum levels.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        You cannot have more than one character with the same name in the same deck.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Once the exchange period has passed, <span class="text-red">you will be unable to exchange medals</span>.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Event-specific medals can only be used during the exchange period and <span class="text-red">cannot be carried over to the next event.</span>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<br>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/29cb1f75ea855916de4810816590abcd9409e2643ebbfc124406d1cca49b4c09','/images/en/operations/banner/55a8579280563eb7220d9736293c5553059efbab20016a23679a18fa8f0a4f86');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1648,0,4,'Final Chapter Countdown Campaign On Now',1709863200000,replace('<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/659dd728ba4f34273619bdf7a6c825507cf762a9ea47222b536d2adb1eb7067b">\n</div>\n\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n<br />\nThe <span class="text-red">Final Chapter Countdown Campaign</span> will be held from Mar. 7 18:00 PST.<br /></p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Final Chapter Countdown Campaign List</h3>\n</section>\n\n<br />\n\n<section>\n<h4>Final Chapter Countdown Login Bonus</h4>\n\n<div class="holding-period">\nMar. 8 0:00 - Mar. 28 23:59 PST\n</div>\n<p>\n <p>\n Get <span class="text-red">Karma Stone</span> from a new login bonus.<br>\n </p>\n <div class="information_table">\n  <table>\n  <tbody>\n  <tr>\n  <th width="120">Day</td>\n  <th>Rewards</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n  <td>Day 1</td>\n  <td>Karma Stone x10</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n  <td>Day 2</td>\n  <td>Karma Stone x10</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n  <td>Day 3</td>\n  <td>Karma Stone x10</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n  <td>Day 4</td>\n  <td><span class="text-red">Karma Stone x20</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n  <td>Day 5</td>\n  <td>Karma Stone x10</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n  <td>Day 6</td>\n  <td>Karma Stone x10</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n  <td>Day 7</td>\n  <td><span class="text-red">Karma Stone x30</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  </table>\n </div>\n <p>\n Note: You can receive login bonuses by going to Mama''s Room or The Cage.<br />\n Note: Login resets at 0:00 PST every day.<br />\n Note: You can retrieve your rewards by logging in during the period before Apr. 29 PST.<br>\n </p>\n <br>\n\n<br />\n\n\n<section>\n<h4>Final Chapter Countdown Gifts</h4>\n\n<p>\n<div class="holding-period">\nMar. 7 18:00 - Mar. 28 23:59 PST\n</div>\n<p>\nAll players will be gifted <span class="text-red">Light ★★★★ Guaranteed Summons Ticket</span> and <span class="text-red">Dark ★★★★ Guaranteed Summons Ticket</span>.\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<br>\n\n<section>\n<h4>Final Chapter Countdown Missions</h4>\n\n<p>\n<div class="holding-period">\nMar. 7 18:00 - Mar. 28 23:59 PST\n</div>\n<p>\nComplete the following missions to earn <span class="text-red">Premium Summon Ticket</span> and <span class="text-red">★★★★ Premium Summon Ticket</span>.<br>\n</p>\n<div class="information_table">\n  <table>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <th width="120">Stamina Used</td>\n        <th>Rewards</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>50</td>\n        <td>Gold x3,000,000</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>100</td>\n        <td>XL Weapon Enhancement x3,000</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>200</td>\n        <td>XL Character Enhancement x3,000</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>300</td>\n        <td>Skip Ticket x30</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>400</td>\n        <td>Small Slab Fragment x500</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>500</td>\n        <td>Medium Slab Fragment x200</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>1,000</td>\n        <td>Black Pearl x2</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>1,500</td>\n        <td>Fire ★★★★ Guaranteed Summons Ticket x3</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>2,000</td>\n        <td>Advanced Handbook x10</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>3,000</td>\n        <td>Water ★★★★ Guaranteed Summons Ticket x3</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>4,000</td>\n        <td>Insignia of Skill x2</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>6,000</td>\n        <td>Wind ★★★★ Guaranteed Summons Ticket x3</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>8,000</td>\n        <td>Insignia of Quality x4</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>10,000</td>\n        <td>Light ★★★★ Guaranteed Summons Ticket x3</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>12,000</td>\n        <td>Zenith''s Brilliance x30</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>15,000</td>\n        <td>Dark ★★★★ Guaranteed Summons Ticket x3</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>18,000</td>\n        <td>Adamant x30</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>20,000</td>\n        <td><span class="text-red">★★★★ Premium Summon Ticket x3</span></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>25,000</td>\n        <td>Karma Stone x30</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>30,000</td>\n        <td>Dark Karma Stone x30</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>35,000</td>\n        <td>Verse of Truth x3</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>40,000</td>\n        <td><span class="text-red">Premium Summon Ticket x50</span></td>\n      </tr>\n\n      </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n\n</section>\n\n<br>\n\n\n <section>\n<h4>Final Chapter Countdown Daily/Dark Memory Quest Drop Bonus</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nMar. 7 18:00 - Mar. 28 23:59 PST\n</div>\n<p>\nThe drop rate of all items in the daily quests and dark memory quests will increase by <span class="text-red">x10.</span><br>\n</p>\n</section>\n\n\n<br>\n \n <section>\n <h4>Final Chapter Countdown Daily/Dark Memory Quest Stamina 50% Off</h4>\n <div class="holding-period">\nMar. 7 18:00 - Mar. 28 23:59 PST\n </div>\n \n <p>\nDaily quests and dark memory quests will only require <span class="text-red">half the normal amount of stamina</span>.<br>\n <br>\n Note: If the original stamina cost is an odd number, the adjusted cost will be rounded down to the nearest integer.<br>\n \n </p>\n\n \n </section>\n<section>\n<h3>\nNotes\n</h3>\n<div class="attention_content">\n<ul>\n<li>\nDuration and content are subject to change without notice.\n</li>\n<li>\nIllustrations shown in notices, etc. may differ from those in-game.\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</section>\n<br />\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.<br /><br />\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/659dd728ba4f34273619bdf7a6c825507cf762a9ea47222b536d2adb1eb7067b','/images/en/operations/banner/86b14da3dec80858b5ddd5d09e3956da136a1c04a428310f1d263f711aca5c96');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1651,0,2,'Resurrected Event Quest "Record: Ritual of Reverie" On Now',1710468000000,replace('<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/ca1d21e70c3286c1d58cfb7575941a354dccb07bcacebeb548d777cfe48ae04c">\n</div>\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n<br />\nThe Resurrected Event Quest <span class="text-red">"Record: Ritual of Reverie"</span> has begun as of Mar. 14 18:00 PST.<br />\n<span class="text-red">Event Small Stamina Boost x300</span> have also been gifted to all players.<br />\n\n* Once the event quest ends, you will be unable to claim or use Event Small Stamina Boosts.\n\n</p>\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Duration</h3>\n<div class="holding-period">Mar. 14 18:00 - Apr. 29 21:59 PST</div>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>How to Play Event Quests</h3>\n\n<p>\nSave up the <span class="text-red">Ritual of Reverie Medals</span> you receive for completing quests to trade in at the <span class="text-red">Ritual of Reverie Medal Exchange</span> for the enhancements and other items.<br />\n<br>\nThe more difficult the quest, the more Medals you will earn as a reward.<br />\n</p>\n</section>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Countdown Resurrected Event Medal Exchange</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nFeb. 8 18:00 - Apr. 29 21:59 PST\n</div>\n\n<p>\nIn addition to the event-specific medals, Countdown Resurrected Event Medals are available at EX Hard difficulty for each Resurrected Event held during the period.<br>\nSave up the <span class="text-red">Countdown Resurrected Event Medals</span> you receive for completing quests to trade in at the <span class="text-red">Countdown Resurrected Event Medal Exchange</span> for an event-exclusive costumes, as well as enhancements and other items.<br />\n</p>\n</section>\n\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Mama Point Missions</h3>\n<p>\nCompleting missions will earn you <span class="text-red">Mama Points</span>.<br />\nCheck the Special tab on the Missions page for details.<br />\n</p>\n</section>\n\n\n\n\n\n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Notes\n  </h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n    <ul>\n\n \n<li>\n        Event duration and content are subject to change without notice.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Illustrations shown in notices, etc. may differ from those in-game.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        The rarity, stats, skills, and abilities of characters and weapons displayed in notices, in the summons screen, and on the official X account are shown at maximum levels.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        You cannot have more than one character with the same name in the same deck.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Once the exchange period has passed, <span class="text-red">you will be unable to exchange medals</span>.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        Event-specific medals can only be used during the exchange period and <span class="text-red">cannot be carried over to the next event.</span>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<br>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/ca1d21e70c3286c1d58cfb7575941a354dccb07bcacebeb548d777cfe48ae04c','/images/en/operations/banner/5a9bb48e4e7fffa7cd5bc48b9da1739e5396d8c34533fc68996e3dfb209bafa2');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1652,0,7,'Hidden Stories Added',1710727200000,replace('<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/b6bf668764f276a71e3c3df63e5f6249c3ba9e4ccd135303b1087143fa891bd0">\n </div>\n <section>\n <p>\n Hello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\n This is a message from the management team.<br />\n <br />\nNew <span class="text-red">Hidden Stories</span> have been added.<br>\n Check them from the Map screen.<br>\n<h3>Chapters with New Hidden Stories</h3>\n<div class="information_table">\n  <table>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <th width="120">Date Added</td>\n        <th>Chapter</td>\n<tr>\n　<td><span class="text-red">Mar. 17 PST</span></td>\n        <td>The People and the World "Act II: The Return"</td>\n\n</tr>\n<tr>\n　<td>Mar. 10 PST</td>\n        <td>The People and the World "Act II: The Return"</td>\n\n</tr>\n<tr>\n　<td>Mar. 3 PST</td>\n        <td>The People and the World "Act II: The Return"</td>\n\n</tr>\n<tr>\n　<td>Feb. 25 PST</td>\n        <td>The People and the World "Act II: The Return"</td>\n\n</tr>\n<tr>\n　<td>Feb. 18 PST</td>\n        <td>The People and the World "Act II: The Return"</td>\n\n</tr>\n\n      </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div>\n </p>\n </section>\n \n \n <section>\n <h3>Hidden Stories</h3>\n \n <h4>Hidden Stories will appear in The Cage for chapters you''ve already completed</h4>\n <p>\n If you use the map to revisit The Cage for a <span class="text-red">chapter you have completed</span>, you may discover a <span class="text-red">Hidden Story</span>.<br>\n Missions will appear upon access, and by clearing all of them, you will receive <span class="text-red">Hidden Stories for each character</span>.<br>\n Note: The map will be unlocked after you complete Quest 1 of Main Quest Ch. 3: Hard Sand.<br>\n Note: Some missions cannot be completed using skip tickets.<br>\n </p>\n \n <h4>The location of Hidden Stories can be found on the Map screen</h4>\n <p>\n Hidden Stories are marked with <span class="text-red">icons and notifications</span> on the Map screen.<br>\n </p>\n \n <h4>Reread Hidden Stories in the Library</h4>\n <p>\n You can read the Hidden Stories you''ve acquired in The Cage via the Hidden Stories option in the <span class="text-red">Extra Stories section of the Library</span>.<br>\n Note: Not all Hidden Stories that appear in the Library are currently available. More will be added in future updates.\n </p>\n \n \n </section>\n \n <section>\n <h3>Notes</h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n  <ul>\n  <li>\n  This content is subject to change without notice.\n  </li>\n  </ul>\n  </div>\n </section>\n <br />\n <p>\n Thank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n </p>','\n',char(10)),NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/b6bf668764f276a71e3c3df63e5f6249c3ba9e4ccd135303b1087143fa891bd0','/images/en/operations/banner/98926bc3f0b0a538126508627bf72e0105903c755eeb42ae0512bbfc59ed92a6');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1653,0,7,'Changes to some Hidden Stories unlock conditions',1710381600000,replace('<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br>\n<br>\nSome Hidden Stories missions will be changed on Mar. 28 18:00 PST.\n\n</p>\n\n<h3>Changes</h3>\n<p>\n</br>\n<div class="information_table">\n    <table style="width:100%">\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th style="width:10%" rowspan="2">\n            Before\n          </th>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <th style="width:20%">\n            After\n          </th>\n\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n\n      <tbody>\n\n        <tr>\n          <td>Win X time(s) in the Arena</td>\n          <td>Use 200 stamina to clear quests</td>       \n\n        <tr>\n\n          <td>Play the Arena X time(s)</td>\n          <td>Battle in Subjugations 5 times</td>\n\n        <tr>\n\n          <td>Send support to your friends X times</td>\n          <td>Send support to your friends 1 time</td>\n    </table>\n\n  </div>\n\n\n<p>\n* If you are in the middle of a mission set to be updated, your progress will be </section><span class="text-red">reset</span>.</br>\n* If you have already completed a mission set to be updated, it will maintain its completion status after the update.</br>\n</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>Thank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.</p>','\n',char(10)),NULL,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1654,0,6,'Maintenance Announcement',1711432800000,replace('<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/526e7b5c4037179e8e67e237d85becf49172380800dd326c06e93c071ac0674d">\n</div>\n<p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br />\n<br />\nMaintenance will take place during the following time.\n</p>\n\n\n<section>\n<h3>Maintenance Period</h3>\n\n<div class="holding-period">Mar. 28 12:00 - 18:00 PST</div>\n<p>*Please note that the maintenance period is subject to change without notice.<br>\n*You will not be able to login during maintenance.</p>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>Maintenance Details</h3>\n<p>\nLaunch preparation for final chapter release.<br />\n</p>\n</section>\n\n\n</section>\n\n<section>\n  <h3>Important</h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n    <ul>\n      <li>You will not be able to login during maintenance.</li>\n      <li>If maintenance occurs while you are in the middle of a quest (including on Auto-Repeat), you will be able to restart the WAVE you are in after maintenance ends.</li>\n<li>If you are unable to go to the title screen due to maintenance, please restart the application to resolve the issue.</li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n</section>\n<br />\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>','\n',char(10)),NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/526e7b5c4037179e8e67e237d85becf49172380800dd326c06e93c071ac0674d','/images/en/operations/banner/c9c5d4d05e8191effc63cf469e350b1386eb2fc7f7909420ed68d8c642c696b8');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1655,0,1,'Ver 3.7.0 Update',1711432800000,replace('<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/2dbfc2692574355ac476fa119e6784df2eade9b1f9f18c130a3c9df53c165feb">\n</div>\n<p>Hello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.</p>\n\n<p>\nThe new version, <span class="text-red">ver. 3.7.0, will be released</span> on Mar. 27 PST.<br>\n</p>\n\n<section>\n<h3>Update Details</h3>\n\n\n<h4>New main quest chapter Act III: Transmigration is now available.</h4>\n\n<br>\n\n<h4>Add Data Required for End of Service.</h4>\n\n<br>\n\n<h4>App Icon Updated.</h4>\n\n<br>\n\n<p>\nIn addition to the above update, we will conduct quality of life improvements and minor bug fixes.<br>\n</p>\n\n</section>\n\n<section>\n  <h3>Notes</h3>\n  <div class="attention_content">\n    <ul>\n <li>It may take some time for the new version of the app to show up in the store.</li>\n <li>This version update requires a large amount of data. We recommend using Wi-Fi while updating.</li>\n <li>The mandatory update to the new version is scheduled for <span class="text-red">Mar. 28, around 17:30 PST</span>.<br>\n* The mandatory update date/time is subject to change without notice. Thank you for your understanding.<br>\n* Until the update becomes mandatory, you can use the application even if you have not updated it yet.\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n\n\n<br>\n<p>Thank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/2dbfc2692574355ac476fa119e6784df2eade9b1f9f18c130a3c9df53c165feb','/images/en/operations/banner/03875df530f8b9b6bfe18b040bba799796a7aab9a4e5024670e373c6e877a0e0');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1656,0,4,'NieR Day Campaign On Now',1711612800000,replace('<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/d134a527c70f0c8edae432f455af20709456fe1901fc622405a3a7d0281da869">\n</div><p>\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\nThis is a message from the management team.<br /><br />\nOn the <span class="text-red">28th of every month,</span> NieR Re[in]carnation will hold various campaigns to celebrate <span class="text-red">NieR Day</span>.\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>NieR Day Gift</h3>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/29aec42b31ca3efc2e622c5d7189c01da4b00325a06be37065d8ad3e0db15583">\n</div>\n<h4>Duration</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nMar. 28 0:00 - 23:59 PST\n</div>\n<p>\nFor 24 hours only, we''re giving out <span class="text-red">Zenith''s Brilliance x1</span>, <span class="text-red">XL Weapon Enhancement x2180</span>, and <span class="text-red">XL Character Enhancement x2180</span>.<br />\nPlease claim them from your gift box.<br />\n<br />\nNote: You can claim the items from your gift box by logging in before Mar.  28 23:59 PST.<br />\nNote: If the items are not in your gift box, restarting the app will make them appear.<br>\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<h3>NieR Day Glorious Enhancement Guaranteed</h3>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/924adaedd067d04321d6b76d29014f7e9b90978e6b47ff3e8f6c2f45ebfdbeba">\n</div>\n<h4>Duration</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nMar. 28 0:00 - 23:59 PST\n</div>\n<p>\nFor 24 hours only, glorious enhancements are guaranteed for characters and weapons.<br>\n</p>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n  <h3>\n    Notes\n  </h3>  <div class="attention_content">\n      <li>\n        Event duration and content are subject to change without notice.\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        The next NieR Day campaigns may differ from the current ones.\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<br />\n<section>\n<p>\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n</p>\n</section>','\n',char(10)),NULL,'/images/en/operations/banner/d134a527c70f0c8edae432f455af20709456fe1901fc622405a3a7d0281da869','/images/en/operations/banner/f2bd28d575a64788fafafdb75d706e43ac76d386a1d1dcd828a49b2eeedfe7cb');
INSERT INTO information VALUES(1664,0,7,'Story Completion Event Content Adjustments',1710403200000,replace('<section>\n <p>\n Hello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\n This is a message from the management team.<br />\n <br />\nAs announced in the Mar. 6 PST Japanese official livestream, the Story Completion Event will be implemented with some adjustments.\n</p>\n<br />\n<section>\n<h4>Content Adjustments</h4>\n <p>\nThe Story Quest Stamina 0 Campaign has been changed to the <span class="text-red">Story Completion Story Quest Stamina 1 Campaign</span>.<br />\n<br />\nAs an apology for any inconvenience caused, all players will receive Gem x3,000. <br />\n*The apology gift is scheduled to be distributed on Mar. 28 PST. <br />\n </p>\n <p>\n Thank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n </p>','\n',char(10)),NULL,NULL,NULL);
